\id MAT - Ekajuk New Testament Nigeria
\h Matiu
\toc1 Matiu
\toc2 Mat
\mt2 NWER NYI
\mt1 MATIU
\c 1
\s1 Nwer nyi etꞌtohngo ji Jisos lohng no
\r (Luk 3:23-38)
\p 
\v 1 A wo li nwer nyi etꞌtohngo ji Jisos Kraist lohng no, ji jolo mmon a Devid,\f + \fr 1:1 \ft Mak 12:25-37\f* Devid ji jolo mmon no Ebraham.\f + \fr 1:1 \ft Jon 8:58\f*
\v 2 Ebraham jele Aisik. Aisik jel Jekob. Jekob jel Juda, a abon bako.
\v 3 Juda jele Peres, go Sera. Nnyehn ebo, bo jo lung-e re Tamar. Peres jel Hesron. Hesron jel Ram.
\v 4 Ram jel Aminadab, Aminadab jel Nason. Nason jel Salmon.
\v 5 Salmon jel Boas. Nnyehn Boas, bo jo lung-e re Rehab. Boas jel Obed. Nnyehn Obed, bo jo lung-e re Rut. Obed jel Jesi.
\v 6 Jesi jel Devid ji jolo ntul. Devid ji jolo ntul jel Solomon. Nnyehn Solomon tohko jol nkal Uraya.
\v 7 Solomon jel Rehoboam. Rehoboam jel Abija. Abija jel Asa.
\v 8 Asa jel Jehosafat. Jehosafat jel Joram. Joram jel Usia.
\v 9 Usia jel Jotam. Jotam jel Ehas. Ehas jel Hesekaya.
\v 10 Hesekaya jel Manase. Manase jel Amon. Amon jel Josia.
\v 11 Josia jel Jekonia, a abon bako, ngare nyi anebe Bebilon ba bob abone Israel, tahm a bo go Bebilon.
\p 
\v 12 Ngare nyi bo ma bob abone Israel, tahm a bo go Bebilon, owo Jekonia kehm jele Sealtiel. Sealtiel jel Serubabel.
\v 13 Serubabel jel Abiud. Abiud jel Eliakim. Eliakim jel Asor.
\v 14 Asor jel Sadohk. Sadohk jel Akim. Akim jel Eliud.
\v 15 Eliud jel Eleasar. Eleasar jel Matan. Matan jel Jekob.
\p 
\v 16 Jekob jel Josef ji jolo nlum a Meri. Meri ji jolo nnyehn Jisos, Jisos ji bo kpo lung-e re Kraist.
\v 17 Bomo goji Ebraham, nde nne lꞌjel mmon, mmon tahm jel ntem mmon ano ano tete ba rehng go ngare nyi Devid, babnde nne jolo ewubu ane ani. Bomo goji Devid, nde nne lꞌjel mmon, mmon tahm jel ntem mmon ano ano tete ba rehng ngare nyi bo bobo abone Israel, tahm a bo go Bebilon, babnde nne jolo ewubu ane ani. Bomo ngare nyi bo bobo abone Israel, tahm abo go Bebilon, nde nne lꞌjel mmon, mmon tahm jel ntem mmon ano ano tete ba rehng ngare nyi Kraist, babnde nne jolo ewubu ane ani.
\s1 Ana bo jele Jisos
\r (Luk 2:1-7)
\p 
\v 18 Ana wo bo jele Jisos Kraist. Nnyehn Jisos, bo jo lung-e re Meri. Ngare nyi bo ma lam elbal abola Josef, Josef tikem noongo a Meri, Meri sa ela go nsahm Etingi Etohko.\f + \fr 1:18 \ft Luk 1:35\f*
\v 19 Josef nlum ewe jolo nnobeljina nne. Á sebem re á sono Meri. Á sebe mbang ana nyi á bahk-e tene, ane kꞌwuk.
\p 
\v 20 Eji Josef jo tir nsol nyio kpee, enjel nyi Esowo kehm bake, ba kpir-e go nlem, kehm-e tongo re, “Josef ji mmon no Devid, ka kpe fahl elkoko Meri go elbal! Tibre ela bi á ma sa o, á sa go nsahm Etingi Etohko.
\v 21 Á bahke jele mmon, no a bahk-e gungu mbing re Jisos (ji lohngo re ntꞌtahre). Tibre á bahke tahre ane ebe yehke go ebo abiafem.”\f + \fr 1:21 \ft Luk 1:77; Elt 4:12\f*
\p 
\v 22 Nsol nyia kpee limi, eji alum nya Jehova bungu sehng goji nnyehnamahr lꞌlohko jol go etingitingi, nya á bungu re,
\v 23 “Mmongungu a nnenkal, (Ngbahme nyi bo kala nꞌnoongo a ne) bahke sake ela, jel mmon no nlum, no bo bahke jo lung-e re Emanuel.” (Ji lohngo re, “Esowo li a nahre”).
\p 
\v 24 Josef nyahme kan go ellu, á kehm limi ana enjel nyi Jehova tong-e no, á feere song ko Meri go elbal.
\v 25 Á tikem noongo a ne tete á jel ngbokambang a mmon ewe no nlum. Josef kehm-e gungu mbing re Jisos.
\c 2
\s1 Ana akahnkahn ane lohngo go ero nfam ba
\p 
\v 1 Jisos, bo jel-e go Betlehem ji Judea ngare nyi Herod jolo ntul. Owo akahnkahn ane kehm lohngo go ero nfam ba go Jeusalem,
\v 2 ba kehme elbahbe re, “Mmon no na, no bo m-e jel, no li ntul no Jus? Tibre wahr ebnyehn elonlo eje go ero nfam. Owo wahnge e ba no re wahr ba kak-e.”
\p 
\v 3 Eji ntul a Herod wuku ano, eltim kehm-e jokko, a aneb Jeusalem kpee.
\v 4 Owo á kehm lungu atubesi abalimajom, a atꞌtibi ba atahm, bo ba kono edi ajehng. Á kehm bahbe bo re, “Kraist jio, bo bahk-e jele gan?”
\p 
\v 5 Bo kehm-e faange re, “Go Betlehem ji Judea.\f + \fr 2:5 \ft Jon 7:42\f* Tibre ana wo nnyehnamahr Esowo nyono no re,
\q1 
\v 6 “ ‘Wahn Betlehem ji Juda,
\q1 wahn erennge ejahbe sang go mbang anyehng anyehng
\q1 go ellong atubesi ajahbe nya li go Juda.
\q1 Tibre go egahne ellong wo,
\q1 ntubesi bahke lohngo,
\q1 no bahke ba fili Israel, ane ebame.’ ”
\p 
\v 7 Herod kehm lungu akahnkahn ane bao, tahm a bo go nkpohko, song bahb bo ekahmekahme ngare nyi elonlo jio lohngo no.
\v 8 Owo á kehm tumu bo tv go Betlehem, a elle ni á tubu bo re, “Songen, wahn song seb mmon noo nob nob! Ń lꞌsong seb-e nyehn, lim-m wahn, me n kahn, eji me n lꞌtob je song kak-e fvfo.”
\p 
\v 9 Eji bo ma wuk ana ntul bungu no, bo kehm tahme. Elonlo ji bo jo nyehn go ero nfam kehm gboko bo mbang tete song yiimi edi ji mmon noo jolo no.
\v 10 Eji bo kpe nyehn elonlo jio yim no, bo bele eyebatahng sehng, fere jo gꞌgeere.
\v 11 Bo kehm yele ekpꞌkpa, song nyehn mmon, a Meri nnyehn, gbo jamme alahng, kak mmon. Bo kehm soro lennge abam ebo, yehke agul, frankinsens, a mmir, yare mmon.
\p 
\v 12 Esowo kehm rehke bo go nlem re, bo kꞌkpe feere goji Herod. Owo bo kehm sehnge mbang nyindiki kehnge.
\s1 Ana Josef abola Meri, be no, tahm go Ijib
\p 
\v 13 Ngare nyi akahnkahn ane bao ma tahm fi, owo enjel nyi Esowo kehm ba kpiri Josef go nlem, kehm-e tongo re, “Tahm, wo rod mmon, a nnyehn, be, song go Ijib, kang ona tete me n kpe ba tong-a. Tibre Herod yahke ba mmon noa seb re á wul.”
\p 
\v 14 Josef kehm tahme, rod mmon, a nnyehn, bo tahm atv atv song rehng go Ijib.
\v 15 Owo á jolo no tete Herod kpo, eji lꞌlohko jol ana Jehova bungu sehng goji nnyehnamahr re, “N lungu mmon ewame go Ijib, á lohng ba.”
\s1 Ana Herod wulu abonse ba nse a nse
\p 
\v 16 Herod sebe kan kahn re, akahnkahn ane m-e nehm, atahng kehm-e rake tete. Á kehm tumu ane, bo song wul abon ba nlum kpee go Betlehem, a abon ajahbe ba li sennge o kak, ba ma kang bomo nnya ebal feere ndi, tib ana á wuku goji akahnkahn ane bao bada ngare nyi elonlo lohngo no.
\p 
\v 17 Ngare nyio nyi lohko lim ana nnyehnamahr Jeremaya bungu no re,
\q1 
\v 18 “Bobwuk ewahl ane go Rama,
\q1 ewahl ji ane ma biingi aling,
\q1 fere kpꞌlingi ndon ndon.
\q1 Resel kpꞌlingi abon ebe.
\q1 Bo kak-e eltim,
\q1 jol eltim we tikem naange,
\q1 tibre bo kpeem li elikiliki.”
\s1 Ana Bab Josef feere kehnge go Nasaret
\p 
\v 19 Ngare nyi Herod ma kpo, owo enjel nyi Jehova kehm kpe song kpiri Josef go nlem, eji á jolo go Ijib, kehm-e tongo re,
\v 20 “Tahm, rod mmon, a nnyehn, wo feere a bo go ndi nyi Israel. Tibre ane ba jo seb re bo ba wul mmon bobkpo.”
\p 
\v 21 Josef kehm tahme, rod mmon, a nnyehn, feere a bo go ndi nyi Israel.
\v 22 Eji Josef wuku re, Arkelaus ebko nji nyi nde Herod, kpꞌfili Judea, á kehm kehme elfahle eljeke o. Owo Esowo kehm-e kpe rehke go nlem, Josef kehm tahme go ejang bi Galili,
\v 23 song lene go ejahbe ji bo kpo lung re Nasaret, eji lꞌlohko jol ana abanyehnamahr Esowo bungu no re, “Bo bahke jo lung-e re nne a Nasaret.”\f + \fr 2:23 \ft Jon 1:46; 7:41\f*
\c 3
\s1 Etib bi Jon ji nwohngalahb jo tiingi
\r (Mak 1:1-8; Luk 3:1-18; Jon 1:19-28)
\p 
\v 1 Ngare nyio Jon ji nwohngalahb kehm lohngo ba, ba kehme elbungu go elka emahng nio ni Judea re,
\v 2 “Yaangen elkpin enahne, tibre etul bi Esowo ebkabbe.”
\p 
\v 3 Jon wo jolo nne no nnyehnamahr Aisaya jo bung bada ne, eji á jo bung re,
\q1 “Nne noa,
\q1 kpꞌrabe go elka emahng re,
\q1 ‘Tuungen mbang nyi Ntul bum-e.
\q1 Limen mbang tꞌtor,
\q1 nyi á bahke sehnge.’ ”
\p 
\v 4 Nsol nyi Jon jo kak, bo limi go anyar nyam nyi bo kpo lung re ekamel. Á jo gbaange egbaange ji bo limi go ngunyam. Á jo li agohrobi, fere jo yab akehng ekon.
\v 5 Ane jo lohngo go Jeusalem je go ege, a ane ba jolo go Judea kpee, go ane kpee ba lene ajahbe nya jolo egbuk ebbal ebbal bi aya ma bo kpo lung re Jodan.
\v 6 Bo jo fvvrv abiafem ebo, á jo wohngo bo alahb go Jodan.
\p 
\v 7 Eji Jon nyehne aneb Farisi, a anebe Sadusi gbalee kpꞌbake re á wohngo bo alahb, á kehm tongo bo re, “Wahn ane ba li ana akumbad ba! Nne awo tong-n re, ḿ bahke foro go erakatahng ji Esowo ji kpꞌbake?
\v 8 Limen nsol nyi bahke tibi re, wahn eblohko yaange elkpin enahne.
\v 9 Kana kpe laange, fere jo bung go egahna ntim re, ‘Ebraham wo li nso ejahre.’\f + \fr 3:9 \ft Jon 8:33-39; Rom 2:28-29; 4:12\f* N kp-n tongo re, Esowo bahke ma ko atal nyaa, lim abon ka Ebraham.\f + \fr 3:9 \ft Gal 3:26-29\f*
\p 
\v 10 “Bobtoobo elfuk bum, ni bo bahke kiimi alohk nti, melle nti nyio. Eti ajehng ajehng ji tohko kab akab nya nno, bo bahke mehle tub, fere rod kak agun.\f + \fr 3:10 \ft Luk 13:7-9\f*
\p 
\v 11 “N kp-n wohngo alahb mao ma egbokondon. Nne no kpꞌbake toon-m wo ga gbal sehnge me. Jol me n fuumem re me n sol akpaketa enye. Á bahk-n wohngo alahb go Etingi Etohko, a agun.\f + \fr 3:11 \ft Elt 1:5; 2:3\f*
\v 12 A fili edꞌda go ebo, kpꞌfebe arasi enye. Á bahke kpuku arasi enye, song kak go ege ekpꞌkpa, fere jahm awal go agun nya lꞌkꞌtiki lahme elahmelahme.”
\s1 Ana Jisos bele ewohngalahb
\r (Mak 1:9-11; Luk 3:21-22)
\p 
\v 13 Ngare nyio Jisos kehm tahme go Galili, song rehng go Jodan goji Jon re Jon wohng-e alahb.\f + \fr 3:13 \ft Luk 12:50; Jon 1:29-34\f*
\v 14 Jon jo gare re á sahd-e, kehm-e tongo re, “Kehn wo wo nobo re wo wohngo na me alahb, wo ma fere ba na ga egame.”
\p 
\v 15 Owo Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Nong jol ano! Tibre fuumu re wahr lim nsol kpee nyi Esowo sebe re wahr lim.”\f + \fr 3:15 \ft 2 Kor 5:21\f* Jon kehm taame.
\p 
\v 16 Tvtv o eji Jisos ma bel ewohngalahb, á kehm lohngo go alahb. Ngare nyio ejahbetul Esowo eblennge ka-e. Owo á kehm nyehne etohko ji Esowo go elfoongo ni ebbehl kpꞌbadde abake, kehm ba jol a ne.
\v 17 Owo bo kehm wuku ellum go ejahbetul Esowo ni bungu re, “A wo li akor-m mmon ewame, no kpo kor-m sꞌsehng.”\f + \fr 3:17 \ft Mak 9:7\f*
\c 4
\s1 Ana nnehm gare Jisos
\r (Mak 1:12-13; Luk 4:1-13)
\p 
\v 1 Etingi Etohko kehm yehke Jisos, song kak go elka emahng re nnehm gar-e.\f + \fr 4:1 \ft Jems 1:2; Hib 4:15\f*
\v 2 Eji Jisos ma bade elne njal nfung atahl abal, owo njal kehm-e yame.
\v 3 Nnehm kehm bake, ba tong-e re, “A lꞌjol Mmon Esowo, tong atal nyaa siingi abred.”
\p 
\v 4 Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Bo nyono go nwer Esowo re, ‘Abred nya nya sang wahnge nne kpo kpin, á kpo bel elkpin go ellum anehng anehng ni lohng go nnyo mi Esowo.’ ”\f + \fr 4:4 \ft Jon 4:34; 6:27\f*
\p 
\v 5 Nnehm kehm rodo Jisos, tahm a ne go mbarebare ejahbe, song kun-e go elkong etahk Esowo,
\v 6 kehm-e tongo re, “A lꞌjol Mmon Esowo, yehb, wo ba gbo go ndi! Tibre bo nyono go nwer Esowo re,
\q1 “ ‘Esowo bahke tongo enjel enye bada na.
\q1 Bo bahk-a gbiiri go bo abo,
\q1 eji a lꞌkꞌba jahre akpade enya go eltal.’ ”
\p 
\v 7 Jisos kehm faange re, “Bo tꞌtob nyon go nwer Esowo re, ‘Ka gare Esowo, Ntul ewa!’ ”\f + \fr 4:7 \ft Mat 27:42\f*
\p 
\v 8 Nnehm kehm kpe rod Jisos, tahm a ne go ewong ji sahb wꞌwahre, fere tib-e ajahbe kpee nya li go njini, a ellub ni bo kpi no,
\v 9 kehm-e tongo re, “M bahk-a kake nyaa kpee, a lꞌjamme alahng kak-m.”
\p 
\v 10 Owo Jisos kehm-e tongo re, “Nnehm, tahm-m go esamahr! Tibre bo nyono go nwer Esowo re, ‘Esowo, Ntul ewa wo wo, a bahk-e jo kak. Ye ntahngtahng wo, a bahke fere jo lok-e.’ ”\f + \fr 4:10 \ft Jems 4:7-8\f*
\p 
\v 11 Nnehm kehm-e soro yake. Babenjel soro ba kak-e ebo.
\s1 Ana Jisos bomo alum Esowo abungu go Galili
\r (Mak 1:14-15; Luk 4:14-15)
\p 
\v 12 Eji Jisos wuku re, Jon, bo m-e kak ngbekobo, á kehm tahme eje, song rehng go Galili.\f + \fr 4:12 \ft Mat 14:3\f*
\v 13 A kehm tahme go Nasaret, fere song lene go Kapenium ji jolo kohlo eto ji Galili, go ndi nyi abone Sebulon, a ba Naftali,
\v 14 eji lꞌlohko jol jang jang ana nnyehnamahr Aisaya bungu no re,
\q1 
\v 15 “Ndi nyi abon Sebulon,
\q1 a ba Naftali,
\q1 ba lene ejang bio bi eto ji Galili li no,
\q1 egbuk Jodan
\q1 jehko go Galili jio ji ane ba ki nyi Esowo,
\q1 
\v 16 ane bao ba jehk go ejannge
\q1 ebnyehn egburu ellennge.
\q1 Ane bao ba nong go emel elkv,\f + \fr 4:16 \ft Elt 26:18\f*
\q1 edi ebkehme bo lennge.”
\p 
\v 17 Bomo ngare nyio asongo Jisos kehm kehme etib ebe tiingi re, “Senngen njahm go egahne abiafem! Tibre etul bi Esowo ebkabbe.”
\s1 Ana Jisos lungu abasahre nsahre, ane na ani
\r (Mak 1:16-20; Luk 5:1-11)
\p 
\v 18 Eji Jisos jo jen go nkpe eto nyi Galili, á kehm nyehne abasahre nsahre, ane na abal, noko jolo Saimon ji bo jo lung-e re Pita, noko, bo jo lung-e re Andru ji mmonannyehn Pita.\f + \fr 4:18 \ft Jon 1:35-42\f* Bo kake erim alahb.
\v 19 Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Tahmen toon-m, m bahk-n limi ń fere jo bim ane.”
\v 20 Bo kehm soro tahm arim ebo sa, tahm toon-e.\f + \fr 4:20 \ft Mat 19:27\f*
\p 
\v 21 Jisos kehm kpe sehng asongo, kpe song nyehn ane abal bako. Noko, bo jo lung-e re Jems. Noko, bo jo lung-e re Jon, mmonannyehn Jems. Bo jolo abon Sibidi. Bo woomo go egbang, jo baade arim ebo, a Sibidi nde ebo. Owo Jisos kehm lungu bo.
\v 22 Bo kehm soro tahm egbang sa, tahm nde ebo sa, tahm toono Jisos.
\s1 Ana Jisos jo tib, fere jo lim aneb ayam, bo nob
\r (Luk 6:17-19)
\p 
\v 23 Jisos kehm tahme, jo yannge go Galili kpee, jo tib ane go bo ntahk ero, fere jo tiingi nnoobo etib bio bi etul bi Esowo, fere jo lim ane, bo nob elkohn eyam abehng abehng.\f + \fr 4:23 \ft Elt 10:38\f*
\v 24 Ane kpee ba jolo go Siria wuku kan elgahm ene, owo bo kehm koko aneb ayam kpee ba go ege, ba jo yam ajoobo ayam tvv, fere jo nyehn ajoobo arem, a ane ba bele abi atohko go bo a ntim, a aneb eyam atatehk, a ane ba ma banne. Jisos limi bo kpee, bo nob.
\v 25 Ellong ane gbalee ba jo toon-e, egom jindiki lohng go Galili, egom jindiki lohng go Dekapolis, egom jindiki lohng go Jeusalem, egom jindiki lohng go Judea, egom jindiki lohng go egbuk Jodan jehko.
\c 5
\s1 Alum nya Jisos bungu go ero ewong
\r (Luk 6:20-23)
\p 
\v 1 Eji Jisos nyehne ellong ane bao, á kehm tahme go ewong. Á ji kan a me, abatꞌtoono ebe kehm bake go ege.
\v 2 Á kehm kehme bo tib re,
\p 
\v 3 “Elfuulu li ka ane ba ma gbo ekpak bio bi etohko. Tibre etul bi Esowo li ka bo.\f + \fr 5:3 \ft Luk 18:13-14\f*
\p 
\v 4 “Elfuulu li ka ane ba jehk ndon ndon. Tibre bo bahke kake bo eltim.\f + \fr 5:4 \ft Ell 7:14-17\f*
\p 
\v 5 “Elfuulu li ka ane ba kpi nnaange eljini. Tibre bo bahke bele njini ana ejum elehke elkv ebo.
\p 
\v 6 “Elfuulu li ka ane ba kpꞌsahb sꞌseb re bo li eno go esamahr bi Esowo. Tibre bo bahke lehke eno.\f + \fr 5:6 \ft Elt 16:30\f*
\p 
\v 7 “Elfuulu li ka ane ba, ane kpo fili bo ndon. Tibre bo bahke tob fili Esowo ndon.\f + \fr 5:7 \ft Jems 2:13\f*
\p 
\v 8 “Elfuulu li ka ane ba ntim ebo li saang. Tibre bo bahke nyehne Esowo.\f + \fr 5:8 \ft 1 Jon 3:2-3\f*
\p 
\v 9 “Elfuulu li ka ane ba kpo seb elkoono.\f + \fr 5:9 \ft Rom 12:18\f* Tibre bo bahke jo lung bo re abon ba Esowo.
\p 
\v 10 “Elfuulu li ka ane ba, bo kpꞌnohko bo tib eji bo kpꞌlimi nsol nyi li go etingitingi. Tibre etul bi Esowo li ka bo.\f + \fr 5:10 \ft 1 Pit 3:14\f*
\p 
\v 11 “Elfuulu li ka-n, ane lꞌjo su-n, fere jo nohk-n, fere jo kiimi elkohn efahnge anehng anehng lak-n tib go egame esi.
\p 
\v 12 “Belen eyebatahng, wahn jo geere. Tibre eltuuru enahne ni li go ejahbetul Esowo kpꞌgbale. Ano wo bo jo tob nohk abanyehnamahr Esowo ba tohko jol, wahn kehm jini.
\s1 Akang abola ellennge
\r (Mak 9:50; Luk 14:34-35)
\p 
\v 13 “Wahn ba li akang ma njini.\f + \fr 5:13 \ft Kol 4:6\f* Elyebe akang lꞌlohng go akang, bahke limi renan, kehm kpe yebe? Nehm kpe nob ellahbe. Bo bahke sale na wohng go, ane jo kadde sehng.
\p 
\v 14 “Wahn ba li ellennge ni njini.\f + \fr 5:14 \ft Fil 2:15\f* Ejahbe ji bo si kunu go ewong nehm kpe ma biiri.
\v 15 Nnene limm, no kpo nyaale etꞌrekahng, rod ejeere konngo. Á bahke rodo na kunu go ejum ji bo kpo kunu atꞌrekahng. Owo bahke yake ka ane kpee ba wob ekpꞌkpa jio.
\v 16 Nong, ellennge enahne ni ń kpi no jo ya go esamahr ane, eji bo lꞌnyehn nnoobo enyahne nyi ń kpo lim, fere jo tehk nso ejahne no li go ejahbetul.\f + \fr 5:16 \ft Ef 5:8-9\f*
\s1 Alum nya Jisos bungu bade atahm nya Moses
\p 
\v 17 “Kana tir re m ba re me m ba range atahm nya Moses, a eltibi ni abanyehnamahr tibi no.\f + \fr 5:17 \ft Rom 3:31\f* M baam re me m ba range, m ba re me n gohro ba lim, biingi go nseenge.\f + \fr 5:17 \ft Rom 8:3-4; 10:4\f*
\v 18 Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Eji elbung abola ndi kpeke li, mmonrꞌrohka mmojum awohng awohng no atahm nehm range tete rehng esꞌkohro ji nsol kpee bahke male.\f + \fr 5:18 \ft Luk 16:17\f*
\p 
\v 19 “Owo fvfo, nne awohng awohng no lꞌyuudu nrꞌrohka mmontahm awohng awohng,\f + \fr 5:19 \ft Jems 2:10\f* afi á tibi ane ano, ye wo bahke ga jol nkpak go ejahbetul Esowo sehnge ane kpee. Nne awohng awohng no lꞌbum atahm, fere jo tꞌtib, ye wo bahke jolo njꞌjoka nne go ejahbetul Esowo.
\p 
\v 20 “N kp-n tongo re, ń nehm ma yel go ejahbetul Esowo, sehngem re, eno ejahne ji ḿ bahke lehke go esamahr Esowo sehnge ji atꞌtibi ba atahm, a Bab Farisi.\f + \fr 5:20 \ft Rom 9:31-33\f*
\s1 Eltibi ni li bade elkoono
\p 
\v 21 “Wahn ebwuk ana bo tongo ane ba jolo mahne mahne re, ‘Kana jo wul nne! Nne awohng awohng no lꞌwul nne, bo bahk-e koko, tahm ane go elam.’
\v 22 Wo, me n kp-n tongo re, Nne awohng awohng no eltim lꞌrak-e tob mmonannyehn, bo bahk-e koko, tahm a ne go elam. Nne awohng awohng no lꞌsu mmonannyehn, bo bahk-e koko, tahm a ne go esub. Nne awohng awohng no lꞌtong mmonannyehn re, ‘Egboolo ji!’ yeblim ebi ji bo bahk-e koko, song kak go ellulagun.\f + \fr 5:22 \ft 1 Jon 3:15\f*
\p 
\v 23 “A lꞌko ayare ba a nya go edi njom alimi, a lꞌfere buumu ona re, ń li go ntong awahn a mmonanne,
\v 24 yake ayare enya bum kohlo edi njom alimi jio, wo feere, tohko song bung ntong nyio mal, fere koono a mmonanne, wo kehm feere ba ka ayare enya.\f + \fr 5:24 \ft Mak 11:25\f*
\v 25 Jo koono a nnekv ewa elwaare, eji ngare kpeke li,\f + \fr 5:25 \ft Hib 3:13,15; 9:27\f* eji nnekv ewa lꞌki-a song kak esub, nlamalam rod-a kak mbehresi go ebo, á rod-a song kak ngbekobo.
\v 26 Etingitingi, n kp-a tongo re, Owo a bahke woomo tete a gohro gal mbong nyi a bele no, jol ederi ajehng ajehng nehm sa.\f + \fr 5:26 \ft Mat 18:34\f*
\s1 Eltibi ni li bade erehbe
\p 
\v 27 “Wahn ebwuk ana bo bungu re, ‘Ka jo lim erehbe!’
\v 28 Wo, me n kp-n tongo re, Nne awohng awohng no lꞌyehke amahr enye kunu nnenkal re á noongo a ne, yeblim abiafem nya erehbe go ege eltim.\f + \fr 5:28 \ft 2 Pit 2:14\f*
\v 29 Elmahr eboblum ena lꞌwahng re wo lim abiafem, luudu ro go! Ga nob re ejum ngubjing enya demme, sehnge re bo rod ngubjing enya kpee, song kak go ellulagun.
\v 30 Eboblum eba lꞌwahng re wo lim abiafem, kim tub go!\f + \fr 5:30 \ft Kol 3:5\f* Ga nob re ejum ngubjing enya tan, sehnge re bo rod ngubjing enya kpee, song kak go ellulagun.
\s1 Eltibi ni li bade elbal amale
\r (Mat 19:9; Mak 10:11-12; Luk 16:18)
\p 
\v 31 “Bo kpe bung re, ‘Nne awohng awohng no lꞌyehke nkal ewe elbal, nong á nyon nwer ka-e, nyi á m-e yehke elbal.’
\v 32 Wo, me n kp-n tongo re, Nne awohng awohng no lꞌyehke nkal ewe elbal, eji nnenlum nondiki ki noongo a ne, á kp-e limi re á lim erehbe. Nne awohng awohng no lꞌko nnenkal no bo m-e yehke elbal, á kpꞌlimi erehbe.\f + \fr 5:32 \ft 1 Kor 7:10-11\f*
\s1 Eltibi ni li bade enyam anyame
\p 
\v 33 “Wahn ebtob wuk ana bo tongo ane ba jolo mahne mahne re, ‘Ka jo tir go edaange! Ka kane enyam bi a nyame no go esamahr bi Jehova!’
\v 34 Wo, me n kp-n tongo re, wahn kꞌjo tir nkpel anyehng anyehng. Kana jo tir elbung! Tibre elbung, eti etul ji Esowo ji.
\v 35 Kana jo tir ndi! Tibre ndi, etikunakpade eje ji. Kana jo tir Jeusalem! Tibre Jeusalem, ejahbe ji egburu ntul ji.
\v 36 Ka jo tir esi eja! Tibre a nehm ma lim ellv esi anehng re, jol mbarebare, jol a nehm ma lim re, jol nnyakenyake.
\p 
\v 37 “Nong, wahn jo faange re, ‘Ee,’ tohko jol ano, ‘Eꞌee.’ Ellum anehng anehng ni lꞌjol sehnge ano, lohng goji Ebinne jio.\f + \fr 5:37 \ft 2 Kor 1:17; Jems 5:12\f*
\s1 Eltibi ni li bada nfem abongo
\r (Luk 6:29-30)
\p 
\v 38 “Wahn ebwuk ana bo bungu re, ‘Nne no lꞌwa ntem elmahr, bo tob wa-e elmahr. Nne no lꞌbahk ntem elmahn, bo tob bahk-e elmahn.’
\v 39 Wo, me n kp-n tongo re, Kana jo sahde ebi nne go eko!\f + \fr 5:39 \ft Mat 26:52-53\f* Nne lꞌrum-a elkpal go ekpoko eboblum, sennge ekpoko ebobkal ka-e, á kpe-a rum.
\v 40 Nne no lꞌgbaame ewobo eja re á kpꞌkoko, kpe yake nkud enya ka-e.\f + \fr 5:40 \ft 1 Kor 6:7\f*
\v 41 Nne no lꞌbob-a re, wo jen mmal anyehng a ne, jen mmal ebal a ne.
\v 42 Nne no lꞌlem-a ejum, ka-e! Nne no lꞌba re á ba yaame ejum go ega, ka-e!
\s1 Ana nne, anebekv ebe bahke jo kor-e
\r (Luk 6:27-28,32-36)
\p 
\v 43 “Wahn ebwuk ana bo tongo re, ‘Nne ebjing ewa bahke jo kor-a, nnekv ewa jo sab-a.’
\v 44 Wo, me n kp-n tongo re, Nong, anebekv ebahne jo kor-n. Jo biren nnoobo tv ane ba kp-n suku! Jo limen nnoobo ka ane ba kpo ko-n ekv!\f + \fr 5:44 \ft Rom 12:20-21\f* Jo kaken ero ka ane ba kpo ka-n ebi mbol mbol, a ane ba kpo nohk-n,\f + \fr 5:44 \ft Elt 7:60\f*
\v 45 eji ń lꞌjol abon ba Nso ejahne no li go ejahbetul.\f + \fr 5:45 \ft Ef 5:1\f* Tibre á kpo lim njul enye jo ya tub abi ane, a anoobo ane. Á kpo na elahb ka ane ba ma li eno, a ane ba ma li ebi.
\p 
\v 46 “Anv, ane ba ń kpo kor bo, bo l'tob jo kor-n, eltuuru anii Esowo bahk-n tuuru? Anv, abakokatak kpehme lim anoa?
\v 47 Ń lꞌjo kak abonane ejahne nnyo ba ba, anv, nkpokosi ejum anyi nyi ḿ ma lim? Anv, ane ba ki nyi Esowo kpehme lim anoa?
\v 48 Jolen saang, wahn kꞌbel elem ajehng ajehng, ana Nso ejahne no li go ero li saang.
\c 6
\s1 Eltibi ni li bada nnoobo alimi
\p 
\v 1 “Kunen ekpu, eji ń lꞌkꞌjo lim nnoobo enyahne go esamahr ane, tohko jol ano, Nso ejahne no li go ero wahn nehm tuuru.
\v 2 Ngare anyehng anyehng nyi a lꞌlim nnoobo, ka jo tooro yannge, ana ane ba kpo tib elbo go ekpꞌkpa ero, fere jo jen alab nfam, eji ane lꞌjo tehk bo. N kp-n tongo re, Eltuuru ebo ebsehng mbang.
\v 3 A lꞌlim nnoobo, nong, ebobkal eba kꞌkahn ji eboblum eba kpꞌlimi,
\v 4 eji nnoobo enya nyi a kpꞌlimi lꞌkꞌjo jol gbul gbul gbuul. Nso no kpo nyehn nsol nyi ki li gbul gbul gbuul bahk-a tuuru.\f + \fr 6:4 \ft Mak 4:22; Luk 8:17\f*
\s1 Eltibi ni li bade ero akake
\r (Luk 11:2-4)
\p 
\v 5 “A lꞌkehme ero kak, ka jo lim ana ane ba kpo tib elfuumu elfuumu. Kpo kor bo re bo jo mehl yiimi go ekpꞌkpa ero, fere yiimi elatahkgur, jo kak ero, eji ane lꞌnyehn bo. Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Eltuuru ebo ebsehng mbang.
\v 6 A lꞌkehm kake ero, yel go ega nkimi. Eji a ma bam mbu tv elna, wo kehm kake ero ka Nso no ane lꞌki-e ma nyehn. Nsoo no kpo nyehn nsol nyi ki li gbul gbul gbuul bahk-a tuuru.
\p 
\v 7 “A lꞌkehm kake ero, ka jo lim ewok mbol mbol, ana ane ba ki nyi Esowo kpo lim. Ane bao ba kpo tir re, Esowo bahke wuku bo, tib eji bo kpꞌkake alaabe aro.
\v 8 Kana jol ana bo! Tibre Nso ejahne kpꞌkahne nsol nyi ń kpꞌsebe, jol ń kehm-e bahbe.
\v 9 Ana wo nobo re wahn jo kak ero re,
\q1 “Nso ejahre no li go ero, nong, mbing enya jol saang.
\q1 
\v 10 Yake etul eba ba.
\q1 Nong ntir enya,
\q1 afi jolo go ndi, afi jolo go ero.\f + \fr 6:10 \ft Mat 7:21; Luk 22:42\f*
\q1 
\v 11 Ka-r ejum alehke ji lꞌbiingi a nahre lela.\f + \fr 6:11 \ft Fil 4:6\f*
\q1 
\v 12 Jo tahm ka-r go egahre abiafem, ana wahr kpo tahm ka ane ba lim-r abiafem.\f + \fr 6:12 \ft Mat 18:21-35\f*
\q1 
\v 13 Ka lim, e yel go elgaare.\f + \fr 6:13 \ft Jems 1:13\f* Jo tahr-r yehke go abiafem.
\p 
\v 14 “Ń lꞌtahm ka ane go bo abꞌbi nya bo lim-n no, Nso ejahne no li go ero bahke tob tahm ka-n go egahne abꞌbi.
\v 15 Ń tohko tahm ka ane go bo abꞌbi nya bo lim-n no, bahke limi renan, Nso ejahne kehm tob tahm ka-n?
\s1 Eltibi ni li bada njal abade
\p 
\v 16 “Ń lꞌkehme elnahne njal bade, kana jo gehn asamahr, ana ane ba kpo tib elfuumu elfuumu kpo lim. Bo kpo gbod asamahr ebo, eji ane lꞌkahn re, bo kpi elbo njal bade. Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Eltuuru ebo ebsehng mbang.\f + \fr 6:16 \ft Luk 18:12\f*
\v 17 A lꞌkehme elna njal bade, jo ru esamahr, wo fere jak esi,
\v 18 eji ane lꞌkꞌkahn re, a kpi elna njal bade, sehngem Nso no ane kil-e elnyehne wo bahke kahne. Nso no kpo nyehn nsol nyi ki li gbul gbul gbuul bahk-a tuuru.
\s1 Afang nya li go ejahbetul
\r (Luk 12:33-34)
\p 
\v 19 “Kana jo kpu nsol afang bum elnahne go njini nyia, edi ji bahke biili amahn, etan fere wo, awajv fere wa yel ba v.\f + \fr 6:19 \ft Luk 12:16-21\f*
\v 20 Ga nob re wahn kpu nsol afang bum elnahne go ejahbetul Esowo, edi ji lꞌkꞌtiki biili amahn, etan lꞌkꞌma wo, awajv lꞌkꞌma wa yel song v.\f + \fr 6:20 \ft Mat 19:21\f*
\v 21 Tibre eltim ena bahke tiki jol edi ji afang enya li no.\f + \fr 6:21 \ft Kol 3:1-3\f*
\s1 Ellennge ni ngubjing
\r (Luk 11:34-36)
\p 
\v 22 “Elmahr ni li ana etꞌrekahng ka ngubjing. Elmahr ena lꞌjol sange sange, ngubjing enya bahke bele ellennge.
\v 23 Elmahr ena lꞌjol abꞌbi abꞌbi, ngubjing enya bahke jolo ejannge ejannge. Ellennge ni wob-a go atahng lꞌfere kpiidi, jol ejannge, nkom ejannge nyi bahke jolo tete, jol nyi nse sang.
\s1 Atꞌtiiri nya njini nyia
\r (Luk 16:13; 12:22-31)
\p 
\v 24 “Nnene limm, no bahke ma loko nde na ebal. Á bahke koko noko ekv, noko jo kor-e. Tohko jol ano, á bahke lake na awohng, fere jo daange noko. Ń nehm ma loko Esowo, fere jo loko akpohko.
\p 
\v 25 “Ana wo wahnge n kp-n tongo re, Kana jo tiiri bada nsol nyi ḿ bahke jo li, fere jo wꞌwo, a nsol nyi ḿ bahke jo kak go ngubjing.\f + \fr 6:25 \ft 1 Pit 5:7\f* Elkpin sang ga gbal sehnge nsol alehka? Ngubjing sang ga gbal sehnge aboma?
\v 26 Nyehnen nruk ana bo kpꞌfonngo go elbung yannge. Bo kpehme bahm nsol. Bo kpehme kpa. Bo kpehme sol, song lake go abuungu. Nso ejahne no li go ero wo kpo le bo. Anv, wahn sang ga gbal sehnge nruka?\f + \fr 6:26 \ft Mat 10:29-31\f*
\v 27 Nne awo ewahne no bahke kpe ma budu abon nnya go ege elkpin, eji á kpꞌtiiri ana?
\p 
\v 28 “Jen ji wahnge ń kpꞌtiiri bada nsol ngubjing? Nyehnen ana atꞌtul nkpad kpo gbal go emahng. Bo kpehme nyennge lim eltum. Bo kpehme jamme nsol kak elbo.
\v 29 N kp-n tongo re, Jol Solomon go ege ellub á liibem ana atꞌtul nyao.
\v 30 Ana Esowo kpo liibi ajele nya li go emahng, nya kpo kpin lela lela, behna bo jahm fi, jen ji wahnge á lꞌki-n tob liibi, wahn ji kpꞌkahn taame ntiil?
\p 
\v 31 “Owo fvfo nobo re wahn kꞌjo tiiri, fere jo bung re, ‘Ejum aji e bahke jo li, fere jo wo, fere jo kak go ngubjing?’
\v 32 Nsol nyia nyi ane ba ki nyi Esowo kpo tiiri. Wo, wahn, Nso ejahne no li go ero kpꞌkahne re, nsol nyia kpee nobo re wahn bel.\f + \fr 6:32 \ft Hib 13:5\f*
\v 33 Ga nob re wahn gbo mbang tiiri bade etul bi Esowo, ana ḿ bahke lehke eno go ege esamahr. Á bahk-n budu nsol nyehko kpee.
\p 
\v 34 “Kana jo tiiri bade nya behna! Nong behna tiiri bade elne. Efung abehng abehng kpo bel afemfem nyanye. Wahn, kana jo budu atꞌtiiri nya nyahne!
\c 7
\s1 Kana jo lam ane bako
\r (Luk 6:37-38,41-42)
\p 
\v 1 “Kana jo lam ane bako, eji Esowo lꞌki-n tob lam.\f + \fr 7:1 \ft Rom 2:1; 1 Kor 4:5\f*
\v 2 Tibre go mbang nyꞌnehm nyi ń kpo lam ane bako, nyi nyi Esowo bahke tob ko lam-n. Ana ń gaare no ka, ano wo Esowo bahke tob gare ka-n.
\p 
\v 3 “Jen ji wahnge a kpꞌseenge mmolsahk no wob mmonanne go elmahr, a kil eltiiri bada nkporti nyi wob go ega elmahr?
\v 4 A bahke sahbe renan, tong mmonanne re, ‘Nong, me n yehk-a mmolsahk no wob-a go elmahr,’ eji nkporti wob-a go elmahr?
\v 5 Wobnob tane! Tohko gbo mbang yehke nkporti go ega elmahr, eji a lꞌmal nyehn, yehke mmolsahk no wob go elmahr mmonanne.\f + \fr 7:5 \ft Gal 6:1-5\f*
\p 
\v 6 “Kana jo ka ebv nsol Esowo nyi li eje eje, eji bo lꞌkꞌtahm kehm-n eljaake.\f + \fr 7:6 \ft Mat 10:14\f* Kana jo rod amohkesol ro tv akuk, eji bo lꞌkꞌkadde go bo akpade.
\s1 Bahben, ḿ bahke bele
\r (Luk 11:9-13)
\p 
\v 7 “Bahben, ḿ bahke bele. Seben, ḿ bahke nyehne. Kahden, bo bahke lennge mbu ka-n.
\v 8 Tibre nne awohng awong no lꞌbahb, á bahke bele. Nne no lꞌseb, á bahke nyehne. Nne no lꞌkahd, bo bahke lennge mbu ka-e.
\p 
\v 9 “Nne awo ewahne no bahke kake mmon ewe eltal, á lꞌbahb-e re á ka-e nsol alehke?\f + \fr 7:9 \ft Mak 11:24\f*
\v 10 Afi á bahke rodo nnyo ka-e, á lꞌbahb-e re á ka-e nsahre?
\v 11 Wahn ji li na abi ane, ń kpꞌkahne ana ń kpo ka abon ebahne nsol nyi nno, lꞌlim renan, Nso ejahne no li go ero lꞌki-n tob ka nsol nyi nno, ń lꞌbahb-e?\f + \fr 7:11 \ft Jems 4:3\f*
\p 
\v 12 “Nsol kpee nyi ń kpꞌsebe re ane bako jo lim ka-n, nyi nyi ḿ bahke tob jo lim ka bo. Ń lꞌlim ano, wahn ebbum atahm nya Esowo, a alum nya abanyehnamahr bungu no.\f + \fr 7:12 \ft Mat 22:37-40; Rom 13:8-10\f*
\s1 Nfiidifiidi eti mbu
\r (Luk 13:24)
\p 
\v 13 “Sehngen go nfiidifiidi eti mbu jio! Tibre mbang nyi li rehng go ellulagun, mbang elfohk elkul nyi, eti mbu eje kpꞌkpange. Ane gbalee ba kpꞌsehnge ona.
\v 14 Wo, mbang nyi li rehng go elkpin, mbang asodaroongo nyi. Eti mbu eje li fii.\f + \fr 7:14 \ft Mat 19:24; Elt 14:22\f* Ane ba kpꞌnyehne mbang nyio li ntiil.
\s1 Nnoobo eti, bo kpo liing-e go ege akab
\r (Luk 6:43-44)
\p 
\v 15 “Jo gberen akimfahnge abanyehnamahr. Bo kpo ba go egahne, jo ba lim, are ejoro bi. Wo, go bo atahng bo li, are abibbib enyam bi.\f + \fr 7:15 \ft Elt 20:29\f*
\v 16 Go bo akab wo, ḿ bahke bo liingi. Anv, asokonso, nne kpo jꞌje song bong akab avaina? Agasame, nne kpo je song bong akab afiga?\f + \fr 7:16 \ft Gal 5:19-23; Jems 3:12\f*
\p 
\v 17 “Eti ji nno ajehng ajehng kpo kab anoobo akab. Esabsab eti kpo kab abi akab.
\v 18 Eti ji nno nehm ma kab abi akab. Esabsab eti nehm ma kab anoobo akab.
\v 19 Eti ajehng ajehng ji tohko kab anoobo akab, bo bahke gbahke kak agun.\f + \fr 7:19 \ft Jon 15:2,6\f*
\v 20 Go bo akab wo fvfo, ḿ bahke bo liingi.
\s1 Wahn n nehme kahn
\r (Luk 13:25-27)
\p 
\v 21 “Nne awohng awohng sang no kpo lung-m re, ‘Ntul, Ntul!’ bahke yele go ejahbetul Esowo, sehngem ye ji kpꞌlimi ji Nsoo no li go ero tong-e no re á lim bahke yele.\f + \fr 7:21 \ft Rom 2:13; Jems 1:22\f*
\v 22 Efung bio ane gbalee bahk-m bahbe re, ‘Ntul, wahr sang jo nyehn amahr go ega mbinga, fere jo kam abi atohko yehke go ega mbinga, jo lim akpokosi gbalee go ega mbinga?’\f + \fr 7:22 \ft 1 Kor 13:1-2\f*
\v 23 Owo m bahke kehm tongo bo re, ‘Me, wahn n nehme kahn.\f + \fr 7:23 \ft Mat 25:12\f* Fak-m wahn go esamahr, wahn aneb abꞌbi ba!’
\s1 Ana ane abal si ntahk
\r (Luk 6:47-49)
\p 
\v 24 “Fvfo, nne awohng awohng no lꞌwuk alum enyame, fere jo lim, á li ana ekahnkahn nne no si etahk eje kunu go ekpartal.\f + \fr 7:24 \ft 1 Kor 10:4\f*
\v 25 Elahb kehm ba na, nnyel kehm yele, kuumu agbunggbung, rehng etahk jio, nfeb kehm kehme ellimi, jo gbul etahk jio. Tikem gbo. Tibre á si kunu go ekpartal.
\p 
\v 26 “Nne awohng awohng no lꞌwuk alum enyame, kꞌlim, á li ana egboolo nne ji si etahk eje kunu go erikehndi.
\v 27 Elahb kehm ba na, nnyel kehm yele, kuumu agbunggbung, rehng etahk jio, nfeb kehm kehme ellimi, jo gbul etahk jio.\f + \fr 7:27 \ft Ell 18:10\f* Etahk jio kehm gboko, wa rꞌrere rꞌrere.”
\s1 Nsahm nyi Jisos
\p 
\v 28 Eji Jisos ma bung nsol nyia mal, eltibi ene kehm kpoko ellong ane bao esi.
\v 29 Á jo tibi bo ana nne no kpi nsahm. Á joom tib ana atꞌtibi ebo ba atahm.
\c 8
\s1 Ana Jisos limi nne abili, á nob
\r (Mak 1:40-45; Luk 5:12-16)
\p 
\v 1 Jisos kehm badde go ewong jio, ellong ane gbalee tahm toon-e.
\v 2 Nne abili kehm lohngo ba go ege, kehm ba jamm-e alahng, kehm bungu re, “Nsoo, lꞌkor-a, a li-m ma lim, n nob.”
\p 
\v 3 Jisos kehm tanne ebo ebe, koor-e, kehm bungu re, “Kor-m kor, wobnob!” Tvtv ona á kehm soro nob abili enye.
\p 
\v 4 Owo Jisos kehm-e tongo re, “Ka tiki tong nne awohng awohng, wobwuka? Song goji nlimajom, wo song tib-e elna, fere lim njom nyi Moses tibi no, eji lꞌjol ejum ntianse ka ane.”
\s1 Ana Jisos limi nlokeltum awohng, á nob go Kapenium
\r (Luk 7:1-10)
\p 
\v 5 Eji Jisos rehnge go Kapenium, ntubesi a nsoja no Rom kehm bake, ba kpir-e, kehm-e gboongo
\v 6 re, “Nsoo, nlokeltum ewame noa go etahk, kpꞌyame gꞌga, jol á nehme ma jen.”
\p 
\v 7 Jisos kehm-e tongo re, “M bahke bake ba lim-e, á nob.”
\p 
\v 8 Owo ntubesi a nsoja noo kehm-e faange re, “Nsoo, me n fuumem re wo ba yel go egame ekpꞌkpa. Lub bung na bung ellum, nlokeltum ewame bahke nobo.
\v 9 Tibre me n li nne no wob nne go elwo. N tob kpi nsoja nyi wob-m go elwo. N lꞌtong noo re, ‘Song!’ á tahm. N lꞌtong noka re, ‘Ba!’ á ba. N lꞌtong nlokeltum ewame re, ‘Lim jia!’ á lim na lim.”
\p 
\v 10 Eji Jisos wuku ano, kehm-e kpoko esi. Á kehm tongo ane ba jo toon-e re, “Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, elkohn eltaame ana nia n ka nyehn a nyehn go Israel.\f + \fr 8:10 \ft Mat 15:28\f*
\v 11 N kp-n tongo re, Ane gbalee bahke lohngo go ero nfam, a erede nfam ba ji a Ebraham, a Aisik, go Jekob go ejahbetul Esowo, jo li nsol a bo.\f + \fr 8:11 \ft Luk 13:28-29\f*
\v 12 Wo, abon ntul ba jol lehke etul, bo bahke rodo bo, ro kak edi ji nkom ejannge li no. Owo ane bahke jo ling, fere jo kono amahn.”
\p 
\v 13 Owo Jisos kehm tongo ntubesi a nsoja noo re, “Song kehnge! Ana a ma taame, ano wo bahke jolo ka-a.”\f + \fr 8:13 \ft Mat 9:29\f* Ngare nyꞌnehm ona nyi nlokeltum ewe nobo eyam ebe.
\s1 Ana Jisos limi aneb ayam gbalee, bo nob
\r (Mak 1:29-34; Luk 4:38-41)
\p 
\v 14 Jisos song rehnge kan etahk Pita, á kehm song nyehn nnyehn nkal a Pita nong kpꞌyame arumbum.\f + \fr 8:14 \ft 1 Kor 9:5\f*
\v 15 Á kehm-e kooro go ebo, á kehm soro nob arumbum nyao, kehm soro tahm, kehm-e kehme elloko.
\p 
\v 16 Eji elgung ba no, ane kehm koko ane gbalee ba bele abi atohko, ba go ege. Á kehm kame bo abi atohko nyao kpee yehke go ege ellum, fere lim aneb ayam kpee, bo nob,
\v 17 eji lꞌlohko jol ana Esowo bungu sehng goji nnyehnamahr Aisaya re,
\q1 “Á rodo elleenge enahre,
\q1 fere sol ayam enyahre.”
\s1 Nong, akvne kpa akvne kak
\r (Luk 9:57-62)
\p 
\v 18 Eji Jisos nyehne ellong ane gbalee ba ma ba yiimi senng-e kak, á kehm tongo abatꞌtoono ebe re, “Wahr tahmen egbuk jehko!”
\p 
\v 19 Owo ntꞌtibi atahm awohng kehm bake go ege, ba tong-e re, “Ntꞌtibi, m bahk-a toono rehng edi ajehng ajehng ji a fi no.”
\p 
\v 20 Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Akpangang kpi abing nya bo kpo woomo. Nruk kpi ntahk nyi bo kpo kang. Wo, Mmon no nne, edi ellohko esi ajehng ajehng á kpimm.”\f + \fr 8:20 \ft 2 Kor 8:9\f*
\p 
\v 21 Nne noko no jolo ntꞌtoono Jisos kehm-e tongo re, “Nsoo, nong, me n tohko song kpa nsoo kak.”\f + \fr 8:21 \ft Mat 10:37\f*
\p 
\v 22 Owo Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Tahm toon-m, nong, akvne kpa atem akvne kak!”\f + \fr 8:22 \ft Ef 2:1; 5:14; Kol 2:13\f*
\s1 Ana Jisos bungu tong nfeb, a ebuku
\r (Mak 4:35-41; Luk 8:22-25)
\p 
\v 23 Jisos kehm yele go egbang, abatꞌtoono ebe tahm toon-e.
\v 24 Owo egburu nfeb nyi nnen a nnen kehm ba kehme ellimi go eto jio, ebuku jo lim, bulu egbang. Ngare nyio Jisos jo lꞌlal.
\v 25 Abatꞌtoono ebe kehm jeke go ege, song nyahm-e, kehm-e tongo re, “Nsoo, tahr-r, e kpꞌtane na a!”
\p 
\v 26 Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Jen ji wahnge ń kpꞌfahle ana, wahn ji kpꞌkahn taame ntiil?”\f + \fr 8:26 \ft Mat 14:31; 16:8\f* Owo á kehm mehle yiimi, kehm nyame nfeb, a ebuku. Edi kehm naange soom.
\p 
\v 27 Owo kehm kpoko ane bao esi. Bo kehm bungu re, “Elkohn nne awo anae, no kpo bung tong nfeb, a ebuku, bo wuk-e?”
\s1 Ana Jisos limi ane abal ba bele abi atohko, bo nob
\r (Mak 5:1-20; Luk 8:26-39)
\p 
\v 28 Jisos kehm bake go Gadara ji jolo go egbuk eto jehko. Owo ane abal kehm lohngo edi ji alahm akvne jolo no, ba wan-e. Bo bele abi atohko go bo atahng. Bo jo mennge sehng. Jol nne awohng awohng joom sahb, sehng mbang nyio.
\v 29 Owo bo kehm biingi tiim re, “Anv, Mmon no Esowo, jen ji e kpi no me atemtem? Anv, a ba na re wo ba kak-r erema, eji ngare kala biinga?”\f + \fr 8:29 \ft 2 Pit 2:4\f*
\p 
\v 30 Ellong akuk jolo ona kpidi kpidi, jo li nsol.
\v 31 Abi atohko kehm gboongo Jisos re, “A lꞌkehm-r kame yake, nong, wahr song yel akuk nyao go atahng.”
\p 
\v 32 Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Songen!” Bo kehm soro lohng, song yel akuk nyao go atahng. Ellong akuk nio kehm soro rehm abahl, song fooro agbunggbung eto jio, yel go alahb tan.
\p 
\v 33 Ane ba jo baabe akuk nyao, kehm soro be ebo tahm, song rehng go nla ejahbe, song tooro kpee, fere tooro ejum ji ma lim ane ba bele abi atohko.
\v 34 Ejahbe jio kpee kehm tahme, song kpiri Jisos. Eji bo song nyehn-e, bo kehm-e gboongo re, á lub tahm ejahbe jio song.\f + \fr 8:34 \ft Jon 4:40\f*
\c 9
\s1 Ana Jisos limi nne no ki jo ma jen, á nob
\r (Mak 2:1-12; Luk 5:17-26)
\p 
\v 1 Jisos kehm yele go egbang, siiri eto jio, song rehng go ege ejahbe.\f + \fr 9:1 \ft Mat 4:13\f*
\v 2 Ane bandiki kehm koko mbanne nyi noongo go edilnong ba a ne go ege. Eji Jisos nyehne eltaame ebo, á kehm tongo mbanne nyio re, “Mmon ewame, bob eltim! Abiafem enya, me n tahm ka-a.”
\p 
\v 3 Owo atꞌtibi ba atahm bandiki kehm kehme elbungu atemtem re, “Nne noa kpꞌsuku Esowo, eji á ma rod elne bum ana Esowo.”
\p 
\v 4 Jisos kꞌkahn ntir atahng ebo, owo á kehm bungu re, “Jen ji wahnge ń kpꞌtiri elkohn abi nsol ana nyao go egahna ntim?\f + \fr 9:4 \ft Jon 2:25\f*
\v 5 Anv, jen ji ga riidi, n lꞌtong-e re, ‘Abiafem enya me n tahm ka-a,’ afi n lꞌtong-e re, ‘Tahm, wo jen!’?
\v 6 M bahk-n tibi re, Mmon no nne kpi nsahm go njini nyia nyi á bahke ma tahm ka nne go ege abiafem.”\f + \fr 9:6 \ft Mat 1:21\f*
\p Owo á kehm tongo mbanne nyio re, “Mehl, wo rod edilnong eja, song kehnge!”
\p 
\v 7 Nne noo kehm mehle yiimi, tahm eje kehnge.
\v 8 Eji ane bao nyehne ano, bo kehm kehme elfahle, fere jo tehk Esowo bi ma ka ane elkohn nsahm ana nyio.
\s1 Ana Jisos lungu Matiu
\r (Mak 2:13-17; Luk 5:27-32)
\p 
\v 9 Jisos kehm tahme edi jio. Eji á jo sehng asongo, á kehm nyehne nne no jehk go ege a nji atak, no bo jo lung-e re Matiu. Owo á kehm-e tongo re, “Tahm toon-m!”
\p Matiu kehm soro tahm toon-e.
\p 
\v 10 Efung abehng eji Jisos jolo go etahk Matiu, jo li nsol, abakokatak gbalee, a aneb abꞌbi jolo a ne o, go abatꞌtoono ebe fvfo, tob jo li nsol.
\p 
\v 11 Egom Farisi jindiki nyehne kan ano, bo kehm tongo abatꞌtoono ebe re, “Jen ji wahnge ntꞌtibi ewahne kpo li nsol edi ajehng a abakokatak, go aneb abꞌbi?”\f + \fr 9:11 \ft Luk 15:2\f*
\p 
\v 12 Jisos kehm wuku ana bo jo bung, kehm faange re, “Ane ba li nob nob kpehme seb nlimakahm, sehngem ane ba kpꞌyame ba ba kpo seb nlimakahm.
\v 13 Songen, wahn song kpili bade ana edi nwer Esowo jia lohngo no, ji bungu re, ‘Njom sang n kpꞌsebe, ndon nyi.’ M baam re me m ba lung anoobo ane, m ba re me m ba lung aneb abꞌbi re bo gbo ndon.”\f + \fr 9:13 \ft Mat 18:11\f*
\s1 Mbahbe nyi li bada njal abade
\r (Mak 2:18-20; Luk 5:33-35)
\p 
\v 14 Abatꞌtoono Jon ji nwohngalahb kehm bake goji Jisos, ba bahb-e re, “Jen ji wahnge wahr, a Bab Farisi, e kpo kono elnahre njal bade, abatꞌtoono eba kil jo bade?”\f + \fr 9:14 \ft Luk 18:12\f*
\p 
\v 15 Owo Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Anv, atem nlumanne li ma ji ndon ndon go elkak elbala, eji nlumanne kpeke li a boa?\f + \fr 9:15 \ft Jon 3:29\f* Efung bahke rehnge bi bo bahke rodo nlumanne go bo ellong, tahm a ne. Ngare nyio nyi, bo bahke kehme elbo njal bade.
\s1 Eltibi ni mahne mahne lꞌli, eltibi ni Jisos lꞌli
\r (Mak 2:21-22; Luk 5:36-39)
\p 
\v 16 “Nnene limm, no bahke koko mmojang mbomo no nfenfe, song baade nkꞌkula mbomo. Á lꞌlim ano, mmojang mbomo no nfenfe nehm yiimi. Nkꞌkula mbomo mio bahke kpe kv edi jio budu sehnge ana wuku wuku.\f + \fr 9:16 \ft Jon 1:17\f*
\v 17 Nnene limm, no bahke yaange amahm ma kpꞌfahle kak go nkꞌkohko eyahbe. Á lꞌlim ano, eyahbe jio bahke bahnge na, amahm sale. Nobo re nne ko amahm ma kpꞌfahle, song yaange kak go eyahbe nfenfe.\f + \fr 9:17 \ft Rom 7:6\f* Eyahbe nfenfe jio, a amahm bahke jolo nob nob.”
\s1 Mmon a ntubesi, a nnenkal no kooro Jisos go ege a nsubu
\r (Mak 5:21-43; Luk 8:40-56)
\p 
\v 18 Eji Jisos jo bung nsol nyia tong bo, owo ntubesi a Jus awohng kehm lohngo ba, ba jamm-e alahng, kehm bungu re, “Mmon ewame kpꞌna kpoko. Ba wahr tahm, wo ba koor-e ebo, eji á lꞌfere bel elkpin.”
\p 
\v 19 Jisos kehm tahme toon-e, a abatꞌtoono ebe fvfo.
\p 
\v 20 Mmonankal awohng no alung sa-e go nnahb ewubu a nnya ebal, kehm kehme Jisos toono go njahm, kehm kooro esꞌsili nsubu enye.
\v 21 Tibre á bungu go ege eltim re, “N lꞌlub kooro nsubu enye nyi nyi, m bahke nobo.”\f + \fr 9:21 \ft Mat 14:36\f*
\p 
\v 22 Jisos kehm keebe, nyehn-e, kehm-e tongo re, “Mmon ewame, bob eltim! Eltaame ena ni ma-a lim, a ma nob.” Ngare nyꞌnehm ona nyi nnenkal noo kehm soro nob.
\p 
\v 23 Owo Jisos kehm ba rehng go etahk ntubesi noo, ba nyehn aneb ase, a ane ba ba elkv, bo kpꞌkubu ase, jo lim ewok.
\v 24 Á kehm tongo bo re, “Tahmen, tibre mmon noa ka kpo, á kpꞌlale na.”
\p Owo bo kehm-e elwolo.
\p 
\v 25 Bo kame kan ane bao yehke me, Jisos kehm yele ekpꞌkpa song jabbe mmonse nkal noo go ebo, á kehm mehle ji.\f + \fr 9:25 \ft Luk 7:15; Jon 11:44\f*
\p 
\v 26 Eka jio kehm yeere na yeere ejahbe jio kpee.
\s1 Ana Jisos limi awakamahr, ane abal, bo nyehn
\p 
\v 27 Jisos kehm tahme edi jio, jo jen asongo. Awakamahr ane abal kehm-e kehme eltoono, fere jo rabe re, “Mmon no Devid, nong, wahr lub fil-a ndon!”
\p 
\v 28 Eji Jisos yele go ekpꞌkpa, awakamahr ane bao kehm ba kpir-e. Owo Jisos kehm bahbe bo re, “Anv, ń kpꞌtaame re m bahke ma lim ejum ana jiaa?”
\p Owo bo kehm taame re, “Ee nsoo.”
\p 
\v 29 Jisos kehm kooro bo go amahr, kehm bungu re, “Nong, jol ana ḿ ma taame.”\f + \fr 9:29 \ft Ell 3:17-18\f*
\p 
\v 30 Amahr ebo kehm soro lennge.
\p Jisos kehm bungu a bo tꞌtahne re, “Kana tiki tong nnene!”
\p 
\v 31 Bo kehm tahme, song tooro tong ejahbe jio kpee ji Jisos ma lim.
\s1 Ana Jisos limi nkamme, á bung
\p 
\v 32 Eji ane bao kpꞌtahme asongo, ane bako kehm koko nkamme ba a ne go ege, nyi bele ebi etohko go ege atahng.
\v 33 Jisos kehm kame nne noo ebi etohko jio yehke, nne noo soro kehme elbungu.
\p Ane bao kehm kpoko bo esi. Bo kehm kehme elbungu re, “Elkohn ejum ana jia, e ka nyehn a nyehn go Israel.”
\p 
\v 34 Bab Farisi kehm bungu re, “Ntul a nnehm wo ka-e nsahm re á jo kam ane abi atohko yehke.”\f + \fr 9:34 \ft Mat 12:24\f*
\s1 Ana ane fili Jisos ndon
\p 
\v 35 Jisos kehm tahme, jo yannge ajahbe nya nnen, a nya nse kpee. Á jo tibi ane go bo ntahk ero, fere jo tiingi bo nnoobo etib bi etul bi Esowo, fere jo lim ane, bo jo nob elkohn eyam abehng abehng.
\v 36 Eji á nyehne ellong ane, bo kehm-e fili ndon. Tibre eko ebtan bo, nkakebo bo kpimm, bo jolo ana ejoro bi ki kpi mbꞌbaabe.\f + \fr 9:36 \ft Mak 6:34\f*
\v 37 Owo á kehm tongo abatꞌtoono ebe re, “Egburu egbe jia, ji elkpake, wo, abalimeltum li ntiil.\f + \fr 9:37 \ft Luk 10:2\f*
\v 38 Gboongen nfono egbe, eji á lꞌtum abalimeltum tv re bo ba kpa egbe eje.”
\c 10
\s1 Abatꞌtoono ebe, ewubu ane abal
\r (Mak 3:13-19; Luk 6:12-16)
\p 
\v 1 Jisos kehm lungu abatꞌtoono ebe, ewubu ane abal tv elne, kehm kake bo nsahm re bo kam ane abi atohko yehke, fere lim ane, bo nob elkohn eyam abehng abehng.
\v 2 Abing abatiingetib ewubu ane abal nya a. Ngbokambang, Saimon ji bo jo lung-e re Pita, go Andru mmonannyehn, go Jems ji mmon a Sibidi, a Jon ji mmonannyehn Jems,
\v 3 go Filip, Batolomi, Tomos, go Matiu nkokatak, Jems ji mmon Alfeus, a Lebeus ji bo jo lung-e re Tadeus,
\v 4 a Saimon ji jo seb re ejahbe eje lohng go elwo ni aneb Rom, go Judas Iskariot ji gungu Jisos.
\s1 Eltum ni abatꞌtoono Jisos song lim
\r (Mak 6:7-13; Luk 9:1-6)
\p 
\v 5 Re Jisos kehm tumu ewubu ane abal bao, á tubu bo elle re, “Kana je ajahbe nya ane ba ki li Jus, a ajahbe Samaria.
\v 6 Songen goji ejoro bi Israel bi ma tan.\f + \fr 10:6 \ft Mat 15:24; Elt 13:46\f*
\v 7 Song bungen alum Esowo re, ‘Etul bi Esowo ebkabbe.’
\v 8 Limen aneb ayam, bo nob, wahn lim aneb abili, bo nob, fere nyahme akvne go elkv, fere kam ane abi atohko yehke.
\p “Ana n ka-n mbol mbol, tob kaan go mbol mbol.\f + \fr 10:8 \ft Elt 20:33; 1 Pit 5:2\f*
\v 9 Kana fili agul, a asilva, jol kana kak apene go egahne abam fili.
\v 10 Kana fili abam efilibo, fere fili mbomo ebal ebal, a akpaketa, a nti efilibo. Tibre nlimeltum fꞌfuumu re á bel nsol alehke.\f + \fr 10:10 \ft Luk 22:35; 1 Kor 9:4-15\f*
\p 
\v 11 “Ejahbe ajehng ajehng ji ń lꞌsong rehng, afi jolo egburu ejahbe, afi jolo mmojahbe no nse, seben nne no bahke kahne re, eltum enahne ni nno ni. Kangen a ne o tete wahn tahm ejahbe jio.
\v 12 Ń lꞌyange go etahk nne, kaken bo nnyo.
\v 13 Ane bao lꞌvvr-n, nong, elkoono ni ń kpi no jol a bo. Bo tohko fere vvr-n, elkoono ni ń kpi no bahke feere, ba tob-n.
\v 14 Nne awohng awohng no tohk-n vvrv, kꞌwuungu atung go egahne alum, afi fere jolo ejahbe, tahmen edi jio, wahn kum ebtohko go egahne akpade.\f + \fr 10:14 \ft Elt 13:51\f*
\v 15 Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Go efung elam, elam ji ejahbe jio bahke bibi sehnge ji Sodom, a Gomorra.\f + \fr 10:15 \ft Mat 11:24\f*
\s1 Ebnohko bi kpꞌbake
\r (Mak 13:9-13; Luk 12:11-12)
\p 
\v 16 “Anv, n kp-n tumu ana ejoro tv go ellong abi enyam. Jo bangen ana enyo, wahn fere jol ana mbehl nyi kil jo lim ebi ejum ajehng ajehng.\f + \fr 10:16 \ft Rom 16:19\f*
\v 17 Jo gberen! Tibre ane bahk-n jo kak go esub, fere jo dv-n go bo a ntahk ero.
\p 
\v 18 “Bo bahke jo ko-n, song yiimi go esamahr atubesi, a atul tib go egame esi. Nsol nyia nyi bahk-n jo lim, eji ń lꞌjo yiim-m ntianse go bo esamahr, a esamahr ane bako ba ki nyi Esowo.\f + \fr 10:18 \ft Elt 25:23; 27:24\f*
\v 19 Bo lꞌkak-n go esub, kana jo tiiri bada nsol nyi ḿ bahke bungu, jol ana ḿ bahke bꞌbung. Tibre ngare nyio bo bahk-n kake alum nya ḿ bahke bungu.
\v 20 Tibre alum nya ḿ bahke bungu, nyanyahne sang, bahke lohngo goji Etohko ji Nso ejahne ji kpꞌbungu go egahne atahng.\f + \fr 10:20 \ft Elt 4:8,13\f*
\p 
\v 21 “Abonanyehn nne bahke jo yake abonanyehn ka re bo wul. Babnde nne bahke tob jo yake abon ebo ka re bo wul. Abon bahke jo kpiidi kuumu babnde, jo jabbe bo ka, bo wul.
\v 22 Nne awohng awohng bahke jo ko-n ekv tib go egama mbing. Nne no lꞌkpuumu tete rehng go esꞌkohro, ye wo bahke bele eltahre.
\p 
\v 23 “Bo lꞌnohk-n go ejahbe jehko, been, song ejahbe jehko. Tibre etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Ń nehm ma tiki lim eltum go ajahbe Israel kpee mal, tete Mmon no nne feere ba.
\p 
\v 24 “Nne no kpꞌkpili kpehme gbal sehnge ntꞌtibi ewe. Nlokeltum kpehme gbal sehnge nde.\f + \fr 10:24 \ft Luk 6:40\f*
\v 25 Nobo re nne no kpꞌkpili tob taame go eyebatahng jol ana ntꞌtibi ewe. Nobo re nlokeltum taame, jol ana nde. Nfontahk, bo lꞌlung-e re ntul a nnehm, bahke limi renan, bo kꞌtob lung ane ebe ano?\f + \fr 10:25 \ft Jon 15:20\f*
\s1 Nne awo fuumu re nne fahl-e?
\r (Luk 12:2-7)
\p 
\v 26 “Kana jo fahl ane! Ejum ajehng ajehng limm, ji bo bulu no, ji Esowo lꞌkꞌlennge. Ejum ajehng ajehng limm, ji bo behre no, ji ane lꞌkꞌkahn.\f + \fr 10:26 \ft Rom 2:16\f*
\v 27 Ejum ji n kp-n tongo a mbehr mbehr, ḿ bahke bungu gbul gbul gbuul. Ji m bungu go awꞌwa tong-n, ḿ bahke bungu go elkab ane.
\p 
\v 28 “Kana jo fahl ane ba kpo wul ngubjing, ba lꞌkꞌma wul etohko. Fahlen ye jio ji bahke ma rannge etohko, a ngubjing go ellulagun.\f + \fr 10:28 \ft Jems 4:12\f*
\v 29 Nne li ma gunu nruk ebal go are, ka mpene. Abehng abehng limm, bi bahke gboko go ndi, sehngem re no, Nso ejahne taame na.
\v 30 Wahn, alv enyahne kpee nya li go egahne asi, bobfange.
\v 31 Kana kpe fahl! Wahn ba ga lub sehnge nruk gbalee.
\s1 Ana nne bahke jo yiimi ntianse ka Jisos
\r (Luk 12:8-9)
\p 
\v 32 “Fvfo, nne awohng awohng no lꞌyiimi ntianse ka-m go esamahr ane, ye wo fvfo, m bahke tob yiimi ntianse ka-e go esamahr bi Nsoo no li go ejahbetul.
\v 33 Nne awohng awohng no lꞌten-m go esamahr ane, ye wo fvfo, m bahk-e tob ten go esamahr bi Nsoo no li go ejahbetul.
\s1 Elkoono sang, ekahngkahng bi
\r (Luk 12:51-53; 14:26-27)
\p 
\v 34 “Kana tir re, n ko elkoono ba a ni go njini nyia.\f + \fr 10:34 \ft Jon 14:27\f* M baam re me n ko elkoono ba a ni, m ba re me n ko ekahngkahng ba a bi.\f + \fr 10:34 \ft Hib 4:12\f*
\v 35 M ba re ‘mmon fere kpiidi kuumu nde, mmon no nkal kpiidi kuumu nnyehn, nkal a nne kpiidi kuumu nnyehn nlum.
\v 36 Nne, ane ebe ba bahke fere jol anebekv ebe.’
\v 37 Nne no nde, afi jolo nnyehn, bo lꞌkor-e sehnge me, á fuumem a name. Nne no abon ebe lꞌkor-e sehnge me, á fuumem a name.\f + \fr 10:37 \ft Luk 14:26\f*
\v 38 Nne awohng awohng no tohko rod ekros eje, tahm toon-m, á fuumem a name.
\v 39 Nne no lꞌgare re á tahre elkpin ene, á bahke tane na elkpin ene. Nne no lꞌtane elkpin ene tib go egame esi, á bahke tahre na elkpin ene.\f + \fr 10:39 \ft Jon 12:25\f*
\s1 Eltuuru
\r (Mak 9:41)
\p 
\v 40 “Nne no lꞌvvr-n, á vvrv me. Nne no lꞌvvr-m, á tob vvrv nne no tum-m no.
\v 41 Nne no lꞌvvrv nnyehnamahr, tib eji á kahne re nnyehnamahr Esowo wo, á bahke bele eltuuru ana ni nnyehnamahr kpo bel. Nne no lꞌvvrv etingitingi nne tib á li go etingitingi, á bahke bele eltuuru ana ni etingitingi nne kpo bel.
\v 42 Nne awohng awohng no lꞌka nne awohng go ellong abonse baa abon alahb re á wo, tib eji á kpꞌkahne re, ntꞌtoono ewame wo, á bahke bele eltuuru go etingitingi.”\f + \fr 10:42 \ft Mat 25:40\f*
\c 11
\s1 Ane ba Jon ji nwohngalahb tumu no
\r (Luk 7:18-35)
\p 
\v 1 Eji Jisos tubu abatꞌtoono ebe, ewubu ane abal, elle mal, á kehm tahme edi jio, song rehng go ajahbe Jus, jo bung alum Esowo, fere jo tib ane.
\v 2 Eji Jon ji nwohngalahb ji woomo go ngbekobo wuku bada nsol nyi Kraist kpꞌlimi, á kehm yehke abatꞌtoono ebe tum tv-e.
\v 3 Bo kehm song bahb-e re, “Wo wo li nne no Jon tongo re á kpꞌbaka, afi wahr ji sik nne nondiki?”
\p 
\v 4 Owo Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Feeren song goji Jon, wahn song tong-e bada nsol nyi ń kpꞌnyehne a, fere kpꞌwuku,
\v 5 ana awakamahr kpꞌnyehne, abanne kpꞌtahme jen, aneb abili kpꞌnobo, alakatung kpꞌwuku, akvne kpꞌnyahme go elkv, akpak, bo kpꞌtiingi bo nnoobo etib.
\v 6 Eyebatahng li ka nne no lꞌki-m sel gbo.”
\p 
\v 7 Eji abatꞌtoono Jon ma feere fi, Jisos kehm bahbe ellong ane bao bada Jon re, “Elka emahng, eji ń jo je goji Jon, ń jo je re wahn song nyehn jen? Eljele ni nfeb kpꞌlimi kpꞌneenga?
\v 8 Anv, ejum aji ń jo jꞌje re wahn song nyehn abee? Nne no ma liibi nsol nyi nno a nnoa? Ane ba kpo liibi ano kpo jol go ntahk nyi atul.
\v 9 Anv, ejum aji ń jo jꞌje o, jo song nyehn? Nnyehnamahr woa? N kp-n tongo re, Wahn ebnyehn nne no gbale sehnge nnyehnamahr.\f + \fr 11:9 \ft Luk 1:76\f*
\v 10 Tibre Jon wo li nne no bo nyono go nwer Esowo bada ne re, ‘M bahke tumu ntiingetib ewame, á gbo-a mbang, song tuungu mbang bum-a.’
\p 
\v 11 “Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, nnene limm, no ma jꞌjol go njini nyia no gbale sehnge Jon ji nwohngalahb. Nne no ga rede go ellong ane ba bahke lehke etul bi Esowo, á gbale sehnge Jon.\f + \fr 11:11 \ft Hib 3:5-6; Mat 13:17\f*
\v 12 Bomo ngare nyi Jon ji nwohngalahb tete rehng anv, etul bi Esowo li go elkake nsahm kehm kuumu, aneb nsahm bahke kuumu go eko akake.\f + \fr 11:12 \ft Luk 16:16; Mak 7:26-30; Luk 18:5\f*
\v 13 Atahm nya Moses, a abanyehnamahr Esowo kpee tete ba rehng ngare nyi Jon bungu bade etul bia.
\v 14 Lꞌkor-n taamen tv alum nyaa, nya li re, Jon wo li Elaija, ji bo bungu re á kpꞌbake.\f + \fr 11:14 \ft Mat 17:10-13\f*
\v 15 Nne no kpi atung, nong, á wuk.
\p 
\v 16 “Anv, m bahke koko ane ba li anv gara jen? Bo li ana abonse ba ma lohng elatahkgur kpi mbene lim. Egom jindiki tong egom jehko re,
\q1 
\v 17 “ ‘Wahr ebwor afiri ka-n,
\q1 ḿ bahnem.
\q1 Wahr ebling aling,
\q1 wahn tobem ling fvfo.’
\p 
\v 18 “Eji Jon ba no, á jo kono elne njal bade, amahm á joom wo. Ane re, á kpi ebi etohko go ege atahng.
\v 19 Eji Mmon no nne ba no, á jo li nsol, fere jo wꞌwo, ane jo bungu re, ‘Nyehnen nlehke ebno noa, no kpo wo amahm, á li ntem no abakokatak, a aneb abꞌbi!’ Nne lꞌkpur nsol nyi aneb elkahne kpo lim, owo á bahke tob kahn ana elkahne li no.”
\s1 Ajahbe nya ki taame
\r (Luk 10:13-15)
\p 
\v 20 Jisos kehm kehme ajahbe nya á ma ga lim akpokosi gbalee ebi ka, tibre bo ka gbo ndon.
\p 
\v 21 “Eyuu a nahne, aneb Korasin! Eyuu a nahne, aneb Betsaida! Li re Taya, a Saidon nyehne agburu akpokosi ana nya wahn ma nyehn a, kehn bo jol gboko ndon wuku wuku, fere kak ajakensol, kpu atong, kak esi.\f + \fr 11:21 \ft Mak 8:22-25\f*
\v 22 Wo, n kp-n tongo re, Efung elam bio, elam nehm ga bib a bo ana bahke bibi a nahne.
\p 
\v 23 “Wahn aneb Kapenium, bo ma-n mehl wahre rehng go ejahbetul Esowo.\f + \fr 11:23 \ft Mat 4:13; 8:5-17\f* Bo bahke fere rod-n, ro kak go ellulagun. Li re aneb Sodom nyehne agburu akpokosi ana nya ḿ ma nyehn a, kehn bo baa, kpeke li tete sik anv.\f + \fr 11:23 \ft Mat 10:15\f*
\v 24 Owo n kp-n tongo re, Efung elam bio, elam nehm ga bib a Sodom ana bahke bibi a nahne.”\f + \fr 11:24 \ft Luk 12:48\f*
\s1 Baan go egame, wahn ba bel erekekv
\r (Luk 10:21-22)
\p 
\v 25 Ngare nyio Jisos kehm bungu re, “Nsoo, wo wo li Ntul go ero, a ndi. N kp-a tehke, tib eji a ma lennge abonbili nsol nyia nyi a behre re akahnkahn ane, a anebkul kꞌnyehn.\f + \fr 11:25 \ft 1 Kor 1:26-29; 2 Kor 4:3\f*
\v 26 Tibre kor-a na re wo lim ano, Nsoo.
\p 
\v 27 “Nsoo ebyake ejum ajehng ajehng kak go egame abo.\f + \fr 11:27 \ft Mat 28:18\f* Nnene limm, no kpꞌkahne Mmon, sehngem Nde ntahngtahng wo kp-e kahne. Nnene limm, no kpꞌkahne Nde, sehngem Mmon ntahngtahng wo kp-e kahne, a nne awohng awohng no Mmon kpꞌsebe re á lennge Nde tib-e.
\p 
\v 28 “Baan go egame, wahn ane kpee ba ma lahng go elsolo nsol nyi kpꞌlubu. M bahk-n kake erekekv.\f + \fr 11:28 \ft Hib 4:10-11\f*
\v 29 Taamen, wahn woom-m go elwo, fere jo kpili go egame. Tibre me n li soom, fere jol reed. Owo atohko enyahne bahke bele erekekv.
\v 30 Tibre eltum ename riidem. Elsol ename ni m bahk-n sehke kpꞌyaare.”\f + \fr 11:30 \ft 1 Jon 5:3\f*
\c 12
\s1 Mbahbe nyi li bade efung Esabat
\r (Mak 2:23-28; Luk 6:1-5)
\p 
\v 1 Ngare nyio eji Jisos jo jen go mbang egbe efung Esabat, abatꞌtoono ebe njal yꞌyam bo. Bo kehm kehme amohk nkohl monngo tv go arahn, jo li.
\p 
\v 2 Eji Bab Farisi nyehne ano, bo kehm tongo Jisos re, “Nyehn ana abatꞌtoono eba kpꞌlimi ejum ji ki fuumu re nne lim efung Esabat!”
\p 
\v 3 Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Ń ka lung a lung bade ana Devid njal yam-e no, a ane ebea?
\v 4 Á song yele ekpꞌkpa Esowo, song li abred nya bo limi no bum go ekpꞌkpa Esowo jio, nya ki tohko fꞌfuumu re á li, a ane ebe, sehngem abalimajom ba ba fuumu re bo jo li.
\v 5 Ń ka lung a lung go atahm nya Moses re, efung Esabat abehng abehng abalimajom ba kpo lim eltum go etahk Esowo kpo sꞌsoodo ntahm nyi Esabat, jol ntahm nyio bo joom gbo.
\p 
\v 6 “N kp-n tongo re, Ejum jia, ji gbale sehnge etahk Esowo.\f + \fr 12:6 \ft Jon 2:21\f*
\v 7 Li re ń kpꞌkahne ana edi nwer Esowo jia lohngo no, ji bungu re, ‘Njom sang n kpꞌsebe, ndon nyi’, kehn ń kpehme ka ane ba ki gbo ntahm ebi.\f + \fr 12:7 \ft Mat 9:13\f*
\v 8 Tibre Mmon no nne tob li nfono Esabat.”
\s1 Nne no ebo ebe lohngo no
\r (Mak 3:1-6; Luk 6:6-11)
\p 
\v 9 Jisos kehm tahme edi jio, song rehng go etahk ero ajehng.
\v 10 Nne jolo o, no ebo ebe lohngo no. Bo kehm bahbe Jisos re, “Anv, nꞌnob re nne lim ane, bo nob ayam ebo efung Esabata?” Tibre bo jo sebe ejum ji bo bahke koko ka Jisos ebi.
\p 
\v 11 Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Anv, nne awohng ewahne lꞌbel njoro, njoro nyio lꞌfere gbo yel go elbing efung Esabat, á nehm song yehk-ea?
\v 12 Anv, nne sang ga gbal sehnge njora? Ano wo wahng ka atahm enyahre bungu re, nne jo lim nnoobo efung Esabat.”
\p 
\v 13 Owo á kehm tongo nne noo re, “Tanne ebo eba!” Á kehm tanne ebo, ebo fere feere ana wuku wuku, nob kpee ana ebo behko.
\p 
\v 14 Bab Farisi kehm soro tahm, song lam kak-e, ana bo bahk-e wulu.\f + \fr 12:14 \ft Jon 5:16\f*
\p 
\v 15 Eji Jisos sebe ano kahn, á kehm tahme eje. Ane gbalee kehm tahme toon-e. Á limi bo kpee, bo nob ayam ebo.
\v 16 Á tongo bo re, bo kꞌtooro tong ane bako bada ne,
\v 17 eji lꞌlohko jol ana Esowo bungu sehng go nnyo mi nnyehnamahr Aisaya re,
\q1 
\v 18 “Nyehnee, a wo li nlokeltum ewame no m ma yehke.
\q1 Akor-m ejame ji kpo kor-m sꞌsehng.
\q1 M bahk-e kake etohko ejame.
\q1 Á bahke jo tiingi ane baka baka elam ejame.
\q1 
\v 19 Á nehm jo taange ntaange, fere jo rabe.
\q1 Bo nehm jo wuk ewok eje go nla ejahbe.
\q1 
\v 20 Eljele ni ma bahne, á nehm wob.
\q1 Etꞌrekahng ji kpꞌrede ellulu,
\q1 á nehm lahme,\f + \fr 12:20 \ft Mak 2:17\f*
\q1 tete etingitingi ba ko nji.
\q1 
\v 21 Go ege a mbing wo ane baka baka bahke jo kunu ekpu.”\f + \fr 12:21 \ft Mat 8:11\f*
\s1 Jisos abola ntul a nnehm
\r (Mak 3:20-30; Luk 11:14-23)
\p 
\v 22 Ane bandiki kehm koko nwakamahr nyi ki jo ma bung, ba a ne, nyi bele ebi etohko go ege atahng. Jisos kehm limi nne noo, á nyehn, fere bung.
\p 
\v 23 Ellong ane bao kehm kpoko bo esi. Bo kehm bungu re, “Anv, mmon a Devid wo aa?”
\p 
\v 24 Bab Farisi wuku kan a me, bo kehm bungu re, “Á kpo kam ane abi atohko yehke tib go nsahm nyi Belsebul, ntul a nnehm ka-e no.”
\p 
\v 25 Jisos kꞌkahn ntir atahng ebo, kehm tongo bo re, “Ejahbe ajehng ajehng ji lꞌyab, jol ebo ebo, bahke tane na. Nfam anyehng anyehng nyi lꞌyab, jol ebo ebo, afi fere jol nlaaga, nehm yiimi.
\v 26 Nnehm lꞌkam nnehm yake go, lohngo re eblehm ebyab. Ejahbetul eje bahke yiimi renan?
\p 
\v 27 “Lꞌfere jol re, n kpo kam ane abi atohko yehke go nsahm nyi ntul a nnehm, anv abon ebahne kpo kam bo yehke go nsahm anyii?\f + \fr 12:27 \ft Luk 9:49; Elt 19:13\f* Owo wahng ka bo bahke jolo ane ba bahk-n lame.
\v 28 N kpo kam ane abi atohko yehke go nsahm nyi etohko ji Esowo, eblohng re, Esowo ebbadde ba go egahne, a etul etul ebe.\f + \fr 12:28 \ft 1 Jon 3:8\f*
\v 29 Nnene limm, no bahke ma wa etahk etahntahn nne yel, song kpu nsol enye tahm a nyi, sehngem re no, á tohko gbo mbang gba etahntahn nne jio alehke, á kehm ma yel, song kpu nsol enye.
\p 
\v 30 “Nne no ki li ka me, á li nnekv ewame. Nne no tohk-m tob elkpiimi, no lun á kpꞌfare na faade.
\v 31 Owo wahnge n kp-n tongo re, ane bahke ma bel eltahmeka go bo abiafem anyehng anyehng nya bo limi no, a ebꞌbi ajehng ajehng ji bo bungu no, sehngem abꞌbi nya bo kpo bung bade Etingi Etohko, nya nya bo lꞌkꞌtiki bel eltahmeka.\f + \fr 12:31 \ft Jon 16:7-9; 1 Tim 1:13\f*
\v 32 Nne awohng awohng no lꞌbung ebꞌbi bada Mmon no nne, á bahke bele eltahmeka. Nne awohng awohng no lꞌbung ebꞌbi bade Etingi Etohko, á nehm bel eltahmeka, jol eying jia ji anv, afi fere jol eying ji kpꞌbake.
\s1 Eti, a akab enye
\r (Luk 6:43-45)
\p 
\v 33 “Re wahn kehm jo bong anoobo akab nti, lohngo re ḿ bahke bahme na nnoobo eti. Ń lꞌbahm ebi eti, ḿ bahke bongo abi akab. Tibre go akab nya kabe no nya, bo bahke liingi eti jio.
\v 34 Wahn ane ba li ana akumbad ba! Ḿ bahke ma bung anoobo nsol renan, eji ń li abꞌbi abꞌbi? Tibre nsol nyi ma rur nne go ege eltim, nyi nyi nne kpo bung go ege a nnyo.
\v 35 Nnooba nne kpo yehke anoobo nsol nya wob-e go ege atahng. Ebi nne kpo yehke abi nsol nya wob-e go ege atahng.
\v 36 N kp-n tongo re, Efung elam bio, nne awohng awohng, Esowo bahk-e bahbe bade ellum anehng anehng ni á bungu no, ni ki lohng ejumjum.\f + \fr 12:36 \ft Jems 1:19; Ef 5:4\f*
\v 37 Tibre Esowo bahke koko alum enya nya a bungu no, lam-a.\f + \fr 12:37 \ft Luk 19:22\f* Fundiki a bahke lehke eno. Fundiki a bahke lehke ebi.”
\s1 Ana bo sebe re bo nyehn nkpokosi
\r (Mak 8:11-12; Luk 11:29-32)
\p 
\v 38 Egom Farisi, a atꞌtibi ba atahm bandiki kehm tongo Jisos re, “Ntꞌtibi, e kpꞌsebe re wo lim nkpokosi, wahr nyehn.”\f + \fr 12:38 \ft Mat 16:1; 1 Kor 1:22\f*
\p 
\v 39 Á kehm faange bo re, “Abi ane ba li anv, ba ma sennge Esowo njahm kpꞌsebe re bo nyehn nkpokosi. Jol nkpokosi anyehng anyehng bo nehm nyehn, sehngem nkpokosi ana nyi nnyehnamahr a Jona nyi nyi bo bahke nyehne.
\v 40 Tibre, ana Jona kange ala nnyam alahb nfung era, ano wo fvfo Mmon no nne bahke tob kang atahng ndi nfung era.\f + \fr 12:40 \ft Rom 1:4\f*
\p 
\v 41 “Go efung elam bio, aneb Ninive bahke mehle yiimi, ka ane ba li anv ebi. Tibre bo gbꞌgbo ndon go bo abiafem, eji bo wuku alum Esowo nya Jona bungu no.\f + \fr 12:41 \ft Mat 11:20-24\f* Nyehnen ga, a wo li nne no ga gbal sehnge Jona.
\v 42 Go efung elam bio, ntul a nnenkal no Seba bahke mehle yiimi, ka ane ba li anv ebi. Tibre á lohngo nlaabambang ejahbe ba goji Solomon re á ba wuk elkahne ene. Nyehnen ga, a wo li nne no ga gbal sehnge Solomon.\f + \fr 12:42 \ft Mat 12:6\f*
\s1 Ana ebi etohko kpo feere, ba yel nne
\r (Luk 11:24-26)
\p 
\v 43 “Ebi etohko lꞌlohng nne, á kpo yannge go adi nya kpꞌwaange, jo seb edi ji á bahke reke ekv, á nehm tiki ting.\f + \fr 12:43 \ft 2 Pit 2:17\f*
\v 44 Owo ebi etohko jio bahke kehm bungu re, ‘M bahke feere go etahk ji n lohng no abake.’ Á lꞌfeere song nyehn etahk jio, li nehme nehme, bo ma feenge kpee, tuungu kpee bum,
\v 45 owo á bahke tahme, song ko atohko nyako na asehma ba a nya, nya sahb bꞌbib sehnge ye. Bo feere ba lene etahk jio. Nne noo bahke kpe sab na sehnge ana wuku wuku. Ano wo fvfo bahke tob jol ka abi ane ba li anv.”\f + \fr 12:45 \ft 2 Pit 2:20\f*
\s1 Nnyehn Jisos, a abonanyehn Jisos
\r (Mak 3:31-35; Luk 8:19-21)
\p 
\v 46 Ngare nyi Jisos kpi mbungu mbungu a ane bao, nnyehn kehm lohngo ba, a abonanyehn.\f + \fr 12:46 \ft Mat 13:55\f* Bo yiimi go elatahk, jo seb re bo bung a ne.
\v 47 Owo nne awohng kehm tongo Jisos re, “Nyehnee, nne, a abonane yim go elatahk kpꞌsebe re bo bung a na.”\f + \fr 12:47 \ft Luk 2:49\f*
\p 
\v 48 Jisos kehm faange nne no tong-e no re, “Nne awo li nnee? Ane aba li abonanee?”
\v 49 Á kehm tono ebo tv abatꞌtoono ebe, kehm bungu re, “A wo li nnee. A wo li abonanee.\f + \fr 12:49 \ft Jon 7:5\f*
\v 50 Tibre nne awohng awohng no lꞌlim ji Nsoo no li go ero kpꞌsebe re á lim, ye wo li mmonannee, a nnee.”\f + \fr 12:50 \ft Rom 8:29\f*
\c 13
\s1 Elgan ni li bada mbahmgbe
\r (Mak 4:1-9; Luk 8:4-8)
\p 
\v 1 Efung bꞌnehm ona, Jisos kehm mehle go etahk, song ji go nkpe eto.
\v 2 Eji ellong ane gbalee ba go ege, owo á kehm yele go egbang, song ji. Ane bao kpee yiimi go nkpe egbuk.
\p 
\v 3 Á ko ngaane, jo tong bo nsol gbalee re, “Nne jolo gona, no tahme no, song wohngo amohk nti enye go ege egbe.
\v 4 Eji á jo wohngo, nyandiki gbo noongo go mbang. Nruk ba suudu kpee mele.
\p 
\v 5 “Nyandiki gbo noongo go ndi nyi jolo atal atal. Abon ndi jolo ntiil. Amohk nti nyao gulu elmahnge. Tibre edi jio ndi gbalem.
\v 6 Njul nyaare kan a me, akohdo nti nyao wuudu, fere kpo. Tibre alohk jolem.
\p 
\v 7 “Nyandiki gbo kuumu go elkob akpiri. Akpiri nyao gbale, bulu akohdo nti nyao.
\p 
\v 8 “Amohk nti nyako gbo noongo go nnooba ndi, kab akab. Atasok nyandiki jo jolo nkab atahl alon alon, atasok nyandiki nkab atahl ara ara, atasok nyandiki eltahl a nkab ewubu eltahl a nkab ewubu.
\p 
\v 9 “Nne no kpi atung, nong, á wuk!”\f + \fr 13:9 \ft Mat 13:18-23\f*
\s1 Ji wahnge Jisos jo tꞌtuubu ngaane
\r (Mak 4:10-12; Luk 8:9-10)
\p 
\v 10 Owo abatꞌtoono Jisos kehm bake go ege, ba bahb-e re, “Jen ji wahnge a kpo ko ngaane, jo bung a bo?”
\p 
\v 11 Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Bo ma-n ka elkahne nio ni etul bi Esowo, bi Esowo behre no. Ane bao, bo kaam bo.
\v 12 Nne no kpi no, bo bahk-e budu na, á bel gbalee. Nne no ki kpi, bo bahk-e taare na ji á kpi no.\f + \fr 13:12 \ft Mat 25:28\f*
\v 13 Owo wahng ka n kpo bung a bo go ngaane. Tibre bo kpo seenge, jol bo kpehme nyehn. Bo kpo wuungu atung, jol bo kpehme wuk, fere kahn.
\m 
\v 14 Bo ba li ane ba nnyehnamahr Aisaya bungu no bada bo re,
\q1 “ ‘Ḿ bahke wuungu na wuungu wuungu atung,
\q1 ń nehm tiki kahn.
\q1 Ḿ bahke seenge na seenge seenge,
\q1 ń nehm tiki nyehn.
\q1 
\v 15 Tibre asi ane bao ebfere tahne.
\q1 Bobsahde atung ebo.
\q1 Bobbulu amahr ebo.
\q1 Ki li ano, kehn, bo kpꞌnyehne, fere wuk,
\q1 fere kꞌkahn go bo a ntim, fere sennge,
\q1 feere go egame, eji n lꞌlim bo, bo nob.’\f + \fr 13:15 \ft 2 Tes 2:11-12\f*
\m 
\v 16 Elfuulu li ka amahr enyahne, eji kpꞌnyehne. Elfuulu li ka atung enyahne, eji kpꞌwuku.
\v 17 Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Abanyehnamahr gbalee, a aneb Esowo gbalee jo sebe re bo nyehn ji ń kpꞌnyehne a. Jol bo tikem nyehn. Bo jo sebe re bo wuk ji ń kpꞌwuku a. Jol bo tikem wuk.\f + \fr 13:17 \ft Luk 10:23-24\f*
\s1 Ana Jisos lennge elgan ni li bada mbahmgbe
\r (Mak 4:13-20; Luk 8:11-15)
\p 
\v 18 “Wuungen atung anv, wahn kahn ana elgan ni li bada mbahmgbe lohngo no.
\p 
\v 19 “Ane ba lꞌwuk alum nya etul bi Esowo, kꞌkahn ana lohngo no, Ebinne bahke bake, ba yehke nsol nyi bo ma bahm go bo a ntim tahm a nyi. Nyao nya li amohk nti nya gbo noongo go mbang.
\p 
\v 20 “Ane bandiki li ana amohk nti nya gbo noongo go ndi nyi jolo atal atal. Bo lꞌwuk alum Esowo nyao o, bo ko tvtv a eyebatahng.
\v 21 Eji bo ki kpi alohk, bo kpehme kang. Erem lꞌba, a ntong tib go alum Esowo nya bo wuku no, bo soro gbo tvtv.
\p 
\v 22 “Ane bandiki li ana amohk nti nya fooro gbo go elkob akpiri. Bo kpꞌwuku alum Esowo, wo, nsol nyi njini nyia kpo gbiingi bo go bo a ntim. Ekor akpohko kpo nehm bo.\f + \fr 13:22 \ft 1 Tim 6:9\f* Nsol nyia kpee kpo bulu alum Esowo nyao tv. Akab bo nehm kab.
\p 
\v 23 “Ane bako li ana amohk nti nya bo wohngo go nnooba ndi.\f + \fr 13:23 \ft Elt 17:11\f* Bo lꞌwuk alum Esowo kahn, bo lohko kab akab, egom jindiki nkab atahl alon alon, egom jindiki nkab atahl ara ara, egom jindiki eltahl a nkab ewubu eltahl a nkab ewubu.”\f + \fr 13:23 \ft Gal 5:22\f*
\s1 Elgan ni li bade agasame
\p 
\v 24 Jisos kehm kpe tub bo elgan nehko re, “Etul bi Esowo li ana nne no tahme song kak nkohl go ege egbe.
\v 25 Eji ane ma lal, nnekv ewe kehm tahme song wohngo afem agasame semme go nkohl nyio, tahm eje.
\v 26 Eji nkohl ma mahng, gbal, fere lake abon, agasame kehm tob mahng.
\v 27 Owo alokeltum ba nfono egbe noo kehm ba bahb-e re, ‘Nsoo, nkohl sang a kake go ega egbea? Anv, agasame nyao lohngo gan ba?’
\v 28 Owo á kehm tongo bo re, ‘Nnekv wo ma lim ejum jio.’ Alokeltum bao kehm-e bahbe re, ‘Anv, a kpꞌsebe re wahr song wooba?’
\v 29 Á kehm tene re, ‘Eꞌee, ń lꞌsong woobo agasame, ḿ bahke woobo nkohl semme.
\v 30 Nong, nsol ebal ebal gbal ano tete rehng go efung elbanne. Owo m bahke tongo ababꞌbanne re, Gboon mbang, wahn tohko woobo agasame, gba agan agan, eji bo lꞌjahm fi, wahn kehm banne nkohl kanne, kpu song kpake go egame etahk.’ ”\f + \fr 13:30 \ft Mat 13:37-43\f*
\s1 Elgan ni li bada mmohk asia
\r (Mak 4:30-32; Luk 13:18-19)
\p 
\v 31 Jisos kehm kpe tub bo elgan nehko re, “Etul bi Esowo li ana mmohk asia nyi nne ko no, song bahm go ege etahngga.
\v 32 Se sehnge mmohk eti anyehng anyehng.\f + \fr 13:32 \ft Fil 2:8\f* Eji gbale no, gbale sehnge eti ajehng ajehng ji bo kpo bahm etahngga.\f + \fr 13:32 \ft Jon 12:24\f* Owo nruk kehm bake, ba si ntahk o.”\f + \fr 13:32 \ft Elt 20:29-30; Mat 13:30\f*
\s1 Elgan nyi li bade ayist
\r (Luk 13:20-21)
\p 
\v 33 Jisos kehm kpe tub bo elgan nehko re, “Etul bi Esowo li ana ayist,\f + \fr 13:33 \ft Mak 8:15; 1 Kor 5:6-8\f* nya nnenkal ko song behr go ebam aflawa na ebra tete semme kpee, fere tung.”\f + \fr 13:33 \ft Mat 13:30\f*
\s1 Ana Jisos lennge elgan ni li bade agasame
\r (Mak 4:33-34)
\p 
\v 34 Nsol nyia kpee, Jisos jo bungu go ngaane, tong ellong ane. Á joom tiki bung na bung, kꞌbung go elgan,
\v 35 eji lꞌlohko jol ana nnyehnamahr bungu no re,
\q1 “M bahke jo bung a bo go ngaane.
\q1 M bahke tongo bo nsol nyi Esowo behre no ngare nyi njini bomo no.”
\p 
\v 36 Jisos kehm tahme ellong ane bao sa, song yel ekpꞌkpa. Abatꞌtoono ebe kehm bake go ege, ba bahb-e re, “Tong-r ana elgan ni li bade agasame lohngo no.”
\p 
\v 37 Owo Jisos kehm faange re, “Nne no kake nkohl, Mmon no nne wo.
\v 38 Edi egbe jio, njini nyi. Nkohl nyio, abon Ntul ba. Agasame nyao, abon ba Ebinne jio ba.
\v 39 Nnekv no wohngo afem agasame, nnehm nyi. Ngare elbanne nyio, esꞌkohro eying jia ji. Ababꞌbanne bao, babenjel ba.
\p 
\v 40 “Ana bo bahke kpuku agasame nyao, jamme fi, ano wo bahke jolo esꞌkohro eying jia.
\v 41 Owo Mmon no nne bahke tumu enjel enye,\f + \fr 13:41 \ft Mat 25:31-46\f* bo bahke yannge go ege ejahbetul, kpu ane kpee ba jo wahng re ane jo lim abiafem, a aneb abꞌbi,
\v 42 ro bo, kak go agun. Owo bo bahke woomo, jo ling, fere jo kono amahn.
\v 43 Aneb Esowo bahke jo ya ana njul go ejahbetul ji Nde ebo.
\p “Nne no kpi atung, nong, á wuk.
\s1 Elgan ni li bade elkohl akpohko
\p 
\v 44 “Etul bi Esowo tob li ana elkohl akpohko ni bo behre edi egbe.\f + \fr 13:44 \ft 1 Pit 1:7; Kol 3:3\f* Nne awohng kehm song nyehn, tuungu behr. Á bele eyebatahng sehng, kehm song gungu nsol enye kpee nyi á bele no,\f + \fr 13:44 \ft Fil 2:6-8\f* fere ba gunu edi egbe jio.\f + \fr 13:44 \ft Ell 5:9\f*
\s1 Elgan ni li bada mmohkesol
\p 
\v 45 “Etul bi Esowo tob li ana njenare no jo seb anoobo amohkesol.
\v 46 Eji á nyehne anyehng nyi sahb kꞌkim ekun, fere nꞌnob, owo á kehm soro tahm, song gungu nsol enye kpee, nyi á bele no, fere ba gunu mmohkesol nyio.
\s1 Elgan ni li bade erim
\p 
\v 47 “Etul bi Esowo tob li ana erim bi bo ma kak go aya, fere bob nsahre go nkohn a nkohn.\f + \fr 13:47 \ft Mat 22:9-10\f*
\v 48 Eji nsahre ma rur, bo kehm tohngo, bum egbuk.\f + \fr 13:48 \ft Mat 24:14\f* Owo bo kehm jehke, kehm kehme nsahre jak. Nyi nno, bo jo kake go ajeere. Abi nsahre, bo ro go.
\v 49 Ano wo bahke jolo go esꞌkohro eying jia. Babenjel bahke bake, ba jak abi ane go ellong anoobo ane,
\v 50 fere ro bo kak agun. Owo bo bahke woomo, jo ling, fere jo kono amahn.”\f + \fr 13:50 \ft Elt 10:35; 1 Kor 6:9-11\f*
\s1 Akꞌkulu nsol, a nsol nfenfe
\p 
\v 51 Jisos kehm bahbe bo re, “Anv, nsol nyia lenng-n lennga?” Owo bo kehm-e faange re, “Ee nsoo.”
\v 52 Á kehm tongo bo re, “Owo wahnge ntꞌtibi no atahm awohng awohng no ma jol ntꞌtoono Esowo, no ma kpili bade etul bi Esowo, á li ana nfontahk no kpo yehke nsol afang enye go elkohl, nyindiki nsol nfenfe,\f + \fr 13:52 \ft Jon 13:34\f* nyindiki akꞌkulu nsol.”\f + \fr 13:52 \ft 1 Tim 1:8; Rom 7:12,14\f*
\s1 Ana bo tene Jisos go Nasaret
\r (Mak 6:1-6; Luk 4:16-30)
\p 
\v 53 Eji Jisos tuubu ngaane nyio kpee mal, owo á kehm tahme edi jio,
\v 54 song rehng go ege ejahbe, song kehme bo tib go bo etahk ero.
\p Ane ba wuk-e no, jo kpo bo esi sehng, bo kehm bahbe re, “Gan wo á bele elkohn elkahne ana nia, a nsahm nyi á kpo ko lim agburu akpokosi nyaa?\f + \fr 13:54 \ft Jon 7:15\f*
\v 55 Ye sang li mmon a kapentaa? Nnyehn sang bo kpo lung-e re Meria? Abonanyehn sang bo kpo lung bo re Jems, Joses, Saimon a Judasa?
\v 56 Abonanyehn ba nkal sang li a nahre a kpeea? Anv, gan wo á bele bel nsol nyio kpee?”
\v 57 Owo bo kehm-e tene.
\p Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Nnyehnamahr, bo kpo kak-e edi ajehng ajehng, sehngem ane ebe, a ejahbe eje ji kil jo kak-e.”\f + \fr 13:57 \ft Jon 4:44\f*
\p 
\v 58 Á limem akpokosi gbalee ejahbe jio tib go bo ekꞌtaame.
\c 14
\s1 Ana Jon ji nwohngalahb kpo no
\r (Mak 6:14-29; Luk 9:7-9)
\p 
\v 1 Ngare nyio Herod ji jolo ntul a Galili kehm wuku bada Jisos.
\p 
\v 2 Owo á kehm tongo alokeltum ebe re, “Jon ji nwohngalahb wo ona ma nyahme go elkv. Ano wo wahnge á kpi egburu nsahm ana nyio nyi kpo mehl-e.”
\p 
\v 3 Tibre Herod bobo Jon, gba-e, kak go ngbekobo tib esi ji Herodias ji jolo nkal a Filip mmonannyehn.\f + \fr 14:3 \ft Mat 11:2\f*
\p 
\v 4 Tibre Jon jo tong-e re, “Fuumem re a ko-e.”
\v 5 Herod jo sebe re á wul-e. Á jo fahle Jus, tibre bo jo bumu Jon ana nnyehnamahr.\f + \fr 14:5 \ft Mat 21:26\f*
\v 6 Efung bi bo ji, buumu efung bi bo jele Herod, mmon no nkal no Herodias kehm kehme ase bahn go elkab ane nio. Herod, atahng yeb-e sehng,
\v 7 á kehm nyame, fere tꞌtir re, “M bahk-a kake ejum ajehng ajehng ji a lꞌbahb-m.”
\p 
\v 8 Nnyehn kehm toobo a ne. Mmon noo kehm song tong Herod re, “Ka-m esi Jon ji nwohngalahb anv anv go ekpingi.”
\p 
\v 9 Ntul kpeem bang, wo, tib go esi ji á tiri no go esamahr ane ba á tiingi bo elkak, owo á kehm tongo re bo lim ka-e ana á bahbe no.
\v 10 Á kehm tumu ane, bo song kim Jon esi go ngbekobo,
\v 11 ko esi jio go ekpingi ba a ji, ba ka mmon noo. Mmon noo kehm soro ko, song ka nnyehn.
\v 12 Abatꞌtoono Jon kehm bake, ba rod ekv eje, song kpa kak, kehm feere song tong Jisos.
\s1 Ana Jisos le ellong ane gbalee (5,000)
\r (Mak 6:30-44; Luk 9:10-17; Jon 6:1-14)
\p 
\v 13 Eji Jisos wuku eka jio bada Jon, owo á kehm tahme edi jio, song yel egbang antahng, song rehng edi ji li soom. Ellong ane ba wuku no, kehm tahme ajahbe ebo, jo jen egbuk egbuk, jo toon-e.
\v 14 Jisos lohngo kan egbang me, á kehm nyehne ellong ane gbalee. Bo kehm-e fili ndon. Á kehm limi aneb ayam ebo, bo nob.
\p 
\v 15 Eji elgung ma ba, abatꞌtoono ebe kehm song kpir-e, kehm-e tongo re, “Tahm edi jia ana rehng go ajahbe, ekidi kpꞌlabe. Wo gana, ngare ebsehng. Nong, ane baa song gunu nsol alehke go abon ajahbe li me.”
\p 
\v 16 Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Bo sang bahke tahme song gunu nsol alehke li, wahn kaan bo nsol alehke, bo li.”
\p 
\v 17 Owo bo kehm-e faange re, “Nsol nyi e kpi a kpee li abon abred na alon, kumu abon nsahre abal.” \fig Ebred eblon kunu abon nsahre abal|alt="5 loaves and 2 fishes" src="hk00155c.tif" size="col" loc="MAT 14.17" copy="Horace Knowles" ref="14:17"\fig*
\p 
\v 18 Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Koon nsol nyio ba ka-m wahn!”
\v 19 Owo á kehm tongo ane bao re, bo ji go ajele. Á kehm rodo abon abred bao na alon, a abon nsahre na abal, kehm kpiidi amahr enye go elbung, kak Esowo saam, fere bakke abon abred bao, ka abatꞌtoono ebe. Abatꞌtoono ebe ko, song bak ellong ane bao.
\p 
\v 20 Bo li ane kpee wohngo. Abatꞌtoono ebe kehm song taare bo erik ji sa no, ruru ewubu ejeere na ebbal.
\v 21 Aneblum ba li nsol nyio jolo ejum ane atahltahl nkpel ewubbal ane atahl awubu (5,000). Jol anebkal, a abonse, bo fangem bo.
\s1 Ana Jisos jene go ero alahb
\r (Mak 6:45-52; Jon 6:15-21)
\p 
\v 22 Jisos kehm tongo abatꞌtoono ebe re bo yel egbang, gbo-e mbang, song go egbuk jehko, ye samme ji, yaame ane bao.
\v 23 Eji á ma yaame ane bao, owo á kehm tahme go ewong antahng re á song kak ero. Eji elgung ba no, Jisos noa, kpeke li go ntahngtahng.\f + \fr 14:23 \ft Luk 6:12\f*
\p 
\v 24 Ngare nyio egbang ebrehng go nlum alahb. Ebuku jo gbulu egbang bio tv edi ajehng ajehng. Tibre nfeb jo lohngo go bo a mbuksong.
\v 25 Nkpese efungfu wo, Jisos jene ero alahb, song kpiri bo.
\v 26 Eji abatꞌtoono ebe nyehn-e no á kpꞌjene go ero alahb, kehm mennge bo. Bo kehm bungu re, “Etohko ji,” fere rabe elfahle elfahle.\f + \fr 14:26 \ft Luk 24:37\f*
\p 
\v 27 Jisos kehm soro bung a bo tvtv re, “Boben eltim, me wo, kana kpe fahl!”
\p 
\v 28 Owo Pita kehm-e faange re, “Nsoo, lꞌlohko jol re wo wo, tong-m, me n lohng, jen go alahb, ba kpir-a!”
\p 
\v 29 Jisos kehm-e tongo re, “Ba!” Pita kehm lohngo go egbang, kehm kehme eljene go ero alahb asongo goji Jisos.\f + \fr 14:29 \ft Jon 21:7\f*
\v 30 Eji á nyehne re, nfeb nyio kpꞌlimi area, á kehm kehme elfahle, soro kehme eltere, kehm rabe re, “Nsoo, tahr-m!”
\p 
\v 31 Owo Jisos kehm soro tanne ebo ebe, jabb-e kehm-e tongo re, “Wo ji kpꞌkahn taame ntiil, jen ji wahnge a kehm fꞌfaabe me?”
\p 
\v 32 Eji bo feere song yel go egbang, nfeb nyio kehm soro naange.
\p 
\v 33 Ane ba woomo go egbang kehm ba jamm-e alahng, kehm bungu re, “Etingitingi, wo Mmon Esowo wo.”
\s1 Ana Jisos limi aneb ayam, bo nob go Genesaret
\r (Mak 6:53-56)
\p 
\v 34 Bo kehm gohro siiri, song rehng go egbuk jehko ji Genesaret.
\v 35 Ane bao liingi kan Jisos, bo kehm tiingi etib tv ajahbe kpee nya jolo o. Bo kehm koko aneb ayam kpee, ba a bo go ege.
\v 36 Bo fere gboong-e re, á nong, aneb ayam lub koor-e go ege asꞌsili nsubu. Ane kpee ba koor-e no, bo nobo ayam ebo.\f + \fr 14:36 \ft Mat 9:21; Luk 6:19\f*
\c 15
\s1 Eltibi ni anebkul jo tib
\r (Mak 7:1-13)
\p 
\v 1 Atꞌtibi ba atahm, a egom Farisi jindiki kehm lohngo go Jeusalem ba goji Jisos, ba bahbe re,
\v 2 “Jen ji wahnge abatꞌtoono eba kpꞌdaange atahm nya babnsoo, tib eji bo kil jo ru abo, kehm jo li nsol?”\f + \fr 15:2 \ft Luk 11:38\f*
\p 
\v 3 Owo á kehm faange bo re, “Jen ji wahnge ń kpo daange atahm Esowo, fere kpꞌtoono eljini nꞌnahne?
\v 4 Tibre Esowo jehke ntahm re, ‘Jo kak nso, a nne!’ Nyehko kpe li re, ‘Nne no lꞌsu nde, afi jolo nnyehn, bo bahk-e wulu.’
\v 5 Wahn kpo tib re, ‘Nne no lꞌbel ejum ji á jol kake nde ebo, afi jolo nnyehn, á lꞌfere bung re, Ejum jia li ka Esowo, kpeem li ka-e re, á kpe kak nde, a nnyehn.’\f + \fr 15:5 \ft 1 Tim 5:8\f*
\v 6 Eji ń kpo tib ana wo wahnge ḿ ma range ntahm nyi Esowo, fere kpꞌtoono eljini nꞌnahne.
\v 7 Wahn aneb alum abal abal ba! Aisaya lohko nyehn enyehnamahr ji nno bada nahne, eji á bungu re,
\q1 
\v 8 “ ‘Ane baa kpo kak-m go nnyo a nnyo.
\q1 Ntim ebo n wobem.
\q1 
\v 9 Bo kp-m kake mbol mbol,
\q1 eji bo kpꞌtibi atahm nya ane baka baka jehke no,
\q1 nya ki li nya Esowo.’ ”
\s1 Nsol nyi kpo lim eltim nne, kꞌjol saang
\r (Mak 7:14-23)
\p 
\v 10 Jisos kehm lungu ellong ane tv elne, kehm tongo bo re, “Wuungen atung, wahn kahn!
\v 11 Ejum ji kpo yel nne go nnyo sang kpo lim eltim nne kꞌkpe jol saang.\f + \fr 15:11 \ft 1 Kor 8:8\f* Jio ji kpo lohng na go ege a nnyo, ji ji kpo lim eltim nne re kꞌkpe jol saang.”\f + \fr 15:11 \ft Jems 3:6\f*
\p 
\v 12 Abatꞌtoono ebe kehm bake go ege, ba tong-e re, “Anv, a kpꞌkahne re, alum nya wuku a bungu no sꞌsab Bab Farisia?”
\p 
\v 13 Owo á kehm faange re, “Eti ajehng ajehng ji Nsoo no li go ero ki bahm, bo bahke mehle na tub go.
\v 14 Yaken na yake bo go! Bo li awakamahr atubesi! Nwakamahr lꞌseb re á tib ntem nwakamahr mbang, bo ane abal abal bahke gboko na, yel go elbing.”\f + \fr 15:14 \ft Rom 2:17-24\f*
\p 
\v 15 Owo Pita kehm-e tongo re, “Tong-r ana elgan nia lohngo no!”
\p 
\v 16 Jisos kehm faange re, “Wahn fvfo, ń nehme tob kahna?
\v 17 Ń nehme kahn re, ejum ajehng ajehng ji lꞌyel nne go nnyo kpo sehng go ala, lohng go ngubjinga?
\v 18 Nsol nyi kpo lohng nne go nnyo kpo lohng-e go eltim. Nsol nyio nyi kpo lim nne, kꞌkpe jol saang.
\v 19 Tibre go eltim nne wo ebi ntir kpo lohng, a ewulane, erehbe alimi, anebkal akono, ejv avohko, ntianse efahnge, a afahnge akiimi lake ane.
\v 20 Nsol nyia ana nyi kpo lim nne, kꞌkpe jol saang. Re nne li nsol kꞌru abo, we nehm ma lim á kꞌkpe jol saang.”
\s1 Nnenkal no taame no
\r (Mak 7:24-30)
\p 
\v 21 Jisos kehm tahme edi jio, song rehng go ejang bi Taya, a Saidon.
\p 
\v 22 Nnenkal a Kenan awohng no lohng ejahbe jio kehm bake go ege, ba rabe gboong-e re, “Nsoo, mmon no Devid, nong, me n fil-a ndon! Mmon ewame, ebi etohko wob-e go atahng, kp-e gbiingi sehng.”
\p 
\v 23 Jisos we tikem faange.
\p Abatꞌtoono ebe kehm bake go ege, ba gboong-e re, “Tong-e á song. Tibre á kpꞌrabe tob-r sehng.”
\p 
\v 24 Owo Jisos kehm faange re, “Bo tum-m tv go ejoro bio bi Israel bi ma tan bi bi.”\f + \fr 15:24 \ft Mat 10:6\f*
\p 
\v 25 Owo nnenkal noo kehm ba gbo go ege alata, kehm bungu re, “Nsoo, kak-m ebo!”
\p 
\v 26 Owo Jisos kehm faange re, “Nobem re nne rod nsol alehke nyi abon, ka ebv.”
\p 
\v 27 Nnenkal noo kehm taame re, “Ee nsoo, jol ebv kpo kpiimi akahb elang nya kpo fooro ekpꞌkuru nde ebo gbo.”
\p 
\v 28 Owo Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Nnenkal, eltaame ena kpꞌgbale gbalee.\f + \fr 15:28 \ft Luk 11:5-8; 18:2-8\f* Nong, lohko jol ana a kpꞌsebe.”
\p Ngare nyꞌnehm ona nyi mmon ewe noo no nkal nobo eyam bio.
\s1 Ana Jisos limi ane gbalee, bo nob
\p 
\v 29 Jisos kehm tahme edi jio, song rehng go eto jio ji Galili, kehm wahre go ewong, song ji.
\v 30 Ellong ane gbalee kehm koko aneb ayam ba a bo goji Jisos. Bandiki jolo abanne, bandiki agboodo, bandiki awakamahr, bandiki akamme. Ane bako gbalee ba jo yame ayam nyandikandiki. Bo jo ba bumu aneb ayam bao go alata nya Jisos. Á jo lim bo, bo nob.
\v 31 Jo kpo ane esi sehng, eji bo nyehne akamme kpꞌbungu, fere nyehn agboodo ma nob, fere nyehn abanne kpꞌjene, awakamahr fere jo nyehn. Bo kehm kehme Esowo bio bi Israel ellub ka.\f + \fr 15:31 \ft Luk 7:16-22\f*
\s1 Ana Jisos kpe le ellong ane nehko (4,000)
\r (Mak 8:1-10)
\p 
\v 32 Jisos kehm lungu abatꞌtoono ebe tv elne, kehm tongo bo re, “Ane baa ma-m fili ndon. Tibre nfung era nyi a, nyi bo ma kang a name. Anv, bo kpeem kpi ejum alehke ajehng ajehng. N nehme seb re me n yake bo, bo song njal njal. Fundiki bo bahke gboko awo go mbang.”
\p 
\v 33 Owo abatꞌtoono Jisos kehm-e bahbe re, “Gan wo e bahke tingi nsol alehke elka emahng nia, kehm leke ellong ane ana nia?”
\p 
\v 34 Owo Jisos kehm bahbe bo re, “Abon abred abik ń kpi no?”
\p Bo kehm-e faange re, “E kpi abon abred na asehma, kunu abon nsahre abik abik.”
\p 
\v 35 Jisos kehm tongo ellong ane bao re, bo ji go ndi.
\v 36 Á kehm rodo abon abred bao na asehma, a nsahre nyio, kehm kake Esowo saam, bakke, ka abatꞌtoono ebe, abatꞌtoono ebe kehm koko, song bak ane.
\v 37 Bo li ane kpee wohngo. Abatꞌtoono ebe kehm taare bo erik ji sa no, ruru ejeere na ebsehma.
\v 38 Aneblum ba li nsol nyio jolo ane atahltahl nkpel ewubu (4,000). Jol anebkal, a abonse, bo fangem.
\p 
\v 39 Jisos kehm yaame ane bao re bo song kehnge, kehm yele egbang, song rehng go egbuk jehko ji Magadan.
\c 16
\s1 Ana bo sebe re bo nyehn nkpokosi
\r (Mak 8:11-13; Luk 12:54-56)
\p 
\v 1 Egom Farisi jindiki, a Bab Sadusi kehm bake goji Jisos re bo ba gar-e. Owo bo kehm-e tongo re, á lim nkpokosi nyi lohng go ejahbetul Esowo tib bo.\f + \fr 16:1 \ft Mat 12:38\f*
\p 
\v 2 Owo Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Ana wo ń kpo kono elbungu. Elgung lꞌba, eji elbung ma biili, ń re, ‘Elahb nehm na.’
\v 3 Efungfu atv atv eji elbung ma biili, fere nyꞌnyak, ń re, ‘Elahb bahke nake.’ Ń kpo kahn ana elbung li no, joare elahb bahke nake, afi nehm na. Anv, nliingi nyi kpꞌtibi bada ngare ń nehme ma liinga?\f + \fr 16:3 \ft 1 Tes 5:1; Luk 2:12; Mat 24:3,30\f*
\v 4 Abi ane ba li anv, ba ma sennge Esowo njahm kpꞌsebe re bo nyehn nkpokosi. Jol nkpokosi anyehng anyehng bo nehm nyehn, sehngem nkpokosi ana nyio nyi nnyehnamahr Jona nyi nyi bo bahke nyehne.”
\p Owo á kehm soro tahm bo sa o, tahm eje.
\s1 Ayist nya Farisis, a nya Sadusis
\r (Mak 8:14-21)
\p 
\v 5 Eji abatꞌtoono Jisos siiri eto jio, song rehng egbuk jehko, ebred ajehng ajehng bo belem. Tibre bo yꞌyini, bo rodem.
\v 6 Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Jo gberen, wahn jo kunu ekpu go ayist nyao nya Farisis, a nya Sadusis.”\f + \fr 16:6 \ft Luk 12:1; Gal 5:9\f*
\p 
\v 7 Bo kehm kehme elbungu atemtem re, “Á bungu ellum nia a, tib eji e ki rod abred ba a nya.”
\p 
\v 8 Eji Jisos sebe kahn ana bo jo bung, á kehm bahbe bo re, “Wahn ane ba kpꞌkahn taame ntiil ba! Jen ji wahnge ń kpꞌbungu atemtem bade ana ń ki rod abred ba a nya?
\v 9 Anv, ń ka tiki kahn naa? Anv, ń nehme kpe buumu ana m bakke abon abred bao na alon, ka ane atahltahl nkpel ewubbal atahl awuba? Anv, erik ji sa no, ji ń taare no, ruru ejeere ebbik?
\v 10 Abon abred bao na asehma ba m bakke, ka ane atahltahl nkpel ewubu, erik ji sa no, ji ń taare no, ruru ejeere ebbik?
\v 11 Jen ji wahnge ń kil tiki kahn re, n joom bung a nahne bade abred? Jo gberen elnahne tib ayist nya Farisis, a nya Sadusis.”
\p 
\v 12 Owo abatꞌtoono ebe kehm kahne re, Jisos jo tongo bo re, bo gbere eltibi nio ni Farisis, a ni Sadusis, bo kꞌgbere ayist nya bo kpo kak go abred.
\s1 Ana Pita bungu bada Jisos
\r (Mak 8:27-30; Luk 9:18-21)
\p 
\v 13 Eji Jisos rehnge go ejang bi Sisaria Filipi, owo á kehm bahbe abatꞌtoono ebe re, “Anv, ane kpo bung renan bada Mmon no nne? Nne awo li Mmon no nne?”
\p 
\v 14 Owo bo kehm faange re, “Ane bandiki kpo bung re, wo Jon ji nwohngalahb wo. Ane bandiki bung re, wo Elaija wo. Ane bandiki re, wo Jeremaya wo, tohko jol ano nnyehnamahr nondiki wo.”
\p 
\v 15 Owo Jisos kehm bahbe bo re, “Anv, wahn kpo tir re, me n li elkohn nne awo?”
\p 
\v 16 Saimon Pita kehm faange re, “Wo wo li Mesaya ji Mmon no Esowo bi li go elkpin.”\f + \fr 16:16 \ft Jon 6:69\f*
\p 
\v 17 Owo Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Eyebatahng li a na, Saimon, mmon a Jona. Ji a bungu a, nne sang tib-a na. Nsoo no li go ero wo ma lennge ka-a.
\v 18 N kp-a kpeke tong re, Wo wo li Pita (ji lohngo re eltal).\f + \fr 16:18 \ft Jon 1:42\f* Go ekpartal jia wo m bahke sehke etahk ero ejame.\f + \fr 16:18 \ft Ef 2:20\f* Jol elkv nehm ma rannge etahk jio.
\v 19 M bahk-a kake agbokoro nya ejahbetul Esowo.\f + \fr 16:19 \ft Elt 15:7\f* Ji a lꞌgba go njini nyia, bobtob gba go ejahbetul Esowo. Ji a lꞌfannge go njini nyia, bobtob fannge go ejahbetul Esowo.”\f + \fr 16:19 \ft Mat 18:18; Jon 20:23\f*
\p 
\v 20 Owo Jisos kehm tongo abatꞌtoono ebe re, bo kꞌtiki tong nne awohng awohng re, ye wo li Mesaya.
\s1 Ana Jisos bungu bade erem ebe, a elkv ene
\r (Mak 8:31-9:1; Luk 9:22-27)
\p 
\v 21 Bomo ngare nyio asongo, Jisos kehm bomo abatꞌtoono ebe eltongo gbul gbul gbuul re, “M bahke jeke go Jeusalem, song nyehn erem gbalee, bi anebkul nfam, a atubesi abalimajom, a atꞌtibi ba atahm bahk-m kake. Bo bahk-m wulu. Lꞌkang nfung era, n nyahme go elkv.”\f + \fr 16:21 \ft Jon 2:19,21\f*
\p 
\v 22 Pita kehm koko Jisos, tahm a ne go nkpohko, kehm-e rehke re, “Nsoo, Esowo kꞌtaame re ejum ana jia lim-a.”
\p 
\v 23 Owo Jisos kehm sennge, tong Pita re, “Nnehm, fak-m go esamahr! Wo kp-m kpane. Tibre a kpo tir ntir nyehka nyehka nyi ane. A kpehme tir ntir nyi Esowo.”\f + \fr 16:23 \ft Mat 4:10\f*
\p 
\v 24 Owo Jisos kehm tongo abatꞌtoono ebe re, “Nne awohng awohng no lꞌseb re á toon-m, nong á ten elne tv-m, fere rod ekros eje tahm toon-m.
\v 25 Tibre nne awohng awohng no lꞌseb re á tahre elkpin ene, á bahke tane na elkpin ene. Nne awohng awohng no lꞌtane elkpin ene tib go egame esi, á bahke bele etingitingi elkpin.
\v 26 Nsehng anyi nne bahke lehke, afi á gbo afang nya njini nyia kpee, fere tane etohko eje? Ejum aji nne bahke kake, kehm fake etohko eje?\f + \fr 16:26 \ft Elt 8:18-20; 1 Pit 1:18-19\f*
\p 
\v 27 “Tibre Mmon no nne yahke ba elbake go ellub ni nde, a enjel enye. Owo á bahke tuuru nne awohng awohng jang jang ana á limi no.\f + \fr 16:27 \ft Rom 2:6; Luk 19:16-19\f*
\v 28 Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Egom ejahne jindiki jia ana, ji lꞌkꞌkpo tete bo nyehn Mmon no nne kpꞌbake ana ntul.”\f + \fr 16:28 \ft Mat 17:2\f*
\c 17
\s1 Ana Jisos yaange ngubjing
\r (Mak 9:2-13; Luk 9:28-36)
\p 
\v 1 Eji ma kang nfung erakera, Jisos kehm yehke Pita, Jems, a Jon ji mmonannyehn a Jems. Bo kehm tahme bo bo, song wahr nwahrewahre ewong.
\v 2 Eji bo jo seenge Jisos, á kehm yaange. Esamahr ebe fere jo ya ana njul. Nsol nyi á kake go ngubjing kehm bare kparaang.
\v 3 Owo bo kehm soro nyehn Moses abola Elaija ma lohng ba, ba kehme elbungu a Jisos.
\p 
\v 4 Pita kehm tongo Jisos re, “Nsoo, a wo li nnoobo edi ji fuumu re wahr jol. Lꞌkor-a, nong, wahr si nkpatahk era a, behko jol bꞌba, behko jol bi Moses, behko jol bi Elaija.”
\p 
\v 5 Eji Pita kpi mbungu mbungu, ekparesemsem ji jo ya, kehm tahle ba bulu bo. Owo bo kehm wuku ellum go ekparesemsem jio re,
\p “A wo li akor-m mmon ewame no kpo kor-m sꞌsehng. Wuken ye!”\f + \fr 17:5 \ft 2 Pit 1:16-18\f*
\p 
\v 6 Abatꞌtoono bao wuku kan ano, bo kehm gboko, kohk asamahr ebo go ndi, kehm kehme elfahle gbalee.
\p 
\v 7 Jisos kehm bake, ba kpiri bo, kooro bo, kehm bungu re, “Mehlen yiimi, kana kpe fahl!”
\p 
\v 8 Eji bo tabe asamahr ebo wahre, bo kpeem nyehn nnene, sehngem Jisos ntahngtahng wo bo nyehn-e no.
\p 
\v 9 Eji bo jo badde go ewong abake, Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Kana tiki tong nne awohng awohng bada nkpokosi nyi ḿ ma nyehn a, tete Mmon no nne nyahme go elkv.”\f + \fr 17:9 \ft Mat 16:20\f*
\p 
\v 10 Abatꞌtoono bao kehm-e bahbe re, “Jen ji wahnge atꞌtibi ba atahm kpo bung re, Elaija bahke tohko gbo mbang ba?”
\p 
\v 11 Á kehm faange re, “Elaija bahke gboko mbang ba, ba tuungu ejum ajehng ajehng.
\v 12 N kp-n tongo re, Elaija ebsi bꞌba. Bo we liingem. Bo lim-e ejum ajehng ajehng ji koro bo.\f + \fr 17:12 \ft Mat 11:14\f* Ano wo fvfo Mmon no nne bahke tob nyehn erem bi ane bao bahk-e kake.”
\p 
\v 13 Owo kehm lennge abatꞌtoono bao re, á jo bungu abo bada Jon ji nwohngalahb.
\s1 Ana Jisos limi mmon no bele ebi etohko, á nob
\r (Mak 9:14-29; Luk 9:37-43)
\p 
\v 14 Eji bo feere no, ba rehng edi ji ellong ane jolo no, nne awohng kehm lohngo ba, ba jamme Jisos alahng,
\v 15 kehm-e tongo re, “Nsoo, nong, mmon ewame fil-a ndon. Á kpo gbo ngboko, kpo gbiing-e sehng. Nkpel tvv á kpo kono elgboko yel agun, fere jo gbo yel alahb.
\v 16 N ko-e ba a ne goji abatꞌtoono eba. Bo we maam lim, á nob.”
\p 
\v 17 Owo Jisos kehm faange re, “Wahn ane ba kpo soodo, fere kꞌtaame ba! M bahke kange renan a nahne? Anv, bahke kange renan, ji m bahke koko tib-n, ń kehm kahne? Ko mmon noo, ba a ne!”
\v 18 Jisos kehm nyame ebi etohko jio, ebi etohko jio kehm soro lohng mmon noo. Mmon noo lohko nob tvtv.
\p 
\v 19 Owo abatꞌtoono Jisos kehm bake, ba kpiri Jisos, eji á li ntahngtahng, kehm-e bahbe re, “Jen ji wahnge wahr ki ma kam ebi etohko jio yehke?”
\p 
\v 20 Owo Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Ekꞌtaame ejahne ji wahnge. Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Ń lꞌtaame, jol afi eltaame enahne se ana mmohk asia, ń li ma tong ewong jia re, ‘Mehl, song rehng o!’ Ewong jio bahke lohko mehl tahm. Ejumjum limm, ji bahk-n riidi.\f + \fr 17:20 \ft Mat 21:21; Luk 17:6\f*
\v 21 Elkohn ebi etohko ana jio ń nehm ma kam yehke, tohko jol re ń kake ero, fere bade elnahne njal.”
\s1 Ana Jisos kpe bung bade elkv ene
\r (Mak 9:30-32; Luk 9:43-45)
\p 
\v 22 Ngare nyi bo jolo go Galili, Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Mmon no nne, bo yahk-e ba elyake, kak ane go ebo.
\v 23 Bo bahk-e wulu. Lꞌkang nfung era, á nyahme go elkv.”
\p Abatꞌtoono ebe, ndon kehm gbale bo go eltim.
\s1 Bade etak atahbe
\p 
\v 24 Eji Jisos, a abatꞌtoono ebe ba rehng go Kapenium, ane ba kpo ko etak ji etahk Esowo kehm ba bahb Pita re, “Anv, ntꞌtibi ewahne kpehme tahb etak ji etahk Esowoa?”
\p 
\v 25 Pita kehm faange re, “Ee.”
\p Eji Pita yele ekpꞌkpa, owo Jisos kehm gboko mbang bahb-e re, “Saimon, anv, a kpo tir renan bade ejum jia? Atul ba njini nyia kpo ko atak goji abon ebo, afi bo kpo ko goji ane baka baka?”
\p 
\v 26 Owo Pita kehm faange re, “Goji ane baka baka.”
\p Jisos kehm bungu re, “Lꞌfere jol ano, lohngo re, abon, ntahm bo wobem.
\v 27 Nong, wahr lim, eji lꞌkꞌsab bo. Song, wo song tub eblo go eto! Yehke ngbokambang a nnyam alahb nyi gbo eblo, wo lennge nnyo eme. Owo a bahke nyehne akpohko nya bahke biingi etak ejame, a jꞌja. Nyao nya a bahke koko, song ka bo.”\f + \fr 17:27 \ft 1 Kor 9:19\f*
\c 18
\s1 Nne awo ga gbal?
\r (Mak 9:33-37; Luk 9:46-48)
\p 
\v 1 Ngare nyio nyi abatꞌtoono Jisos ba rehng go ege, owo bo kehm-e bahbe re, “Nne awo ga gbal go ellong ane ba wob go elwo ni Esowo?”
\p 
\v 2 Jisos kehm lungu mmonse, ba yiimi go bo a mbuksong,
\v 3 kehm bungu re, “Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Ń tohko tiki yaange jol ana abonse, ń nehm tiki li etul bi Esowo.
\v 4 Fvfo, nne no lꞌrede elne, jol ana mmonse noa, ye wo ga gbal go ellong ane ba wob go elwo ni Esowo.
\v 5 Nne awohng awohng no lꞌvvrv elkohn mmonse ana noa tib go egama mbing, á vvrv me.\f + \fr 18:5 \ft Mat 10:40\f*
\s1 Nsol nyi kpo wahng nne yel abiafem
\r (Mak 9:42-48; Luk 17:1-2)
\p 
\v 6 “Ga nob re bo kahn nne egburu eltal go emel, tub-e kak alahb, sehnge re á lim mmonse awohng no ma taame tv-m, á gbo yel abiafem.
\p 
\v 7 “Eyuu a ane ba njini nyia tib nsol nyi kpo wahng re ane jo lim abiafem! Nsol nyio bahke tiki ba. Eyuu a ane ba kpꞌkoko ba a nyi!
\p 
\v 8 “Ebo eba, afi jolo ekpade eja lꞌkehm-a limi re wo gbo yel abiafem, kim tub go! Ga nob re wo yel go edi elkpin ebo abehng, tohko jol ano ekpade ajehng, sehnge re wo bel abo abal abal, a akpade abal abal, bo ro-a kak go agun nya li go njinanjini.\f + \fr 18:8 \ft Mat 5:29-30\f*
\p 
\v 9 “Elmahr ena lꞌkehm-a limi re wo lim abiafem, luudu ro go! Ga nob re wo bel elmahr anehng, yel edi elkpin, sehnge re wo bel amahr abal abal, bo ro-a kak ellulagun.
\p 
\v 10 “Jo kunen ekpu, eji ń lꞌkꞌdaange mmonse awohng awohng no wob go ellong abonse baa. Tibre n kp-n tongo re, Enjel ebo nya li go ejahbetul Esowo kpo nyehn esamahr Nsoo no li go ero ngare anyehng anyehng.\f + \fr 18:10 \ft Hib 1:14\f*
\v 11 Tibre Mmon no nne ba re, á ba tahre jio ji ma tan.
\s1 Elgan ni li bada njoro nyi tane no
\r (Luk 15:3-7)
\p 
\v 12 “Anv, ń kpꞌtiri renan bade ejum jia? Nne lꞌbel ejoro atahl alon, anyehng kehm ba tan, nfono ejoro nehm tahm ejoro behko sa go awong, song seb nyio nyi ma tana?\fig mbaabebul a ebul ebe|alt="shepherd with a sheep" src="lb00001c.tif" size="col" loc="MAT 18:12" copy="Louise Bass" ref="18:12"\fig*
\v 13 Á lꞌseb-e nyehn, etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, á bahke ga bel eyebatahng go njoro nyio, sehnge ejoro behko bi ki tan.
\v 14 Ano wo fvfo Nso ejahne no li go ero kil sebe re mmonse awohng awohng go ellong abonse baa tan.
\s1 Ana nne Esowo bahke jo lim mmonannyehn lꞌsood-e
\p 
\v 15 “Mmonanne lꞌlim abiafem bada na, song lennge ebi ji á lim-a no ka-e wahn wahn. Á lꞌwuk-a, a m-e ko, feere a ne.\f + \fr 18:15 \ft Luk 17:3; Mat 18:21-22; Gal 6:1\f*
\v 16 Á tohk-a fere wuk, ko ntianse anyehng, tohko jol ano ebal, je a bo, ‘eji ellum anehng anehng lꞌjo yiimi, ni ntianse ebal, tohko jol ano ni ntianse era bungu no, bum nnyo amehng.’
\v 17 Á tohko fere wuk bo, tooro tong aneb ero. Á tohko fere wuk aneb ero, ko-e na ko ana nne no ki nyi Esowo, tohko jol ano ana nkokatak.\f + \fr 18:17 \ft 1 Kor 5:9-13\f*
\s1 Nsahm nyi li go ero akake
\p 
\v 18 “Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Ejum ajehng ajehng ji ń lꞌgba go njini nyia, bobtob gba go ejahbetul Esowo. Ejum ajehng ajehng ji ń lꞌfannge go njini nyia, bobtob fannge go ejahbetul Esowo.\f + \fr 18:18 \ft Jon 20:23\f*
\p 
\v 19 “N kp-n kpeke tong re, Ejum ajehng ajehng ji ane abal ebahne lꞌkod abo kak ero go njini nyia, Nsoo no li go ero bahke limi ka bo.\f + \fr 18:19 \ft Mak 11:24\f*
\v 20 Tibre edi jio ji ane abal, ane ara lꞌkono go egama mbing, me n li go bo ellong.”
\s1 Elgan ni li bada nne no ki tahm ka ntem
\p 
\v 21 Pita kehm bake goji Jisos, kehm ba bahb-e re, “Nsoo, nkpel ebik nyi mmonannee lꞌsood-m, m bahke jo tahm ka-e?”
\p 
\v 22 Owo Jisos kehm-e faange re, “N kp-a tongo re, Nkpel esehma sang, li nkpel atahltahl atahl ani nkpel ewubu.\f + \fr 18:22 \ft Luk 17:3-4\f*
\p 
\v 23 “Etul bi Esowo li ana ntul awohng no lungu alokeltum ebe re bo ba toobo akpohko enye ka-e.
\v 24 Á bomo kan eltoobo a alokeltum ebe, owo bo kehm koko nne awohng ba go ege, no bel-e mbong ekpa akpohko atahltahl nkpel atahltahl.
\v 25 Eji nlokeltum noo ki bel ejumjum ji á bahke kake, owo nde kehm tongo re, bo gung-e, fere gungu nkal ewe, gungu abon ebe, a nsol kpee nyi á kpi no, ko akpohko nyao gal mbong.
\p 
\v 26 “Owo nlokeltum noo kehm jamme nde alahng, kehm-e gboongo re, ‘Nsoo titi, tohko kpe nong, m bahk-a gale mbong enya kpee.’
\p 
\v 27 “Nde nlokeltum noo, ndon kehm-e fili, á kehm-e yake, á song, fere yake mbong nyi á bel-e no tv-e.\f + \fr 18:27 \ft Luk 6:36; Ef 4:32\f*
\p 
\v 28 “Nlokeltum nonehm o kehm tahme song kpiri nte ewe, no jo tob loko nde nonehm o. Nte ewe noo bel-e mbong a mpon esehma. Á kehm-e tubu ejahm go nkahng, fere tong-e re, ‘Gal-m mbong enyame!’
\p 
\v 29 “Nte ewe noo kehm-e jamme alahng, fere jo gboong-e re, ‘Titi, tohko kpe nong, m bahk-a gale mbong enya.’
\p 
\v 30 “Jol atung we á joom wuungu. Á tahm a ne, song kak-e ngbekobo re á woomo o tete gal-e mbong enye.
\p 
\v 31 “Eji alokeltum bako nyehne ano, bo kpeem jo bang. Bo kehm tahme, song tooro nsol kpee nyi ma lim, tong nde ebo.
\p 
\v 32 “Owo nde kehm-e lungu, kehm-e tongo re, ‘Wo ebi nlokeltum wo. Mbong nyio nyi a bel-m no kpee, me n yake tv-a, tib eji a gboong-m no.
\v 33 Anv, limm nyi kehn nte ewa jol-a tob fili ndon, ana a fil-m ndona?’
\p 
\v 34 “Nde noo, atahng rak-e sehng, owo á kehm tumu nlokeltum noo ngbekobo re bo kak-e erem tete á gal-e mbong enye kpee.\f + \fr 18:34 \ft Mat 5:26\f*
\p 
\v 35 “Ano wo Nsoo no li go ero bahke limi nne awohng awohng ewahne no tohko jo tahm ka mmonannyehn go abiafem nya á lim-e no kpee eltim eltim ene.”\f + \fr 18:35 \ft Jems 2:13\f*
\c 19
\s1 Ana Jisos tibi bade elbal amale
\r (Mak 10:1-12)
\p 
\v 1 Eji Jisos ma bung ano mal, á kehm tahme o Galili, feere go Judea, egbuk Jodan jehko.
\v 2 Ellong ane gbalee kehm tahme toon-e. Á kehm limi bo, bo nob ayam ebo.
\p 
\v 3 Egom Farisi jindiki kehm bake re bo ba gar-e. Bo bahb-e re, “Anv, ntahm enyahre bꞌbung re, nfem anyehng anyehng lꞌgbo nne abola nkal ewe, á yehk-e na yehke elbala?”\f + \fr 19:3 \ft Mat 5:31-32\f*
\p 
\v 4 Owo Jisos kehm faange re, “Anv ń ka tiki lung bade ana Esowo limi ane go mbomannahb re, á limi ‘nnenlum, a nnenkala?’
\v 5 fere bung re, ‘Ano wo wahnge nne bahke tahme nde, a nnyehn sa, bo song jol ebo ebo abola nkal ewe. Ane bao na abal bahke fere jol ajehng.’
\v 6 Bo nehm kpe jol ane abal, bo bahke fere jol ana ngubjing anyehng. Ejum ji Esowo ma kono edi ajehng, nne kꞌyaame.”\f + \fr 19:6 \ft 1 Kor 7:10-11\f*
\p 
\v 7 Owo Bab Farisi kehm-e bahbe re, “Jen ji wahnge Moses kehm jehke ntahm re, nne jo nyon nwer, ka nkal ewe, kehm-e kame, á song?”
\p 
\v 8 Jisos kehm faange re, “Moses jehke ntahm re wahn jo yehke akal ebahne ano tib go egahne etahnsi. Go mbomannahb jolem ano.
\v 9 Wo, n kp-n tongo re, Nne awohng awohng no lꞌkam nkal ewe, eji nnenlum nondiki ki noongo a ne, fere ko nkal nondiki, yeblim abiafem nyao nya erehbe. Nne no lꞌko nnenkal no bo m-e yehke elbal, yebtob lim abiafem nya erehbe.”\f + \fr 19:9 \ft Luk 16:18\f*
\p 
\v 10 Abatꞌtoono ebe kehm-e tongo re, “Joare ano wo li no bada nnenlum, a nnenkal, ga nob re nne kꞌko nkal.”
\p 
\v 11 Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Ellum ni n fi elbungu a, ane kpee sang bahke lennge bo, sehngem ane bao ba Esowo ma lennge ka bo, bo ba bahke lennge bo.
\v 12 Ane baa, ba bo ma fang bo. Ane baa, ba bo jele na bo ano. Ane baa, ba fange elbo antahng tib esi jio ona ji etul bi Esowo.\f + \fr 19:12 \ft 1 Kor 7:7,32-35\f* Nne no lꞌmal kahn ana lohngo no, nong, á kahn.”
\s1 Ana Jisos jo fuulu abon ba nse
\r (Mak 10:13-16; Luk 18:15-17)
\p 
\v 13 Ane bandiki kehm koko abon ba nse, ba goji Jisos re á kunu bo abo, kak ero. Abatꞌtoono Jisos kehm nyame ane bao.
\p 
\v 14 Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Yaken abon ba nse, bo jo ba ga egame. Kana jo sahde bo! Tibre etul bi Esowo li ka ane ba li ana bo.”\f + \fr 19:14 \ft Mat 18:2-3\f*
\v 15 Á kehm kunu bo abo, kehm tahme eje o.
\s1 Njangkun nyi jolo efange nne
\r (Mak 10:17-31; Luk 18:18-30)
\p 
\v 16 Nne awohng kehm bake goji Jisos, ba bahb-e re, “Ntꞌtibi, nnoobo anyi m bahke limi, eji n lꞌbel elkpin ni li go njinanjini?”\f + \fr 19:16 \ft Luk 10:25-28\f*
\p 
\v 17 Owo Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Jen ji wahnge a kehm-m bahbe bade ji kpꞌnobo? Esowo ntahngtahng bi kpꞌnobo. Lꞌjol re a kpꞌsebe re wo bel elkpin, jo bum atahm!”
\p 
\v 18 Owo á kehm-e bahbe re, “Atahm anya?”
\p Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Ka jo wul nne! Ka jo lim erehbe! Ka jo v ejv! Ka jo yiimi ntianse efahnge!
\v 19 Kak nso, a nne! Nne ebjing ewa jo kor-a ana ebjing eba!”
\p 
\v 20 Owo njangkun nyio kehm-e faange re, “Nyaa kpee n kpo bꞌbum. Anv, ejum aji kpe li, ji m bahke kpe lim!”
\p 
\v 21 Jisos kehm-e tongo re, “A lꞌseb re wo jol go nseenge, song, wo song gungu nsol kpee nyi a kpi no, ko akpohko nyao song ka akpak, a bahke bele afang go ejahbetul Esowo, wo feere ba toon-m.”\f + \fr 19:21 \ft Luk 12:33-34\f*
\p 
\v 22 Eji njangkun nyio wuku ano, á kehm tahme eje ndon ndon. Tibre á fange sehng.
\p 
\v 23 Jisos kehm bungu tong abatꞌtoono ebe re, “Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Bahke riidi sehng re, efange nne kehm lehke etul bi Esowo.
\v 24 N kp-n kpeke tong re, Re efange nne kehm yele go ejahbetul Esowo, ekamel bahke sehnge go mbang a nga.”
\p 
\v 25 Abatꞌtoono ebe wuku ano, kehm sahb kpꞌkpo bo esi, bo kehm bahbe re, “Wo anv, nne awo bahke kehm bele eltahre me?”
\p 
\v 26 Jisos kehm seenge bo too, kehm bungu tong bo re, “Jia, nne nehm ma lim. Wo, goji Esowo ejum ajehng ajehng riidem.”
\p 
\v 27 Owo Pita kehm bungu re, “Nyehn ana e ma yake nsol kpee kp-a toono. Ejum aji e bahke bele?”
\p 
\v 28 Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Ngare nyi Mmon no nne bahke jehke go eti etul ji ellub ene, ngare nyio nyi nsol kpee ma yaange, jol nyi nfenfe, owo wahn jia ji jo toon-m ḿ bahke tob ji go ewubu a nti etul ebal, fere lam ewubu etꞌtohngo ebbal bi Israel.\f + \fr 19:28 \ft Luk 22:30; 1 Kor 6:2-3\f*
\v 29 Nne awohng awohng no lꞌyake etahk eje, yake abonanyehn, yake nde, yake nnyehn, yake abon ebe, fere yake egbe eje tib go esi mbing enyame, á bahke bele budu nkpel atahl alon, fere bel elkpin ni li go njinanjini.
\v 30 Ane gbalee ba li agbokombang bahke fere jol akahlenjahm. Akahlenjahm bahke fere jol agbokombang.\f + \fr 19:30 \ft Mat 20:16\f*
\c 20
\s1 Elgan ni li bade ane ba bo lake bo egbe
\p 
\v 1 “Etul bi Esowo li ana nfono egbe no tahme no efungfu atv atv, song lak ane egbe eje.\f + \fr 20:1 \ft Mat 9:37\f*
\v 2 Eji á ma lam are ane bao re á bahke kake bo nne awohng awohng nsiring elon elon efung, owo á kehm tubu bo tv go ege egbe re bo song lim eltum.
\p 
\v 3 “Eji ma rehng nkaranka esehmwubu, á kehm jeke are, song nyehn ane bamongo yim no mbol mbol, kil ejumjum lim.
\v 4 Owo á kehm tongo bo re, ‘Wahn tob songen go egame egbe, wahn song lim eltum. M bahk-n kpiki nob nob ana bo kpo kono elkpiki.’
\p 
\v 5 “Owo bo kehm tahme.
\p “Nfono egbe noo kehm kpe je ngare efin, fere kpe je go nkaranka era nyi elgung, tob lim ano jang jang.
\v 6 Eji ma rehng nkaranka elon nyi elgung, á kehm kpe je, song nyehn ane bako yim no mbol mbol, kil ejumjum lim. Owo á kehm tongo bo re, ‘Jen ji wahnge ń yim na yim ana efung kohro kohro, ń kil ejumjum lim?’
\p 
\v 7 “Owo bo kehm-e faange re, ‘Nnene limm, no ma-r lak eltum.’
\p “Á kehm tongo bo re, ‘Tob songen fvfo go egame egbe, wahn song lim eltum. M bahk-n kpiki nob nob ana bo kpo kono elkpiki.’
\p 
\v 8 “Eji elgung ba no, nfono egbe noo kehm tongo ntubesi a nlokeltum ewe re, ‘Lung aneb eltum ebame, bo ba, wo kpi bo. Gbo mbang bom goji ane ba n gohro ko bo ba, wo kehm gohro kpi ane ba n gbo mbang ko bo.’
\p 
\v 9 “Ane ba bomo eltum nkaranka elon nyi elgung kehm bake, ba ko nsiring elon elon.
\v 10 Owo ane ba, á gbo mbang lak bo kehm bake. Bo jo tiri re, bo bahke koko akpohko sehnge ane bao. Bo fvfo tob ko nsiring elon elon.
\v 11 Eji bo ma ko ano, owo bo kehm kehme elmemme tob nfono egbe noo re,
\v 12 ‘Ane baa ba a gohro ko bo ba, bo limi eltum awa anyehng nya nya, wobkpi bo jang jang ana a kpi-r no, wahr ji ma nyehn erem go nfuba njul nyia efung kohro kohro.’
\p 
\v 13 “Owo nfono egbe kehm faange nne awohng re, ‘Mbi, wa n nehmem na. Nsiring elon sang wuku e lame area?
\v 14 Ko akpohko enya, wo song a nya! Anv, lꞌkor-m re me n ka ane ba gohro ba ekahlenjahm ana n ka-a no,
\v 15 anv, akpohko enyame sang n kpꞌkoko lim ana kor-m noa? Anv, a kpꞌmemme tib eji m ma wehr aboa?’ ”\f + \fr 20:15 \ft Rom 9:16\f*
\p 
\v 16 Jisos kehm gohro bung re, “Akahlenjahm bahke gboko mbang, agbokombang fere kahle njahm.\f + \fr 20:16 \ft Rom 11:25-26\f* Ane gbalee ba bo ma lung bo, wo, abon amohk ane ntiil ba bo ma jak.”\f + \fr 20:16 \ft Rom 10:21\f*
\s1 Ana Jisos gohro bung bade elkv ene
\r (Mak 10:32-34; Luk 18:31-34)
\p 
\v 17 Eji Jisos jo tahm go Jeusalem, ngare nyi bo li go mbang, á kehm koko abatꞌtoono ebe, ewubu ane abal, tahm a bo go nkpohko anyehng, song tong bo re,
\v 18 “Nyehnen, anv, e kpꞌtahme go Jeusalem. Mmon no nne, bo bahk-e yake, kak atubesi abalimajom, a atꞌtibi ba atahm go ebo. Bo bahke lame elam ji bo bahk-e wulu,
\v 19 fere yak-e, kak ane baka baka go ebo, ba bahk-e nyoko, fere dv-e, kum-e go ekros. Lꞌkang nfung era, á nyahme go elkv.”
\s1 Ejum ji nnyehn Bab Jon gboongo no
\r (Mak 10:35-45)
\p 
\v 20 Nkal a Sibidi kehm koko abon ebe Jon, a Jems, ba a bo goji Jisos, kehm ba gong go ege alata, kehm-e gboongo re, á lub lim ejum ka-e.
\p 
\v 21 Jisos kehm-e bahbe re, “Jen ji a kpꞌsebe me?”
\p Á kehm-e faange re, “Ka abon ebame baa na abal nsahm, eji noko lꞌji go ega ejang eboblum, noko go ega ejang ebobkal ngare nyi a ma jol ntul.”
\p 
\v 22 Owo Jisos kehm faange re, “Ń nehme kahn ji ń kpꞌbꞌbahb. Anv, ḿ bahke ma wo go nkob nyi n yahke ba elwoka?”\f + \fr 20:22 \ft Mat 26:39; Luk 12:50\f*
\p Bo kehm-e faange re, “Ee, e bahke ma wo.”\f + \fr 20:22 \ft Luk 22:33\f*
\p 
\v 23 Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Etingitingi, ḿ bahke lohko wo go egama nkob.\f + \fr 20:23 \ft Elt 12:2; Ell 1:9\f* Me, nsahm n kpimm, nyi m bahke yehke ane, noko ji go egame ejang eboblum, noko ji go egame ejang ebobkal. Adi nyao li ka ane ba wahnge Nsoo toobo bum.”
\p 
\v 24 Abatꞌtoono bako na ewubu wuku kan ano, atahng kehm rake bo tob Jon, a Jems.
\p 
\v 25 Owo Jisos kehm lungu bo tv elne, kehm bungu re, “Ń kpꞌkahne re, atubesi ba njini nyia kpi nsahm nyi bo kpo fili ane. Ajꞌjok ane kpo tob fili ane.
\v 26 Wahn, kana jo lim ano go egahne ellong. Nne awohng awohng ewahne no lꞌseb re á jol njꞌjoka nne, á bahke jolo na nlokeltum ewahne.
\v 27 Nne awohng awohng ewahne no lꞌseb re á jol ntubesi, á bahke fere jol na nlokeltum ewahne,
\v 28 ana Mmon no nne ki ba re bo lok-e, á ba re á ba loko, fere ka elkpin ene, fak ane gbalee yake.”\f + \fr 20:28 \ft Fil 2:7-8; 1 Tim 2:6\f*
\s1 Ana Jisos limi awakamahr abal, bo nyehn
\r (Mak 10:46-52; Luk 18:35-43)
\p 
\v 29 Eji bo jo tahm go Jeriko asongo, ellong ane gbalee kehm tahme toono Jisos.
\p 
\v 30 Awakamahr na abal ji o nkpe a mbang. Eji bo wuku re, Jisos kpꞌbake elsehnge, bo kehm kehme elrabe re, “Mmon no Devid, nong, wahr fil-a ndon!”
\p 
\v 31 Ellong ane bao kehm sahde bo re bo rahke ewok. Bo jo kpe nyennge na rabe re, “Mmon no Devid, nong, wahr fil-a ndon, nsoo!”
\p 
\v 32 Jisos kehm yiimi, lung bo re bo ba. Á kehm bahbe bo re, “Ń kpꞌsebe re me n lim jen ka-n?”
\p 
\v 33 Owo bo kehm-e faange re, “Nsoo, lub lenng-r amahr enyahre!”
\p 
\v 34 Owo Jisos ndon kehm-e fili. Á kehm song kooro bo abo go amahr, bo kehm soro nyehn tvtv, soro tahm toon-e.
\c 21
\s1 Ana Jisos yele go Jeusalem, a egburu ellub
\r (Mak 11:1-11; Luk 19:28-40; Jon 12:12-19)
\p 
\v 1 Eji bo ma kabbe Jeusalem, bo kehm ba rehng go Betfage ji jolo go nnahb ewong ji bo kpo lung re Oliv. Owo Jisos kehm yehke abatꞌtoono ebe, ane na abal,
\v 2 kehm tongo bo re, “Songen ejahbe ji li-n o mbuksong. Owo ḿ bahke nyehne mbvankang nyi bo kahn-e go eti, a mmon ewe. Fanngen bo, wahn ko bo ba ka-m.\f + \fr 21:2 \ft Mak 14:13\f*
\v 3 Nne awohng awohng no lꞌbahb-n ejum bade ebvnkang bio, tongen ye re, ‘Nsoo kpꞌsebe bo,’ nfono ebvnkang bio bahke yake bo elwaare ka.”
\p 
\v 4 Nsol nyia limi, eji lꞌlohko jol go etingitingi ana nnyehnamahr Esowo bungu no re,
\q1 
\v 5 “Tong Sayon re,
\q1 Nyehnen,
\q1 ntul ewahne kpꞌbake go egahne.
\q1 Á li soom,
\q1 á kun go mbvankang.\f + \fr 21:5 \ft Mat 11:29\f*
\q1 Á kun go mmon a nnyam no kpo sol nsol.”
\p 
\v 6 Abatꞌtoono ebe kehm tahme, song lim ana Jisos tongo bo.
\v 7 Bo kehm koko mbvankang nyio, a mmon ba a bo, yehke awobo ebo, kunu go bo a njahm, Jisos kehm wahre, kuumu mmon a mbvankang noo.
\v 8 Ellong ane gbalee kehm yehke awobo ebo, yal go mbang. Ane bandiki song ja amang, jo ba yal go mbang.
\v 9 Ellong ane ba gbo Jisos mbang, a ellong ane ba jo toon-e njahm kehm kehme elrabe re,
\q1 “Tehken mmon no Devid!
\q1 Elfuulu li ka nne no kpꞌbake go mbing nyi Jehova.
\q1 Tehken Esowo bi li go ero!”
\p 
\v 10 Eji Jisos yele go nla Jeusalem, edi kehm kehme elvvrv na vvrv. Ane kehm kehme elbahbe re, “Nne awo ona?”
\p 
\v 11 Owo ellong ane bao kehm jo bung re, “Jisos wo ana, ji li nnyehnamahr. Á lohng go Nasaret nyi Galili.”
\s1 Ana Jisos sehnge song yange go etahk Esowo
\r (Mak 11:15-19; Luk 19:45-48; Jon 2:13-22)
\p 
\v 12 Jisos kehm yange go etahk Esowo, song kam ane ba jo gungu, a ane ba jo gunu, fere gbul akpꞌkuru nya abayaangakpohko tuubu go, a nti nyi abagungumbehl.
\v 13 Á kehm tongo bo re, “Bo nyono go nwer Esowo re, ‘Etahk ejame, bo bahke jo lung re, etahk ero akake.’ Wahn ebfere rod, bum ana ebehre awajv.”\f + \fr 21:13 \ft Rom 2:22\f*
\p 
\v 14 Awakamahr ane, a abanne kehm bake, ba kpir-e go etahk Esowo jio. Á lim bo, bo nob.
\p 
\v 15 Eji atubesi abalimajom, a atꞌtibi ba atahm nyehn akpokosi nya á limi no, fere wuk abonse kpꞌrabe go etahk Esowo jio re, “Tehken mmon no Devid!”\f + \fr 21:15 \ft Mat 1:1\f* atahng kehm rake bo.
\v 16 Owo bo kehm tongo Jisos re, “Wobwuk ana bo kpꞌraba?”
\p Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Ee, n kpꞌwuku. Wo, ń ka tiki lung edi nwer Esowo ji bungu re,
\q1 “ ‘Esowo ebko anyo abonse,
\q1 a nya abonbili, lim,
\q1 eji lꞌjol ejum eltehke ka yefono antahnga?’ ”
\p 
\v 17 Jisos kehm tahme bo sa, song rehng go Betani, fere kang o.
\s1 Ana Jisos nyehne amahr bade efig
\r (Mak 11:12-14,20-24)
\p 
\v 18 Efungfu atv atv eji Jisos feere asongo go Jeusalem, njal kehm-e yame.
\v 19 Á kehm nyehne eti ji bo kpo lung re efig go nkpe a mbang. Á jeere kan kohlo o me, á nyehnem nkab anyehng anyehng, sehngem anyane nya nya á nyehne no.\f + \fr 21:19 \ft Luk 13:6-9\f* Owo á kehm tongo eti jio re, “A nehm kpe tiki kab akab go njinanjini.” Tvtv ona eti jio kehm soro kpo.
\p 
\v 20 Eji abatꞌtoono ebe nyehne ano, kehm kpoko bo esi. Bo kehm bungu re, “Jen ji wahnge eti jia ma tahr kpꞌkpo elwaare elwaare anae?”
\p 
\v 21 Owo Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Ń lꞌtaame, kꞌjo faabe, ḿ bahke jo lim ana m ma lim eti jia, jol sꞌsehnge na ana.\f + \fr 21:21 \ft Jon 14:12\f* Ń li ma tong ewong jia re, ‘Mehl, song yel aya!’ Bahke lohko lim ano.
\v 22 Ejum ajehng ajehng ji ń lꞌbahb go egahne ero bi ń kpꞌkake, ń lꞌtaame, ḿ bahke bele.”
\s1 Ana bo bahbe Jisos bada nsahm enye
\r (Mak 11:27-33; Luk 20:1-8)
\p 
\v 23 Jisos kehm feere go etahk Esowo.
\p Eji á jo tib, atubesi abalimajom, a anebkul nfam kehm bake, ba kpir-e, kehm-e bahbe re, “Nsahm anyi a kpi no, nyi wahnge a kpo lim nsol ana nyia? Nne awo ka-a nsahm ana nyio?”\f + \fr 21:23 \ft Jon 2:18\f*
\p 
\v 24 Jisos kehm faange bo re, “M bahk-n tob bahb mbahbe fvfo. Ń lꞌfaang-m, n kehm-n tongo bada nsahm nyi n kpi no, nyi wahnge n kpo lim nsol ana nyia.
\v 25 Anv, nsahm nyi Jon jo wohngo ane alahb lohng go ejahbetul Esowo baa, afi lohng goji ane?”
\p Bo kehm kehme eltoobo atemtem re, “E lꞌbung re, ‘Nsahm nyi Jon lohng go ejahbetul Esowo’, á bahk-r bahbe re, ‘Jen ji wahnge ń ki taame tv Jon?’
\v 26 E lꞌfere bung re, ‘Nsahm enye lohng goji ane’, ma ane bahk-r limi ejum nji. Tibre e kpꞌfahle bo, tib eji bo kpee jo bum Jon ana nnyehnamahr.”\f + \fr 21:26 \ft Mat 14:5\f*
\v 27 Owo bo kehm faange Jisos re, “Wahr nehme kahn.”
\p Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Fvfo, wahn n nehm tong bada nsahm nyi n kpi no, nyi n kpo ko, lim nsol nyia.
\s1 Elgan ni li bade abon na abal
\p 
\v 28 “Anv ń kpꞌtiri renan bade elgan nia? Nne jolo go, no bele abon na abal. Owo á kehm jeke goji ngbokambang a mmon, kehm song tong-e re, ‘Mmon ewame, song lela go egame egbe, wo song lim eltum.’
\p 
\v 29 “Mmon noo kehm faange re, ‘N nehm je.’ Ji kan mmokidi, á kehm yaange ntir atahng enye, fere tahm egbe nde.
\p 
\v 30 “Owo nde kehm kpe je, song kpiri mmon noko, kehm-e tob tong ano fvfo. Á kehm taame re, ‘Ee nsoo.’ Jol egbe á tikem je.\f + \fr 21:30 \ft Mat 7:21\f*
\p 
\v 31 “Nne awo go abon abal bao limi ji nde tong-e re á lim?” Bo kehm-e faange re, “Ngbokambang a mmon wo.”
\p Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Abakokatak, a abajenasꞌsa ba bahke song yel go ejahbetul Esowo,\f + \fr 21:31 \ft Luk 18:13-14\f* wahn sa elatahk, jo seenge bo.
\v 32 Tibre Jon ji nwohngalahb ba, ba tib-n mbang nyi nno, nyi elsehnge, ń tikem taame tv-e. Abakokatak, a abajenasꞌsa ba taame no tv-e.\f + \fr 21:32 \ft Luk 7:29\f* Jol eji ń nyehne nyehn ano, ń tikem yaange ntir atahng enyahne, fere taame tv-e.”
\s1 Elgan ni li bade abayaame etahngga
\r (Mak 12:1-12; Luk 20:9-19)
\p 
\v 33 Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Wuken elgan nehko! Nne jolo go, no bahme avain, fere kak ega sennge.\f + \fr 21:33 \ft Ef 2:14\f* Á kehm rahme elbing ni bo jo kak akab nti, fere jo kaame akab nti nyao tv elbing nio, alahb jo lohng. Á si enyong, kak ane ba jo baabe edi jio,\f + \fr 21:33 \ft Hib 13:17\f* kehm yaame abahmgbe edi jio, toono eje tahm ejahbe jehko ji li fee.\f + \fr 21:33 \ft Mat 25:14\f*
\p 
\v 34 “Eji ngare nyi bo kpo bong akab nti nyao ma kabbe, owo á kehm tumu alokeltum ebe tv ane ba á yaame bo etahngga eje, eji bo lꞌsong ko akab nti enye, ba ka-e.
\v 35 Abayaame etahngga kehm bobo alokeltum ebe. Noko, bo dv-e, noko, bo wul-e, fere tuubu noko atal, á kpo.
\p 
\v 36 “Owo nfono etahngga kehm kpe tum alokeltum bako gbalee, sehnge ba á gbo mbang tum. Abayaame etahngga tob limi bo jang jang ana bo limi ane bako.
\p 
\v 37 “Esꞌkohro, á gohro tum mmon ewe tv bo. Á bungu re, ‘Bo bahke kake mmon ewame.’
\p 
\v 38 “Eji abayaame etahngga bao nyehne mmon ewe noo kpꞌbake, bo kehm bungu atemtem re, ‘Ye wo li nlehkelkv, nong, wahr song wulen ye, eji etahngga jia lꞌfere jol jꞌjahre.’\f + \fr 21:38 \ft Mat 27:18\f*
\v 39 Bo kehm-e bobo, ro njahm etahngga nyehko, fere song wul-e.
\v 40 Anv, nfono etahngga lꞌba, á bahke limi abayaame etahngga bao renan?”
\p 
\v 41 Bo kehm-e faange re, “Á bahke wulu abi ane bao, bo kpo esabsab elkv, fere yaame ane bako etahngga jio, ba bahke jo ka-e akab nti nyao go ngare nyi nno.”
\p 
\v 42 Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Ń ka tiki lung a lung edi nwer Esowo jia re,
\q1 “ ‘Eltal ni asehketahk tene no,
\q1 ni ni ma fere jol nnahb ekahma?\f + \fr 21:42 \ft 1 Pit 2:6-8\f*
\q1 Jehova limi jia ji li nkpokosi go egahra ntim.’
\p 
\v 43 “Owo wahnge n kp-n tongo re, Esowo bahk-n taare etul ebe, faake a bi, ka ane ba bahk-e kake akab nti go ngare nyi nno.\f + \fr 21:43 \ft 1 Pit 2:9-10\f*
\q1 
\v 44 “Nne no lꞌfooro gbo eltal nio, á bahke banne.
\q1 Wo, nne no eltal nio lꞌgbo nyed-e á bahke rere na rere kpee.”
\p 
\v 45 Atubesi abalimajom, a Bab Farisi wuku kan ngaane enye, bo kehm soro kahn tvtv re, á jo bungu bada bo.
\v 46 Bo kehm gare ana bo bahk-e bobo. Bo jo fahle ellong ane ba jo bum Jisos ana nnyehnamahr.
\c 22
\s1 Elgan ni li bade elkak elbal
\r (Luk 14:15-24)
\p 
\v 1 Jisos kehm kpe tub bo elgan nehko re,
\v 2 “Etul bi Esowo li ana ntul no toobo ebjing bi elkak elbal, ni mmon ewe yahke ko nkal.\f + \fr 22:2 \ft Jon 3:29\f*
\v 3 Á kehm tumu alokeltum ebe re, bo song tong ane ba á tiingi bo elkak re bo ba.\f + \fr 22:3 \ft Ell 19:7\f* Korem bo elbake.
\v 4 Á kehm kpe yehke alokeltum bako, kehm tongo bo re, ‘Songen, wahn song tong ane ba n tiingi bo elkak re, Me n toobo ejum ajehng ajehng kpee bum. Bobwul efong ebame, a atohkondi nya m ma le bo, bo ma jok. Baan go elkak elbal!’
\p 
\v 5 “Ane ba bo tiingi bo elkak, elkak nio lubem bo. Bo tahme na go bo alimi nsol. Noko tahme go ege egbe, noko tahm go ege a nju are.
\v 6 Egom ane bako bobo alokeltum ntul noo, nohk bo, fere wul bo.
\p 
\v 7 “Ntul, atahng rak-e sehng. Á kehm tumu nsoja enye, bo song wul awulane bao, fere jahm ejahbe ebo fi.\f + \fr 22:7 \ft Mat 24:2\f*
\v 8 Owo á kehm tongo alokeltum ebe re, ‘Nsol elkak kpee, me n toobo bum. Ane ba n tiingi bo, bo kpeem fuumu.
\v 9 Songen go ayaame mbang! Nne awohng awohng no ń lꞌnyehn-e, tongen ye, á ba go elkak elbal.’
\p 
\v 10 “Alokeltum bao kehm tahme, jo yannge. Nne awohng awohng no bo nyehn-e no, lꞌkor-e, bo ko-e tahm a ne go elkak. Ane bandiki jolo abi ane,\f + \fr 22:10 \ft Luk 19:1-10\f* bandiki jol anoobo ane.\f + \fr 22:10 \ft Elt 10:1-2\f* Ekpꞌkpa elkak nio kehm ruru ane ane.
\p 
\v 11 “Owo ntul kehm tahme re á song nyehn ane ba jo li nsol. Á kehm nyehne nne no kake ewobo ji ki fuumu elkak elbal nio.
\v 12 Ntul kehm-e bahbe re, ‘Mbi, a limi renan, kehm yele a, kꞌkak ewobo ji fuumu elkak nia?’\f + \fr 22:12 \ft Kol 3:12; Ell 19:8\f*
\p “Nne noo belle na belle eje.
\p 
\v 13 “Owo ntul kehm tongo alokeltum ebe re, ‘Boben ye, wahn gba-e alehke go abo, a akpade akpade, fere ro-e tv go elatahk, edi ejannge jio ji ane kpo woomo, jo ling, fere jo kono amahn go esi.’
\p 
\v 14 “Tibre ane gbalee ba bo tiingi no. Abon amohk ane abik abik ba bo ma jak.”
\s1 Bade etak atahbe
\r (Mak 12:13-17; Luk 20:20-26)
\p 
\v 15 Bab Farisi kehm tahme, song toobo ana bo bahk-e bobo go ege alum nnyo.
\v 16 Bo kehm tumu abatꞌtoono ebo, a aneb ntul a Herod tv goji Jisos. Bo kehm song bahb-e re, “Ntꞌtibi, e kpꞌkahne re, wo etingi nne ji. A kpo tib mbang nyi Esowo go etingitingi. A kpehme rang nnene. Jol esamahr ane, a kpehme be.
\v 17 Tong-r ana a kpꞌtiri bade ejum jia. Nꞌnob re wahr jo tahb etak ka ntul a Roma, afi nobem?”
\p 
\v 18 Jisos kꞌkahn ebi ntir atahng ebo, owo á kehm faange re, “Wahn aneb alum abal abal ba! Jen ji wahnge ń kp-m gare?
\v 19 Tib-m wahn akpohko nya ḿ bahke koko tahb etak.” Bo kehm koko ba a nya.
\p 
\v 20 Jisos kehm bahbe bo re, “Esi jia ji nyehne ji? Mbing nyia nyi nyehne nyi?”
\p 
\v 21 Bo kehm faange re, “Esi jia ji ntul ji. Mbing nyia nyi ntul nyi.”
\p Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Kaan ntul ji li ka ntul,\f + \fr 22:21 \ft Rom 13:1-7; Luk 23:2\f* wahn ka Esowo ji li ka Esowo.”\f + \fr 22:21 \ft 1 Pit 2:17\f*
\p 
\v 22 Eji bo wuku ano, kehm kpoko bo esi. Bo kehm-e yaame sa, tahm ebo.
\s1 Bade elnyahme go elkv
\r (Mak 12:18-27; Luk 20:27-40)
\p 
\v 23 Efung bꞌnehm ona, egom Sadusi jindiki kehm bake ba kpiri Jisos. Bo ba kpo tib re, elnyahme go elkv limm.\f + \fr 22:23 \ft Elt 23:8\f* Owo bo kehm tongo Jisos re,
\v 24 “Ntꞌtibi, Moses bungu re, ‘Nne lꞌkpo, eji á ki jel abon, mmonannyehn nkvne ko nnenkal noo, eji á lꞌjel abon ka mmonannyehn no ma kpo.’
\p 
\v 25 “Abonanyehn na asehma ba jolo a nahre. Ngbokambang ko nkal, mmon awohng awohng á jelem, á kehm kpoko, nkal ewe sa.
\v 26 Ano wo tob lim etoono mmonannyehn, a mmonannyehn noko no toono noo, a erik abonanyehn bako kpee.
\v 27 Esꞌkohro, nnenkal noo tob kpo.
\v 28 Anv, efung bi ane lꞌnyahme go elkv, nne awo á bahke jolo nkal ewe? Tibre bo ane kpee ko-e ana nkal abo.”
\p 
\v 29 Owo Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Ń kpo soodo, tibre ń nehme kahn nwer Esowo, a nsahm nyi Esowo.
\v 30 Ngare nyi ane ma nyahme go elkv, bo bahke jolo ana babenjel. Aneblum nehm kpe jo ko akal. Anebkal nehm kpe jo bal alum.\f + \fr 22:30 \ft 1 Kor 15:44\f*
\v 31 Bade elnyahme ngubjing go elkv, ń ka lung alung ana Esowo tong-n no re,
\v 32 ‘Me wo li Esowo bi Ebraham,\f + \fr 22:32 \ft Luk 16:22\f* a bi Aisik, a bi Jekob.’ Jia lohngo re, Ye li Esowo bio bi ane ba li go elkpin, bi akvne sang.”
\p 
\v 33 Eji ellong ane bao wuku ana á jo tib, kpo bo esi sehng.
\s1 Ntahm nyi ga gbal
\r (Mak 12:28-34; Luk 10:25-28)
\p 
\v 34 Eji Bab Farisi wuku re, Jisos ebga aneb Sadusi, bobbelle, bo kehm song kono edi ajehng.
\v 35 Nne awohng go bo ellong no jolo ntꞌtibi no atahm kehm bake ba bahb Jisos mbahbe, jo gar-e. Á bahb-e re,
\v 36 “Ntꞌtibi, ntahm anyi ga gbal kpee go egahre atahm?”
\p 
\v 37 Owo Jisos kehm-e faange re, “ ‘Esowo, ntul ewa bahke jo kor-a eltim eltim ena, etohko etohko eja, a ntir a ntir enya.’
\v 38 A wo li ngbokambang a ntahm nyi ga gbal.
\v 39 Etoono ntahm tob li na li ana nyio o, nyi li re, ‘Nne ebjing ewa jo kor-a ana ebjing eba.’
\v 40 Atahm nya Moses kpee, a eltibi ni abanyehnamahr tohk ntahm ebal nyia.”\f + \fr 22:40 \ft Rom 13:10; Gal 5:14; 1 Jon 4:20-21\f*
\s1 Mbahbe nyi li bada Mesaya
\r (Mak 12:35-37; Luk 20:41-44)
\p 
\v 41 Ngare nyi Bab Farisi ba kono edi ajehng, Jisos kehm bahbe bo mbahbe re,
\v 42 “Anv, ń kpo tir renan bada Mesaya? Ye mmon a nyehne wo?”
\p Owo bo kehm-e faange re, “Mmon a Devid wo.”
\p 
\v 43 Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Jen ji wahnge Devid lungu Mesaya re, ‘Ntul ewame’, eji Etingi Etohko mehl-e no, á bungu re,
\q1 
\v 44 “ ‘Jehova tongo ntul ewame re,
\q1 Ji go egame ejang eboblum
\q1 tete me n lim anebekv eba etikunakpade eja.’
\p 
\v 45 “Yefono Devid jo lung-e re, ‘Ntul ewame’, bahke limi renan, ntul noo kehm fere jol mmon ewe?”\f + \fr 22:45 \ft Mat 1:1; Ell 5:5\f*
\p 
\v 46 Nnene jolem, no male elfaange Jisos ellum anehng anehng. Bomo efung bio asongo nnene kpeem jo sahb, bahb-e mbahbe.
\c 23
\s1 Ana Jisos jo rehke ane bade atꞌtibi ba atahm, a Bab Farisi
\r (Mak 12:38-39; Luk 11:43,46; 20:45-46)
\p 
\v 1 Jisos kehm tongo ellong ane bao, a abatꞌtoono ebe re,
\v 2 “Atꞌtibi ba atahm, a Bab Farisi ebko nji nyi Moses.
\v 3 Jo bumen ejum ajehng ajehng ji bo lꞌtong-n, wahn fere jo lim. Kana jo toono eljini ni bo! Tibre bo kpehme lim ji bo kpo bung.
\p 
\v 4 “Bo kpo tuuru alublub nsol, nya kpo riidi go elsolo, rod si ane. Jol bofono antahng bo kpehme gare elmehle.
\v 5 Bo kpo lim ejum ajehng ajehng, eji ane lꞌjo nyehn bo. Nyehnen ana awer nya bo kpo kahn go bo abuk, a abo abo kpꞌkpange, nya bo nyono adi nwer Esowo! Nyehnen ana asohk nya bo tohko go asꞌsili akpawobo ebo kpꞌlabe!
\v 6 Go elkak, kpo kor bo re, bo ji adi nya fuumu re ajꞌjok ane ji.\f + \fr 23:6 \ft Luk 14:7\f* Go ekpꞌkpa ero, kpo kor bo re, bo ji mbuksong.
\v 7 Go are, kpo kor bo re, ane jo gong kak bo nnyo, fere jo lung bo re atꞌtibi.
\p 
\v 8 “Nong, ane ki-n jo lung re atꞌtibi. Tibre nne awohng wo wo li ntꞌtibi ewahne. Wahn kpee abonanyehn ba.
\v 9 Kana jo lung nne awohng awohng go njini nyia re Nso ejahne. Tibre nne awohng wo wo li Nso ejahne, ye jio ji li go ejahbetul.
\v 10 Nong, ane ki-n jo lung re atubesi. Tibre nne awohng wo wo li ntubesi ewahne, ye ji li Mesaya.
\p 
\v 11 “Nne no lꞌga gbal go egahne ellong, ye wo bahke jolo nlokeltum ewahne.
\v 12 Nne awohng awohng no lꞌmehl elne wahre, bo bahk-e rede na. Nne awohng awohng no lꞌrede elne, bo bahk-e mehle wahre.\f + \fr 23:12 \ft Luk 18:14; 1 Pit 5:5\f*
\s1 Ana Jisos jo wa Bab Farisi eyuu
\r (Mak 12:40; Luk 11:39-52; 13:34-35; 20:47)
\p 
\v 13 “Eyuu a nahne, wahn atꞌtibi ba atahm, a Farisis! Wahn aneb alum abal abal ba! Ń kpo bam ejahbetul Esowo tv ane.\f + \fr 23:13 \ft Jon 9:22\f* Ń kpehme taame, yake ane ba kpꞌgare re bo yel. Wahnfono antahng nehm yel.
\p 
\v 14 “Eyuu a nahne, wahn atꞌtibi ba atahm, a Farisis! Wahn aneb alum abal abal ba! Ń kpo nehm akalebun, taare ntahk ebo. Eyaame jehko, ń kpo kak alaabe aro, jo tib elnahne. Tib esi jio ji bahke wahnge elam ejahne sahb gbꞌgbal!
\p 
\v 15 “Eyuu a nahne, wahn atꞌtibi ba atahm, a Farisis! Wahn aneb alum abal abal ba! Ń kpo yannge go njini kpee, jo siiri agburu aya, eji ń lꞌlub were nne awohng, á fere yel-n. Ń lꞌting nne, ń rod-e, lim mmon ellulagun no sahb sꞌsab sehnge wahnfono antahng.
\p 
\v 16 “Eyuu a nahne, wahn awakamahr ane ba kpo tib ane mbang! Ń kpo tib re, ‘Nne awohng awohng no lꞌtir etahk Esowo, ejumjum limm. Wo, nne no lꞌfere tir agul nya li go etahk Esowo, á bahke tiki lim, nehm tiki kane.’
\v 17 Wahn agboolo awakamahr ba! Anv, ejum aji ga gbal, agul, afi etahk Esowo ji wahnge agul nyao li saang?
\v 18 Ń kpo kpe tib re, ‘Nne awohng awohng no lꞌtir edi njom alimi, ejumjum limm. Wo, nne no lꞌfere tir ejum njom ji kun edi njom alimi jio, á bahke tiki lim, nehm kane.’
\p 
\v 19 “Wahn agboolo awakamahr ba! Anv, ejum aji ga gbal, ejum njom, afi edi njom alimi ji wahnge ejum njom li saang?
\v 20 Fvfo, nne lꞌtir edi njom alimi, yebtir edi njom alimi jio, a nsol njom kpee nyi kun o.
\v 21 Nne no lꞌtir etahk Esowo, yebtir etahk Esowo, a Esowo bi lene o.
\v 22 Nne no lꞌtir ejahbetul Esowo, yebtir eti etul ji Esowo, a nne no jehk o.\f + \fr 23:22 \ft Mat 5:34\f*
\p 
\v 23 “Eyuu a nahne, wahn atꞌtibi ba atahm, a Farisis! Wahn aneb alum abal abal ba! Ń kpo ka eltahme go abon asahkesahke nsol ana nkambe, nfehne, a abehne, fere gbake alahmlahm nsol ana elam,\f + \fr 23:23 \ft Hib 9:27\f* ndon,\f + \fr 23:23 \ft Luk 1:78; Jems 2:13\f* a eltaame,\f + \fr 23:23 \ft Hib 11:6\f* bum go nkpe. Limen nsol ebal ebal, kana gbake ajehng bum go nkpe!
\p 
\v 24 “Wahn awakamahr ane ba kpo tib ane mbang ba! Ń kpo yehke nnyamnyame go egahne alahb elwoko, fere mele ekamel!
\p 
\v 25 “Eyuu a nahne, wahn atꞌtibi ba atahm, a Farisis! Wahn aneb alum abal abal ba! Tibre ń kpo ru njahm a nkob, a njahm ekpingi. Go atahng, nsol ejv ebrur, a nsol nyi ń kpo lahm ane bako etong.\f + \fr 23:25 \ft Mak 7:4\f*
\v 26 Wo nwakamahr a nne a Farisi wo! Gbo mbang ru atahng nkob, a atahng ekpingi, eji njahm lꞌtob bar.
\p 
\v 27 “Eyuu a nahne, wahn atꞌtibi ba atahm, a Farisis! Wahn li ana alahm nya bo ma taame efem go njahm elatahk, ma nob. Go atahng, akahb akvne nya ma rur, a nsol eltehb.
\v 28 Ana wo fvfo ń tob li. Go njahm elatahk ń kpo jol nne awohng awohng, are ń li nob nob. Go atahng, abꞌbi nya ma rur, a afahnge afahnge.\f + \fr 23:28 \ft Ell 3:1\f*
\p 
\v 29 “Eyuu a nahne, wahn atꞌtibi ba atahm, a Farisis! Wahn aneb alum abal abal ba! Wahn ba kake alahm nya abanyehnamahr Esowo, fere liibi alahm nya atingitingi ane,
\v 30 fere jo bung re, ‘Li re e jolo ngare nyi babnso ejahre, kehn, e jolem limi ana bo limi no, fere wul abanyehnamahr Esowo.’
\v 31 Wahnfono antahng ebyiimi ntianse re wahn ba li abon ba ane ba wulu abanyehnamahr.\f + \fr 23:31 \ft Elt 7:52,56\f*
\v 32 Wahn ebba soro asi, kpꞌgohro lim ji babnso ejahne limi no sa.
\p 
\v 33 “Wahn enyo bia, wahn abon akumbad baa, ḿ bahke ma for renan go elam ji bo bahk-n lame, kim ebi ka-n, fere kak-n go ellulagun?
\v 34 Owo wahng ka m bahke tumu abanyehnamahr tv-n, fere tum akahnkahn ane, fere tum atꞌtibi. Egom jindiki, ḿ bahke wulu bo, jindiki, ń kum bo lake go akros, jindiki, ḿ bahke jo dv bo go egahna ntahk ero, fere jo kam bo yannge ajahbe ajahbe ajahbe,
\v 35 eji ń lꞌli ebi tib go atingitingi ane ba bo wulu bo go njini kpee, bomo goji Ebel ji jolo etingi nne tete ba rehng goji Sekaraya ji jolo mmon a Barakaya, ye ji ń wul-e no go elka elka ni etahk Esowo, a edi njom alimi.
\p 
\v 36 “Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Ane ba li anv bahke lehke ebi tib go nsol nyio kpee.
\p 
\v 37 “O Jeusalem, Jeusalem! Wahn ba kpꞌwulu abanyehnamahr Esowo, fere tuubu ane ba Esowo tumu bo tv-n atal. Nkpel tvv n jo gare re me n lung-n tv elname, ana nkok kpo lung abon ebe tv elne, fere walle bo go ege akpungkpung. Wahn joom kor elbake.
\p 
\v 38 “Etahk ejahne bahke sake nehme nehme.
\p 
\v 39 “N kp-n tongo re, Bomo anv asongo, me n nehm kpe nyehn, tete ngare nyi ḿ bahke bungu re, ‘Elfuulu li ka nne no kpꞌbake go mbing nyi Ntul!’ ”
\c 24
\s1 Ana bo bahke rannge etahk Esowo
\r (Mak 13:1-2; Luk 21:5-6)
\p 
\v 1 Jisos kehm lohngo go etahk Esowo jio tahm. Abatꞌtoono ebe kehm bake, ba tib-e ntahk nyi bo si go nlaaga nyi etahk Esowo jolo no.
\p 
\v 2 Owo Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Nyehnen ntahk nyia a kpee! Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Jol eltal anehng anehng limm, ni bahke kpe kuumu a ntem.\f + \fr 24:2 \ft Luk 19:44\f* Bo bahke wake kpee, wohng ndi.”
\s1 Erem, a afemfem
\r (Mak 13:3-13; Luk 21:7-19)
\p 
\v 3 Eji Jisos song ji go ewong ji bo kpo lung re Oliv, owo abatꞌtoono ebe kehm song kpir-e bo bo, kehm-e bahbe re, “Tong-r ngare nyi ejum jio bahke limi, wo fere tib-r elliingi ni bahke tibi elbake ena ni a bahke bake, a ni esꞌkohro eying jia.”
\p 
\v 4 Owo Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Kunen ekpu, eji nne awohng awohng lꞌki-n nehm.
\v 5 Tibre ane gbalee bahke bake go egama mbing, jo ba bung re, ‘Me wo li Mesaya.’ Toono o, bo nehm ane gbalee.\f + \fr 24:5 \ft Elt 5:36-37; 1 Jon 2:18\f*
\v 6 Ḿ bahke kehme elwuku bada nta, fere jo wuk aka nta. Kana jo fahl! Tibre nsol nyia kpee bahke tiki lim, jol o esꞌkohro sang ma rehng na.
\v 7 Ajahbe nyandiki bahke jo nok atemtem. Ajahbe nyandiki bahke kehme elnoko a atem ajahbe nyako! Njal, a ayam nya kpo sehnge ane, go ndi agbehke bahke jo jol adi adi.
\v 8 Nsol nyia kpee nyi li mbomannahb erem.
\p 
\v 9 “Ngare nyio nyi bo bahke jo bob-n, song ka re bo kak-n erem, fere wul-n. Ane kpee bahk-n jo ko ekv tib go egama mbing.\f + \fr 24:9 \ft Jon 16:2; Ell 13:15,17\f*
\v 10 Ane gbalee bahke kehme elseele gbo, tibre bo bahke jo jabbe atemtem ka go, fere jo ko atemtem ekv.
\p 
\v 11 “Akimfahnge abanyehnamahr gbalee bahke longo ba, ba nehm ane gbalee.\f + \fr 24:11 \ft 1 Jon 4:1\f*
\v 12 Owo eji abꞌbi ma tv ano, elkoro ni ane gbalee bahke kehme elmale.\f + \fr 24:12 \ft 2 Tim 3:1-5\f*
\v 13 Nne no lꞌyiimi tꞌtahne go mbang nyi Esowo tete rehng go esꞌkohro, ye wo bahke bele eltahre.
\v 14 Ngare nyi bo ma tiingi nnoobo etib bade etul bi Esowo tong njini kpee ana ejum ntianse, owo esꞌkohro bahke kehm rehnge.
\s1 Ejum ji kpꞌsahb sꞌsab
\r (Mak 13:14-23; Luk 21:20-24)
\p 
\v 15 “Ḿ bahke nyehne ‘ejum ji kpꞌsahb sꞌsab, ji bahke rannge edi’, ji nnyehnamahr a Daniel bungu no bade, yim go mbarebare edi.\f + \fr 24:15 \ft 2 Tes 2:4\f* Nne no lꞌlung nsol nyia, nong á kahn.
\p 
\v 16 “Ngare nyio nyi ane ba li go Judea bahke beke, tahm go awong.
\v 17 Nne no lꞌkuumu go ege ero etahk, á kꞌtohko seb elyele go ekpꞌkpa, song rod ejum fili.\f + \fr 24:17 \ft Luk 17:31\f*
\v 18 Nne no lꞌjol go ege egbe, á kꞌtohko be, ba etahk, ba rod nsol ebjing enye.
\p 
\v 19 “Eyuu a anebkal ba bahke jolo ela ngare nyio, a anebkal ba kpi abon go ebo.
\v 20 Kaken ero, eji elbeke enahne ni ḿ bahke beke lꞌkꞌjol ngara nnale, kꞌfere jol efung Esabat.
\v 21 Tibre erem bio bahke gbale sehng. Jol erem ana bio ka jol a jol ejolojolo bomo eji njini bomo no tete rehng anv. Jol nehm kpe tiki jol ano ejolojolo.
\p 
\v 22 “Tohko jol re Esowo tele afung nyao kahbe, nnene nehm jol no bahke bele eltahre. Tib go esi ji ane ba Esowo ma yehke, owo wahnge Esowo bahke tele afung nyao kahbe.
\p 
\v 23 “Ngare nyio, nne lꞌtong-n re, ‘Nyehnen, Kraist ga!’ afi á tong-n re, ‘Nyehnen Kraist go!’ kana taame tv-e.
\v 24 Akimfahnge ane bahke lohngo ba, jo ba bung re, Bo ba li Mesaya. Egom jindiki bahke jo bung re, Bo ba li abanyehnamahr Esowo. Bo bahke kehme nliingi tib, fere jo lim akpokosi, eji limi limi kan, bo lꞌnehm aneb Esowo, ba Esowo ma jak.\f + \fr 24:24 \ft 2 Tes 2:9; Ell 13:13\f*
\v 25 Kunen ekpu, m ma-n tong jia ana, re ngare kehm rehnge.
\p 
\v 26 “Ane lꞌkehm-n tongo re, ‘Nyehnen, ye go elka emahng!’ kana je go! Bo lꞌfere tong-n re, ‘Nyehnen, ye ga nkimi nyia!’ kana taame tv bo.
\v 27 Ana emangedu kpo lim, lennge duu, bomo go ero nfam tete rehng go erede nfam, ano wo elbake ni Mmon no nne bahke jolo.\f + \fr 24:27 \ft Luk 17:23-24\f*
\v 28 Tibre edi ajehng ajehng ji ekpakv ejum lꞌnoongo, owo ntere bahke jeke song rur.\f + \fr 24:28 \ft Ell 19:17,21\f*
\s1 Elbake ni Mmon no nne
\r (Mak 13:24-27; Luk 21:25-28)
\p 
\v 29 “Ngare nyi erem bio ma mal,
\q1 “njul bahke dvvrv,
\q1 ebareka nehm kpe jo ya na eyakeyake.
\q1 Alonlo bahke kehme elfooro go elbung gbo.
\q1 Atahm nya elbung bahke range.\f + \fr 24:29 \ft 2 Pit 3:10\f*
\p 
\v 30 “Owo ane bahke kehm nyehne elliingi ni Mmon no nne go elbung. Ane kpee ba li go njini bahke kehme ellingi, fere nyehn Mmon no nne kpꞌbake go akparesemsem, a nsahm a nsahm, a egburu ellub.\f + \fr 24:30 \ft Ell 1:7; 19:11\f*
\v 31 Owo enjel bahke woro ntang wahre wahre.\f + \fr 24:31 \ft 1 Tes 4:16; 1 Kor 15:52; Ell 10:7\f* Á bahke tumu babenjel tv ejang njini abehng abehng, a ejang elbung abehng abehng, eji bo lꞌsong ko ane ba á jake bo, ba a bo edi ajehng.
\s1 Ejum elkpili ji li bade efig
\r (Mak 13:28-31; Luk 21:29-33)
\p 
\v 32 “Kpilen ejum go elgan ni li bade eti ji bo kpo lung re efig.\f + \fr 24:32 \ft Luk 13:6-9; Elt 15:16\f* Eji eti jio ma nyono, fere kak anyane, owo ḿ bahke kahne re, nnale ebba.
\v 33 Tob li ka-n fvfo re, ń lꞌnyehn nsol nyio kpꞌlimi, owo ḿ bahke kehm kahne re, ngare ebkabbe kpidi kpidi.
\p 
\v 34 “Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Ane bao ba bahke jolo go elkpin ngare nyio, bo nehm kpo, tete nsol nyio lim kpee.
\v 35 Elbung abola ndi bahke tane, alum enyame nehm tiki tan.”
\s1 Nnene limm, no kpꞌkahne ngare nyio
\r (Mak 13:32-37; Luk 17:26-30,34-36)
\p 
\v 36 “Nnene nehme kahn efung bio, a ngare nyio, jol babenjel ba li go ejahbetul Esowo nehme kahn, jol Mmon nehme kahn, sehngem Nsoo ntahngtahng wo kpꞌkahne.\f + \fr 24:36 \ft Elt 1:7\f*
\p 
\v 37 “Ana jolo go ngare nyi Noa, ano wo fvfo bahke tob jol ngare nyi Mmon no nne bahke bake.
\v 38 Ana wo jolo no ngare nyi nnyel nyi bulu njini kala yel. Ane bao jo li nsol, fere jo wꞌwo. Aneblum jo ko akal, anebkal jo bal alum tete rehng efung bi Noa yele go egbang.
\v 39 Tvtv o bo joom kahn ji kpꞌlꞌlim, tete nnyel yel, ba feenge bo kpee, tahm abo.
\p “Ano wo fvfo bahke tob jol ngare nyi Mmon no nne bahke bake.\f + \fr 24:39 \ft 2 Pit 3:5-7\f*
\v 40 Ngare nyio ane abal bahke jolo go egbe, noko, bo bahk-e koko, noko sa.
\v 41 Anebkal abal bahke jo gok nsol, noko, bo bahk-e koko, noko sa.
\p 
\v 42 “Jo baaben, tibre ń nehme kahn efung bi Ntul ewahne bahke bake.
\v 43 Ji fuumu re wahn kahn, li re, nfontahk kꞌkahn ngare nyi nwajv bahke bake atv, kehn á jol baabe, á jolem taame re, bo ba lahm etahk eje ye.\f + \fr 24:43 \ft Luk 12:39-40\f*
\v 44 Owo fvfo nobo re wahn toobo ebjing kpee. Tibre Mmon no nne bahke gbede na ba ngare nyi ń ki bum re á kpꞌbake.
\s1 Nnooba nlokeltum, a ebi nlokeltum
\r (Luk 12:41-48)
\p 
\v 45 “Nne awo li ekahnkahn nlokeltum no kpi ekakesehk? Ye wo li nne no nde ma yake alokeltum bako kak go ege ebo re á jo le bo go ngare.\f + \fr 24:45 \ft Jon 21:15,17\f*
\v 46 Eyebatahng bahke jolo a nlokeltum noo no nde lꞌba, á bahke ba kpir-e, á kpꞌlimi ano.\f + \fr 24:46 \ft 1 Kor 4:2\f*
\v 47 Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Nde bahke faake a nsol enye kpee, kak-e go ebo.\f + \fr 24:47 \ft Mat 25:21,23\f*
\p 
\v 48 “Á lꞌfere jol ebi nlokeltum, á bahke bungu go ege eltim re, ‘Nsoo nehme waka ba.’
\v 49 Á bahke kehme alokeltum bako dv, fere jo jen a abawokamahm, jo li nsol a bo, fere jo wꞌwo.
\v 50 Owo nde nlokeltum noo bahke kehnge efung bi á ki ekpu kunu, a ngare nyi á kil kahne.
\v 51 Nde bahk-e bomo, kiimi akv akv akv, fere rod-e, kak edi ji ane ba kpi alum abal abal wob no. Owo ane bahke woomo, jo ling, fere jo kono amahn go esi.
\c 25
\s1 Elgan ni li bada ngbahme na ewubu
\p 
\v 1 “Etul bi Esowo bahke jolo ana ngbahme na ewubu nyi rodo atꞌrekahng ebo, tahm re bo song wane nlumanne.\f + \fr 25:1 \ft Luk 12:35-36; Ell 19:7\f*
\v 2 Ngbahme na elon jolo akahnkahn. Ngbahme nyehko na elon jolo agboolo.
\v 3 Agboolo agbahme nyao rodo atꞌrekahng ebo, akehng bo filem.
\v 4 Akahnkahn agbahme nyao rodo atꞌrekahng, fere fili akpuma akehng budu.
\p 
\v 5 “Eji nlumanne laange elbake, agbahme nyao kpee kehm kehme amahke lal, soro sa lal.
\v 6 Nlum atv, nne jo rꞌrabe re, ‘Nyehnen, nlumanne kpꞌbake! Songen, wahn song wan-e!’
\p 
\v 7 “Agbahme nyao kpee kehm mehle, toobo atꞌrekahng ebo bum.
\v 8 Owo agboolo nyao kehm tongo akahnkahn re, ‘Nyahken akehng emahne ka-r, tibre atꞌrekahng enyahre yahke lahme.’
\p 
\v 9 “Owo akahnkahn kehm faange bo re, ‘Akehng maa nehm biingi rehng egahne. Songen goji abajenare, wahn song gunu antahng.’
\p 
\v 10 “Eji bo tahme no re bo song gunu akehng, nlumanne kehm bake. Ane bao ba toobo ebjing kehm tahme toon-e, song rehng go elkak elbal. Bo kehm bame mbu.
\p 
\v 11 “Ji kan a, agbahme nyako kehm tob ba, ba kehme elbungu re, ‘Nsoo, nsoo, lenng-r mbu!’\f + \fr 25:11 \ft Luk 13:25-27\f*
\p 
\v 12 “Owo á kehm faange bo re, ‘Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Wahn n nehme kahn!’ ”
\v 13 Jisos kehm gohro bung re, “Jo kunen ekpu, tibre n nehme kahn efung, a ngare nyi Mmon no nne bahke bake.
\s1 Elgan ni li bade alokeltum na ara
\r (Luk 19:11-27)
\p 
\v 14 “Etul bi Esowo bahke jolo ana nne no yahke ba eltahme eljen. Á kehm lungu alokeltum ebe, yake nsol enye, kak go bo abo.\f + \fr 25:14 \ft Mat 21:33\f*
\v 15 Á ka nne awohng awohng ana á bahke ma lim. Noko, á ka-e ekpa akpohko eblon, noko, ekpa akpohko ebbal, noko ajehng, kehm soro tahm eje.\f + \fr 25:15 \ft Rom 12:6\f*
\v 16 Nne no ko ekpa akpohko eblon kehm soro tahm, song jen are, li nsehng go ekpa akpohko eblon.
\v 17 Ano wo nne no ko ekpa ebbal tob li nsehng ekpa ebbal fvfo.
\v 18 Nne no ko ekpa ajehng kehm song rahm elbing, rod akpohko nde, kak o behr.
\p 
\v 19 “Eji ma sahb kꞌkang, nde alokeltum bao kehm kehnge, kehm ba tong alokeltum ebe re, bo ba toobo akpohko enye ka-e.
\p 
\v 20 “Nlokeltum no ko ekpa akpohko eblon kehm koko ekpa akpohko eblon behko budu, ba a bi, kehm bungu re, ‘Nsoo, a ka-m ekpa akpohko eblon, nyehn ekpa akpohko eblon behka gana bi m ma li nsehng.’
\p 
\v 21 “Owo nde kehm-e tongo re, ‘Woblim sehng, nkakesehk a nlokeltum no nno. Eji a bele ekakesehk go abonsꞌsohko abon nsol, m bahke yake agburu nsol, kak-a go ebo.\f + \fr 25:21 \ft Luk 16:10\f* Ba yel ga, wo bel eyebatahng ana n kpi no.’
\p 
\v 22 “Nne no ko ekpa akpohko ebbal kehm tob ba, ba bung re, ‘Nsoo, a ka-m ekpa akpohko ebbal, nyehn ekpa ebbal behka bi m ma li nsehng.’
\p 
\v 23 “Owo nde kehm-e tongo re, ‘Woblim sehng, nkakesehk a nlokeltum no nno. Eji a bele ekakesehk go abonsꞌsohko abon nsol, m bahke yake agburu nsol, kak-a go ebo. Ba yel ga, wo bel eyebatahng ana n kpi no.’
\p 
\v 24 “Nne no ko ekpa akpohko ajehng kehm tob ba, ba bung re, ‘Nsoo, n kpꞌkahne re, wo ebibbib nne ji. Á kpo kpa ji a ki bahm, fere fv nya a ki kak.
\v 25 N jo fꞌfahl, owo n kehm tahme song behr akpohko enya go ndi. Nyehn nyanya ana.’
\p 
\v 26 “Owo nde kehm-e faange re, ‘Wo ebi nlokeltum wo, no ma gbo ewon. Á kꞌkahn re, n kpo kpa ji n ki bahm, fere fv nya n ki kak.
\v 27 Kehn nde, a jol kake abajenare akpohko enyame, n lꞌba, m ba ko, fere ko nsehng budu.\f + \fr 25:27 \ft 2 Kor 6:1\f*
\v 28 Taaren ye ekpa akpohko jio, wahn ka nne no kpi ekpa ebwubu.
\p 
\v 29 “ ‘Tibre nne awohng awohng no kpi no, bo bahk-e kake na budu, á bel gbalee. Nne no ki kpi, jol ntiil ana á kpi no, bo bahk-e taare na.
\v 30 Roden edemme nlokeltum noa, ro tv elatahk edi ejannge. Owo nne bahke woomo, jo ling, fere jo kono amahn go esi.’
\s1 Ana Mmon no nne bahke lame njini
\p 
\v 31 “Ngare nyi Mmon no nne bahke bake go ege ellub, a enjel kpee, á bahke jehke go eti etul jio ji ellub ene.\f + \fr 25:31 \ft Ell 20:11-15\f*
\v 32 Ane ba li go njini kpee, bo bahke koko bo, ba yiimi go ege esamahr. Owo á bahke kehm yabe bo ana mbaabebul kpo yab ejoro, bum eje eje, ebulbaange jol eje eje.\f + \fr 25:32 \ft Jon 5:29\f*
\v 33 Á bahke rodo ejoro, bum ege ejang eboblum, fere rod ebulbaange, bum ege ejang ebobkal.
\v 34 Owo ntul bahke kehm tongo ane ba yiim-e go ege ejang eboblum re, ‘Baan, wahn jia ji Nsoo ma-n fuulu! Baan, wahn ba li etul bi Esowo ma toobo bum-n, bi lohng eji njini bomo na bom.
\v 35 Tibre njal jo yam-m yam, ń jo ka-m, n li. Alahb kor-m kor, ń ka-m, n wo. N yel-n ejen, ń vvr-m.
\v 36 N jolo ebun ebun, ń ka-m, m bobo. N jo yꞌyam, ḿ ba, ba nyehn-m. N woomo go ngbekobo, ḿ ba, ba nyehn-m.’
\p 
\v 37 “Owo atingitingi ane bao bahk-e kehm faange re, ‘Ntul, ntahn wo e nyehn-a no, njal ma-a yam, e ka-a, a li? Ntahn wo e nyehn-a no, alahb ma-a kor, e ka-a, a wo?
\v 38 Ntahn wo e nyehn-a no ana njenne, e kehm-a vvrv?\f + \fr 25:38 \ft Hib 13:2\f* Ntahn wo e nyehn-a ebun ebun, e kehm-a kake, a bobo?
\v 39 Ntahn wo e nyehn-a no, a kpꞌyame, jol go ngbekobo, e kehm ba nyehn-a?’
\p 
\v 40 “Owo ntul noo bahke kehm faange bo re, ‘Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Ngare anyehng anyehng nyi ń jo lim ano ka nne awohng no sahb rꞌrede go ellong abonanee ba li a, ń jo limi ka me.’\f + \fr 25:40 \ft Hib 2:11\f*
\p 
\v 41 “Owo á bahke kehm tongo ane ba yiim-e go ege ejang ebobkal re, ‘Fak-m wahn go esamahr, wahn ji Esowo ma-n su. Songen go ellulagun ni li go njinanjini, ni bo ma toobo bum nnehm, a enjel enye.\f + \fr 25:41 \ft Ell 20:10,15\f*
\v 42 Tibre njal yam-m yam, me ń kaam, n li. Alahb kor-m kor, me ń kaam, n wo.
\v 43 N yel-n ejen, me ń vvrem. N jolo ebun ebun, me ń kaam, m bobo. N jo yꞌyam, fere woomo go ngbekobo, ḿ baam, ba nyehn-m.’
\p 
\v 44 “Owo bofono bahke tob faange re, ‘Ntul, ntahn wo e nyehn-a no, njal kp-a yame, alahb jo kor-a? Ntahn wo e nyehn-a no ana njenne? Ntahn wo e nyehn-a no ebun ebun? Ntahn wo e nyehn-a no, a kpꞌyame? Ntahn wo e nyehn-a no, a wob go ngbekobo? Ntahn wo e nyehn-a ano, ki-a kak ebo?’
\p 
\v 45 “Owo á bahke kehm faange bo re, ‘Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Ngare anyehng anyehng nyi ń ki jo lim ano ka nne awohng no sahb rꞌrede go ellong abonanee ba li a, ń limem ka me.’
\p 
\v 46 “Ane baa bahke song yel go edi erem, jo nyehn erem o go njinanjini. Atingitingi ane bahke bele elkpin ni li go njinanjini.”
\c 26
\s1 Ana bo lame kak Jisos
\r (Mak 14:1-2; Luk 22:1-2; Jon 11:45-53)
\p 
\v 1 Eji Jisos ma bung alum nyaa kpee mal, á kehm tongo abatꞌtoono ebe re,
\v 2 “Ń kpꞌkahne re, lela ebsa nfung ebal, elkak Pasova rehng. Efung bio bi bo bahke jabbe Mmon no nne ka re bo kum-e go ekros.”\f + \fr 26:2 \ft 1 Kor 5:7\f*
\p 
\v 3 Owo atubesi abalimajom, a anebkul nfam kehm song kono go nlaaga ntubesi abalimajom no bo jo lung-e re Kayafas.
\v 4 Owo bo toobo no ana bo bahke bobo Jisos mbehr mbehr, song wul.
\p 
\v 5 Bo jo bungu re, “Nong, wahr kꞌlim ngare elkak, eji lꞌkꞌgbo ntong.”
\s1 Ana bo wohngo Jisos akehng
\r (Mak 14:3-9; Jon 12:1-8)
\p 
\v 6 Eji Jisos jolo go Betani go etahk Saimon ji nne abili,
\v 7 nnenkal awohng kehm bake go ege, no fili elom akehng ji nno a nno, ji sahb kꞌkim ekun. Á kehm yaange akehng mao, kak-e go esi ngare nyi á jehk go ekpꞌkuru kpi nsol li.
\p 
\v 8 Eji abatꞌtoono ebe nyehne ano, atahng kehm rake bo. Bo kehm bahbe re, “Jen ji wahnge á kpꞌfade akehng ana maa?
\v 9 Kehn akehng maa bo jol gungu, ko akpohko gbalee, fere ko, ka akpak.”
\p 
\v 10 Jisos sebe kan kahn ana bo jo bung, á kehm tongo bo re, “Jen ji wahnge ń kpꞌgbiingi mmonankal noa? Yeblim nnoobo ka-m.
\v 11 Akpak li a nahne ngare anyehng anyehng, wo, me n limm a nahne ngare anyehng anyehng.
\v 12 Tibre eji mmonankal noa wohng-m akehng go egama ngubjing, á toobo ebjing ebame bum, bi m bahke kpoko.\f + \fr 26:12 \ft Mak 16:1\f*
\v 13 Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Edi ajehng ajehng go njini kpee, ji bo bahke tiingi nnoobo etib bia, bo bahke tob jo bung jia ji nnenkal noa ma lim, fere jo buum-e.”
\s1 Ana Judas gungu Jisos
\r (Mak 14:10-11; Luk 22:3-6)
\p 
\v 14 Nne awohng go ellong abatꞌtoono Jisos, ewubu ane abal, no bo jo lung-e re Judas Iskariot kehm tahme, song kpiri atubesi abalimajom,
\v 15 kehm bahbe bo re, “Ejum aji ḿ bahk-m kake, n lꞌjabbe Jisos, kak-n go ebo?”
\p Bo kehm-e kake mpon esehma.\f + \fr 26:15 \ft Jon 11:57; 1 Tim 6:9-10\f*
\v 16 Bomo ngare nyio asongo, Judas kehm kehme mbang seb ana nyi á bahke jabbe Jisos ka bo.
\s1 Ana Jisos li elkak Pasova, a abatꞌtoono ebe
\r (Mak 14:12-21; Luk 22:7-14,21-23; Jon 13:21-30)
\p 
\v 17 Ngbokambang efung elkak ni Jus kpo li abred nya bo kil jo kak ayist, abatꞌtoono Jisos kehm ba kpir-e, fere bahb-e re, “Gan wo a kpꞌsebe re wahr song toobo nsol alehke nyi elkak Pasova bum-a?”
\p 
\v 18 Á kehm tongo bo re, “Songen go nla ejahbe goji nne awohng, wahn song tong-e re, ‘Ntꞌtibi re, Ngare enyame ebkabbe. M bahke lehke elkak Pasova, a abatꞌtoono ebame go ega etahk.’ ”
\p 
\v 19 Abatꞌtoono Jisos kehm song toobo nsol elkak Pasova nio bum, ana Jisos tongo bo.
\p 
\v 20 Eji elgung ma ba, Jisos kehm song ji go ekpꞌkuru, jo li nsol, a abatꞌtoono ebe, ewubu ane abal.
\v 21 Eji bo jo li nsol o, á kehm bungu re, “Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Nne awohng ewahne bahk-m jabbe ka go.”
\p 
\v 22 Ndon kehm fili bo. Bo kehm-e kehme elbahbe. No nne re, “Nsoo, me wo afi?”
\p 
\v 23 Owo á kehm faange bo re, “Nne no kpꞌna tohko ebred eje ekpingi ajehng a name, ye wo li nne no bahk-m jabbe ka.\f + \fr 26:23 \ft Jon 13:18\f*
\v 24 Mmon no nne bahke kpoko jang jang ana bo nyono bada ne. Eyuu a nne no bahke jabbe Mmon no nne ka.\f + \fr 26:24 \ft Luk 17:1\f* Jol ga nob, li re nne noo bo we jelem.”
\p 
\v 25 Judas ji gung-e no kehm bahbe re, “Ntꞌtibi, anv, me woa?”
\p Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Ee, wo wo.”
\s1 Nsol alehke nyi elbuumu Jisos
\r (Mak 14:22-26; Luk 22:15-20; 1 Kor 11:23-25)
\p 
\v 26 Eji bo kpi nlehke nlehke nsol, Jisos kehm rodo ebred, kak Esowo saam, fere bakke, ka abatꞌtoono ebe, kehm bungu re, “Koon, wahn li! A wo li ngubjing enyame.”
\p 
\v 27 Owo á kehm rodo nkob, kak Esowo saam, kehm kake bo, kehm bungu re, “Woon, wahn ane kpee!
\v 28 Tibre a wo li alung emame ma egbanngalung ji nfenfe, ma kpꞌfabe ka ane gbalee, eji bo lꞌbel eltahmeka go bo abiafem.
\v 29 N kp-n tongo re, N nehm kpe wo alahb avain maa tete efung bio rehng bi m bahke kpe wo a nahne go ejahbetul ji Nsoo.”
\v 30 Owo bo kehm yimi ese, kehm lohngo tahm go ewong ji bo kpo lung re Oliv.\f + \fr 26:30 \ft Luk 22:39; Jon 18:1-2\f*
\s1 Ana Jisos nyehne amahr bade ana Pita bahk-e tene
\r (Mak 14:27-31; Luk 22:31-34; Jon 13:36-38)
\p 
\v 31 Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Atv maa ḿ bahke dulu tib esi ejame. Tibre bo nyono go nwer Esowo re,
\q1 “ ‘M bahke wulu mbaabebul,
\q1 ejoro bahke yaame ebo.’\f + \fr 26:31 \ft Jon 16:32\f*
\m 
\v 32 Ngare nyi m ma nyahme, m bahk-n gboko mbang, song rehng go Galili.”\f + \fr 26:32 \ft Mat 28:7\f*
\p 
\v 33 Owo Pita kehm-e faange re, “Afi ane baka kpee dulu na, me, wa n nehm be sa.”
\p 
\v 34 Owo Jisos kehm-e tongo re, “Etingitingi, n kp-a tongo re, Atv maa, re nkok kehm kuku, a bahke gbaame nkpel era re, me a nehme kahn.”
\p 
\v 35 Pita kehm-e faange re, “Afi elkv ni m bahke kpoko a na, wa n nehm tiki ten.”
\p Abatꞌtoono bako kpee tob bung ano fvfo.
\s1 Ana Jisos kake ero go Gesemani
\r (Mak 14:32-42; Luk 22:39-46)
\p 
\v 36 Owo Jisos kehm koko abatꞌtoono ebe, tahm a bo song rehng go edi ji bo jo lung re Gesemani, kehm tongo bo re, “Jiin ana, tete me n song kak ero o feere.”
\p 
\v 37 Á kehm rodo Pita, a abon abal ba Sibidi, tahm a bo. Ndon kehm-e kehme elfili, ala fere jo teel-e.\f + \fr 26:37 \ft Hib 5:7\f*
\v 38 Á kehm tongo bo re, “Eltim ename ebjol ndon ndon sehng, rehng go elkv. Jiin a, wahn jo tob-m elbaabe.”
\p 
\v 39 Á kehm reenge je go esꞌsong, song gbo, kohk esamahr ndi, kehm kehme ero kak re, “Nsoo, tohko ga tahne, fak-m nkob erem nyia. Ana koro me sang, ana koro wo wo.”\f + \fr 26:39 \ft Jon 12:27; Hib 5:8; Fil 2:8\f*
\p 
\v 40 Á kehm feere ba kpiri abatꞌtoono ebe kpꞌlale, kehm tongo Pita re, “Ḿ maam ji awa anyehng nya nya tob-m elbaaba?
\v 41 Jo baaben, wahn jo kak ero, eji ń lꞌkꞌyel go elgaare. Etohko, mbang nyi Esowo kp-e koro, wo ga, ngubjing kpꞌleenge.”
\p 
\v 42 Á kehm kpe feere, song kak ero re, “Nsoo, lꞌfere jol nyi m bahke woko go nkob nyia, a tohko fere fak-m nkob nyia go elbohngo, nong, mbang enya lim!”
\p 
\v 43 Eji á kpe feere ba, á kehm kpe ba nyehn bo kpꞌlale. Tibre akpakamahr lubu bo ellu ellu.\f + \fr 26:43 \ft Rom 7:22-23\f*
\p 
\v 44 Jisos kehm kpe tahm bo sa, kpe song kak ero bꞌnehm.
\v 45 Á kehm kpe feere ba kpiri abatꞌtoono ebe, kehm tongo bo re, “Ń kpi nlale nlala, fere jo re ekva? Ngare ebkabbe na a, nyi bo bahke jabbe Mmon no nne, kak aneb abiafem go ebo.
\v 46 Mehlen, wahr tahmen! Nyehnen, nne no bahk-m jabbe ka, ma kabbe a.”
\s1 Ana bo bobo Jisos
\r (Mak 14:43-50; Luk 22:47-53; Jon 18:3-12)
\p 
\v 47 Eji Jisos kpi mbungu mbungu, Judas ji woomo go ellong abatꞌtoono ebe, ewubu ane abal, kehm ba lohng, a ellong ane gbalee ba fili akahngkahng, a atahmtahm. Atubesi abalimajom, a anebkul nfam ba tumu bo.
\p 
\v 48 Nne no gung-e no tongo ane bao wuku wuku ana bo bahke liingi Jisos. Á tongo bo re, “Nne no n lꞌsod-e nnyo, ye wo, ḿ bahk-e bobo.”
\v 49 Owo á kehm soro sehng na sehng, song rehng goji Jisos, kehm bungu re, “Ntꞌtibi, n kp-a kake nnyo,” kehm soro sod-e nnyo.
\p 
\v 50 Jisos kehm-e bahbe re, “Mbi, a ba jen?”
\p Owo bo kehm bake, ba bob Jisos.
\v 51 Nne awohng go ellong ane ba jolo a Jisos o kehm wobo ekahngkahng ebe go mbak, kpale nlokeltum a ntubesi abalimajom etung.
\p 
\v 52 Owo Jisos kehm-e tongo re, “Feere a ekahngkahng eba, wo kak go mbak! Tibre ane ba kpo nok abohng akahngkahng, bo bahke kpoko elkv akahngkahng.
\v 53 Anv, a nehme kahn re, n jol ma gboongo Nsoo, á tum sehnge nlong enjel ewubbal re bo ba kak-m eboa?\f + \fr 26:53 \ft Jon 10:18\f*
\v 54 Wo, lꞌfere jol ano, adi nwer Esowo nya bungu bade elkv ename bahke kehm jolo go etingitingi renan?”
\p 
\v 55 Owo Jisos kehm bungu tong ellong ane bao re, “Anv, ń lohngo ba a akahngkahng, a atahmtahm re wahn ba bob-m ana n li nwajva? Efung abehng abehng n jo ji go etahk Esowo, jo tib-n, me ń tikem bob.
\v 56 Nyaa kpee limi, eji alum nya abanyehnamahr Esowo nyono no lꞌlohko jol go etingitingi.”\f + \fr 26:56 \ft Mat 26:31\f*
\p Abatꞌtoono ebe kpee kehm-e yaame sa, be ebo tahm.
\s1 Ana Jisos yiimi go esamahr elam
\r (Mak 14:53-65; Luk 22:54-55,63-71; Jon 18:13-14,19-24)
\p 
\v 57 Ane ba bobo Jisos kehm-e koko, tahm a ne go etahk Kayafas ji jolo ntubesi abalimajom. Owo atꞌtibi ba atahm, a anebkul nfam kono asi.
\v 58 Jisos jo jene ekv. Pita jen ekv, á kehm ba rehng go nlaaga ntubesi abalimajom, kehm song ji a alokeltum nfontahk, eji á lꞌnyehn ji bahke jolo.
\p 
\v 59 Atubesi abalimajom, anebkul nfam, a atul esub jo sebe mbang ana nyi bo bahke kiimi afahnge lake Jisos, toono o, bo wul-e.
\v 60 Bo tikem kahn mbang anyehng anyehng, jol eji akimfahnge atianse gbalee lohngo lohng ba yiimi.
\p Esꞌkohro, akimfahnge atianse na abal kehm gohro lohng ba yiimi,
\v 61 fere bung re, “Nne noa tongo re, á bahke ma wa etahk Esowo, fere tuungu si go nfung era.”\f + \fr 26:61 \ft Jon 2:19-21\f*
\p 
\v 62 Owo ntubesi abalimajom kehm mehle yiimi, kehm bahbe Jisos re, “A nehm faanga? Ejum aji ane baa kpꞌbungu tob-a?”
\p 
\v 63 Jisos belle na eje.
\p Ntubesi abalimajom kehm-e kpe tong re, “N kpa rehke go esamahr Esowo bi li go elkpin re wo tong-r joare wo Mesaya wo, ji li Mmon no Esowo.”
\p 
\v 64 Owo Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Me wo. N kp-a tongo re, Bomo anv asongo ḿ bahke nyehne Mmon no nne jehk go ejang eboblum bi Esowo bi gbale sehng, ń fere nyehn-e á kpꞌbake go akparesemsem.”\f + \fr 26:64 \ft Mat 24:30; Ell 14:14\f*
\p 
\v 65 Owo ntubesi abalimajom noo kehm yare ewobo eje, kehm bungu re, “Yebsu Esowo! Ntianse anyehng anyehng e nehme kpe seb. Wahnfono antahng ebwuk abꞌbi alum nya á ma bung.
\p 
\v 66 “Ń tiri renan?” Bo kehm faange re, “Yebli ebi ji fuumu re bo wul-e.”\f + \fr 26:66 \ft Jon 10:33; 19:7\f*
\p 
\v 67 Bo kehm soko atel wohng-e go ege esamahr, fere dv-e. Egom jindiki jo ruum-e nkpal,
\v 68 fere jo bung re, “Mesaya, nyehn-r amahr, wo fere tong-r nne no rum-a no.”
\s1 Ana Pita tene Jisos
\r (Mak 14:66-72; Luk 22:56-62; Jon 18:15-18,25-27)
\p 
\v 69 Pita ji eje ga elatahk. Nlokeltum awohng no jolo nnenkal kehm lohngo ba rehng go ege, kehm-e tongo re, “Wo fvfo, a tob jolo a Jisos ji Galili.”
\p 
\v 70 Á kehm gbaame go esamahr ane bao kpee re, “N nehme kahn ejum ji a kpꞌbꞌbung.”
\p 
\v 71 Eji Pita ma tahm, song rehng go mbuga, nnenkal noko kehm-e kpe nyehn, kehm tongo ane ba jolo ona re, “Ye jia tob jolo a Jisos ji Nasaret.”
\p 
\v 72 Á kehm kpe gbaame, fere tir re, “Nne noo, we n nehme kahn.”
\p 
\v 73 Eji ma ji mmokidi, ane ba yiimi kohlo o kehm bake ba kpiri Pita, kehm-e tongo re, “Etingitingi, a tob wob go bo ellong. Tibre alum nya a kpꞌbungu, nya nya kpꞌtibi ejahbe ji a lohng no.”
\p 
\v 74 Pita kehm tiri re, “Esowo demm-m na demme. N nehme kahn nne noo.”
\p Tvtv ona nkok kehm soro kuk.
\p 
\v 75 Pita kehm soro buumu alum nya Jisos tong-e re, “Re nkok kehm kuku, a bahk-m tene nkpel era.” Pita kehm lohngo ona, song kehme ellingi ndon ndon.
\c 27
\s1 Ana bo ko Jisos, tahm a ne goji Pailet, nne a Rom no jo fili Juda
\r (Mak 15:1; Luk 23:1-2; Jon 18:28-32)
\p 
\v 1 Eji efungfu se no, atubesi abalimajom kpee, a anebkul nfam kehm toobo ana bo bahke wulu Jisos.
\v 2 Eji bo m-e kak agbekobo, bo kehm-e koko, tahm a ne, song yak-e kak Pailet go ebo, ye ji jolo ntubesi ejahbe.
\s1 Ana Judas kpo no
\r (Elt 1:18-19)
\p 
\v 3 Eji Judas ji gung-e no nyehne re, Jisos ebli ebi, á kehm gboko ndon, fere rod mpon esehma nyio, feere a nyi re á song ka atubesi abalimajom, a anebkul nfam,\f + \fr 27:3 \ft Mat 26:15\f*
\v 4 kehm bungu tong bo re, “Me n lim abiafem, eji n gungu nne no ki lim ebi ajehng ajehng.”
\p Bo kehm-e faange re, “O elam ejahre sang, nfem enya nyi go.”
\p 
\v 5 Á kehm saade akpohko nyao, kak go etahk Esowo, kehm tahme eje, song kahn elne ekehd.
\p 
\v 6 Atubesi abalimajom kehm rodo akpohko nyao, fere bung re, “Abi akpohko nyaa, akpohko alung nya. Fuumem re, akpohko nyaa woomo semme a akpohko ayare.”
\p 
\v 7 Bo kehm toobo, rod akpohko nyao, song gunu edi egbe ji jolo ji ntokatu, eji bo lꞌjo kpa ajahmjahm kak edi ndi jio.
\v 8 Owo wahnge bo kpo lung edi ndi jio re, “Egbe alung”, tete sik anv.
\p 
\v 9 Owo kehm lohko jol go etingitingi ana nnyehnamahr Jeremaya bungu no re, “Bo rodo mpon esehma nyio nyi jolo ekun bi aneb Israel taame re bo ka go ege esi,
\v 10 song gunu edi egbe ji ntokatu, ana Jehova tong-m no.”
\s1 Ana Pailet jo bahb Jisos abahbe
\r (Mak 15:2-5; Luk 23:3-5; Jon 18:33-38)
\p 
\v 11 Jisos kehm song yiimi go esamahr ntubesi ejahbe no bahb-e re, “Wo wo li ntul no Jusa?”
\p Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Ee, me wo.”
\p 
\v 12 Eji atubesi abalimajom, a anebkul nfam jo ka-e ebi, ejumjum á faangem.\f + \fr 27:12 \ft Mat 26:63\f*
\p 
\v 13 Owo Pailet kehm-e bahbe re, “Anv, a nehme wuk nsol gbalee nyi bo kpꞌbungu tob-aa?”
\p 
\v 14 Jol Jisos we tikem faange.\f + \fr 27:14 \ft Jon 19:9\f*
\p Ntubesi ejahbe noo kehm-e kpoko esi tete.
\s1 Elam ji bo kimi re bo wul Jisos
\r (Mak 15:6-15; Luk 23:13-25; Jon 18:39-19:16)
\p 
\v 15 Elkak anehng anehng ntubesi ejahbe jo kono elyehke nne a ngbekobo awohng, ka ellong ane, no bo lꞌseb.
\v 16 Ngare nyio nne awohng woomo ngbekobo, no bo jo lung-e re Barabas. Nnene jolem no ki-e kahn.
\p 
\v 17 Eji bo ba kono edi ajehng, Pailet kehm bahbe bo re, “Nne awo ń kpꞌsebe re me n yehke yake, Barabas, afi Jisos ji bo kpo lung-e re Kraist?”
\p 
\v 18 Tibre á jo kahne kpee re, bo ko-e ba ka-e, tib eji á jo teele bo ala.\f + \fr 27:18 \ft Elt 13:45\f*
\p 
\v 19 Eji Pailet jehk go ege eti elam, nkal ewe kehm tiingi tv-e re, “Ka lak etingi nne jio abo, tibre ye wo wahng ka n nyehne erem gbalee go egama nlem nyi n leeme no lela.”
\p 
\v 20 Atubesi abalimajom, a anebkul nfam kehm kehme ellong ane bao eltim sennge re, bo gboongo Pailet, á yehke Barabas yake, fere wul Jisos.
\p 
\v 21 Ntubesi ejahbe noo kehm bahbe bo re, “Ane abal baa, nne awo ń kpꞌsebe re me n yehke yake?”
\p Bo kehm faange re, “Barabas wo.”\f + \fr 27:21 \ft Elt 3:14; 1 Pit 3:18\f*
\p 
\v 22 Pailet kehm bahbe bo re, “Anv, me n lim Jisos jen, ye ji bo kpo lung-e re Kraist?”
\p Bo ane kpee kehm faange re, “Kum-e go ekros!”
\v 23 Ntubesi ejahbe noo kehm bahbe re, “Anv, ebi aji á ma lim?”
\p Bo kehm kpe rabe wahre wahre wahre re, “Kum-e go ekros!”
\p 
\v 24 Eji Pailet sebe kahn re, ejumjum kpeem li ji á bahke kpe ma lim, gana ntong yahke gbo, owo á kehm koko alahb, ba ru abo go esamahr ane bao, kehm bungu re, “Elkv ni nne noa bahke kpoko, ebo ebame o wobem, nfem enyahne nyi go.”
\p 
\v 25 Owo ellong ane bao kpee kehm-e faange re, “Nong, alung eme tuun-r, a abon abon ebahre.”
\p 
\v 26 Pailet kehm yehke Barabas ka bo, á for, tong bo dv Jisos, fere yak-e ka re bo song kum-e go ekros.
\s1 Ana nsoja nyoko Jisos
\r (Mak 15:16-20; Jon 19:2-3)
\p 
\v 27 Owo nsoja nyi ntubesi ejahbe noo kehm rodo Jisos, tahm a ne go nlaaga ntubesi noo, kehm song lung ellong nsoja nehko re bo ba.
\v 28 Bo kehm-e yehke nsol go ngubjing, fere kak-e mbilibili ekpawobo ana ji atul kpo kono elkake.
\v 29 Bo kehm tahnge ekpasi akpiri, ba konng-e go esi, fere ka-e ebti, á fili go ege eboblum, kehm jo gbo, jamm-e alahng go ege alata, fere jo nyok-e re, “E kp-a kake nnyo, ntul no Jus.”
\v 30 Bo kehm jo so atel wohng-e, fere taare ebti bi á fili go ebo, jo rum-e go esi.
\v 31 Eji bo m-e nyok ano kpee, owo bo kehm-e yehke ekpawobo jio, feere a nsol enye kak-e, ko-e tahm a ne re bo song kum-e go ekros.
\s1 Ana bo kumu Jisos go ekros
\r (Mak 15:21-32; Luk 23:26-43; Jon 19:17-27)
\p 
\v 32 Eji bo ma lohng fi, bo kehm song nyehn nne no bo jo lung-e re Saimon ji jolo nne a Sirin. Bo kehm-e bobo re á sol ekros ji Jisos.
\p 
\v 33 Eji bo song rehng go edi ji bo jo lung re Golgota ji lohngo re “edi nkpakesi”,
\v 34 owo bo kehm-e kake amahm ma bo semme alullul anyane. Eji Jisos wuungu no, á kpeem wo.
\v 35 Bo kum-e kan a lake go ekros, bo kehm soro kehme elfaange tub, eji bo lꞌmal baange nsol ebjing enye.
\v 36 Eji bo ma baange nsol nyio, bo kehm jehke o, jo baab-e.
\p 
\v 37 Bo kehm lake ekpakenwer go ero kohlo go ege esi, ji bo nyono ebi ji bo ka-e re, “A WO LI JISOS, NTUL NO JUS.”
\v 38 Owo bo kehm tob kum awajv abal lake go akros, noko go ege ejang eboblum, noko go ege ejang ebobkal.
\p 
\v 39 Ane ba jo sehng go mbang kehm kehme aromo tuubu, fere jo su-e re,
\v 40 “Wo sang jo bung re, a bahke wake etahk Esowo, fere tuungu si go nfung eraa? Tahre elna anv me! Lꞌjol re, wo Mmon no Esowo wo, badde go ekros me!”\f + \fr 27:40 \ft Mat 26:61; Jon 2:19-21\f*
\p 
\v 41 Atubesi abalimajom, a atꞌtibi ba atahm, go anebkul nfam tob jo nyok-e ano fvfo re,
\v 42 “Á kpo tahre ane bako, yefono nehm ma tahre elne! Lꞌjol re ye ntul no Israel wo, nong, á tohko badde go ekros ba, wahr kehm taame tv-e.\f + \fr 27:42 \ft Mat 12:39-40\f*
\v 43 Á kpo bum Esowo go etingitingi, nong, Esowo tahr-e me, á lꞌkor-e. Tibre á kpo bung re, ye Mmon Esowo wo.”
\v 44 Awajv nya bo tob kumu bo ana ye, jo tob su-e ano.
\s1 Ana Jisos kpo no
\r (Mak 15:33-41; Luk 23:44-49; Jon 19:28-30)
\p 
\v 45 Eji efin ma yiimi, ejannge kehm gboko go ejahbe jio kpee, ji tete biingi awa ara.
\p 
\v 46 Eji ma rehng nkaranka era nyi elgung, Jisos kehm rabe wahre wahre wahre re, “Eli, Eli, lama sabaktani?” ji lohngo re, “Nsoo, Nsoo, jen ji wahng ka a ma-m yake ana?”\f + \fr 27:46 \ft 2 Kor 5:21\f*
\p 
\v 47 Ane bandiki ba yiimi o wuk, kehm bungu re, “Á kpi Elaija lung.”
\p 
\v 48 Owo nne awohng kehm soro be eje, song rod ndꞌdahng, suku go evinegar, tung go esi ebti, rod ton-e re á yab.
\v 49 Egom ane bako kehm bungu re, “Tohken nong, wahr nyehnen, joare Elaija bahke bake, ba tahr-e.”
\p 
\v 50 Jisos kehm kpe rabe wahre wahre wahre, kehm yake etohko eje ka go.
\v 51 Owo ekpiki ji bo tohko go etahk Esowo kehm soro yang ejang ebbal, bomo go ero tete ba jahm ndi.\f + \fr 27:51 \ft Hib 10:19-20\f* Ndi kehm gbehke. Akpartal bahnge.
\v 52 Alahm kehm lennge. Aneb Esowo gbalee ba kpo no, kehm nyahme.
\v 53 Ngare nyi Jisos nyahme go elkv, bo kehm lohngo go alahm, tahm song rehng go Jeusalem. Owo ane gbalee nyehne bo.\f + \fr 27:53 \ft Elt 26:23\f*
\p 
\v 54 Eji ntubesi a nsoja, a nsoja nyehko nyi jo tob baabe Jisos a ne nyehne ana ndi ma gbehke, fere nyehn nsol nyehko nyi kpe lim budu, bo kehm kehme elfahle, fere kehme elbungu re, “Etingitingi, nne noa lohko jol Mmon no Esowo!”
\p 
\v 55 Anebkal gbalee ba lohngo go Galili, ba jo toono Jisos, fere jo kak-e ebo, yiimi ebo go fee, jo nyehn.\f + \fr 27:55 \ft Luk 8:2-3\f*
\v 56 Meri ji lohng go Magdala woomo go bo ellong, a Meri nnyehn Jems a Josef, go nnyehn abon Sibidi.
\s1 Ana bo kake Jisos go elahm
\r (Mak 15:42-47; Luk 23:50-56; Jon 19:38-42)
\p 
\v 57 Eji elgung ma ba, efange nne ajehng ji bo jo lung-e re Josef, ji lohng go Arimatia kehm bake. Ye fvfo tob jolo ntꞌtoono no Jisos.
\v 58 Á kehm tahme song kpiri Pailet, fere gboong-e re á yake ekv ji Jisos ka-e. Pailet kehm tongo re, bo yake ekv eje ka-e.
\v 59 Josef kehm rodo ekv ji Jisos, kpennge abarebare abomo nya nfenfe,
\v 60 fere rod, song kak go ege elahm bi bo kpꞌna rahme go ekpartal. Á kehm bannge egburu eltal, bulu go nnyo elahm, kehm tahme eje.
\v 61 Meri ji lohng go Magdala, a Meri jehko, bo kehm song ji, wane elahm bio.
\s1 Ane ba jo baabe elahm
\p 
\v 62 Etoono efung behko, eji efung ebjing atoobo ma sehng, atubesi abalimajom, a Bab Farisi kehm song kono asi go etahk Pailet,
\v 63 kehm-e tongo re, “Nsoo, wahr ebbuumu ana nnehm a nne noo bungu ngare nyi á kpeke li go elkpin re, ‘Nfung era m bahke nyahme go elkv.’\f + \fr 27:63 \ft Mat 12:40\f*
\v 64 Tum ane, bo song baabe elahm bio tete nfung era nyio biingi, eji abatꞌtoono ebe lꞌkꞌsong v ekv eje, fere jo bung tong ane re, ‘Yebnyahme go elkv’. Tohko jol ano, esꞌkohro enehm bia bahke sabe sehnge bi ngbokambang.”
\p 
\v 65 Owo Pailet kehm bungu re, “Koon abꞌbaabe, wahn song baabe elahm ana ń kahne no.”
\p 
\v 66 Bo kehm tahme, song bum abꞌbaabe o re bo baabe elahm, fere rod elak lake, kak elliingi,\f + \fr 27:66 \ft Ell 5:1\f* (eji bo lꞌkahn, nne lꞌyel go elahm).
\c 28
\s1 Ana Jisos nyahme go elkv
\r (Mak 16:1-10; Luk 24:1-12; Jon 20:1-10)
\p 
\v 1 Eji Esabat ma sehng, ngbokambang efung go erahde, efungfu behre behre Meri ji lohng go Magdala, a Meri jehko, bo kehm tahme re, bo song nyehn elahm.
\v 2 Owo ndi kehm soro kehme elgbehke tete, tibre enjel nyi Jehova lohngo go ejahbetul Esowo ba, ba bannge eltal nio bum go nkpe, fere ji.
\v 3 Á jolo are emangedu ji. Nsol nyi á kake go ngubjing jo bare kparaang.\f + \fr 28:3 \ft Mat 17:2; Elt 1:10\f*
\v 4 Abꞌbaabe bao fahl-e sehng, fere jo kꞌkahm, bo fere jolo are akvne nya.
\p 
\v 5 Enjel nyio kehm tongo anebkal bao re, “Kana kpe fahl! Tibre n kpꞌkahne re, n kpi Jisos seb, ji bo kum-e go ekros.
\v 6 Ana á limm, yebnyahme fi, ana á bungu no. Baan, wahn ba nyehn edi ji á noongo no.
\v 7 Songen anv elwaare, wahn song tong abatꞌtoono ebe re, yebnyahme go elkv. Á bahk-n gboko mbang song rehng go Galili.\f + \fr 28:7 \ft Mat 26:32\f* Go wo ḿ bahk-e nyehne. Buumen ji m ma-n tong a!”
\p 
\v 8 Owo bo kehm lohngo go elahm elwaare, elfahle elfahle, a egburu eyebatahng, be re bo song tong abatꞌtoono ebe.
\v 9 Eji bo fi no re bo song tong abatꞌtoono ebe, owo Jisos kehm ba wane bo, kehm bungu re, “N kp-n kake nnyo.”
\p Bo kehm jeere kohl-e, jamm-e alahng, jabb-e akpade, fere kak-e.
\v 10 Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Kana kpe fahl! Songen, wahn song tong abonanee re,\f + \fr 28:10 \ft Hib 2:11\f* bo song go Galili. Go wo bo bahk-m nyehne.”
\s1 Ana abꞌbaabe elahm song tooro
\p 
\v 11 Eji anebkal bao ma tahm fi, abꞌbaabe elahm bandiki kehm tahme, song rehng go nla ejahbe, song tooro ejum ajehng ajehng ji ma lim, tong atubesi abalimajom.
\v 12 Atubesi abalimajom, a anebkul nfam kehm song kono edi ajehng, kehm toobo, ka abꞌbaabe elahm bao akpohko gbalee,
\v 13 kehm bungu re,
\p “Ana wo ḿ bahke jo bung re, ‘Abatꞌtoono ebe ba atv, ba v nkvne, tahm a ne ngare nyi e jo lal.’\f + \fr 28:13 \ft Mat 27:64\f*
\v 14 Ntubesi ejahbe lꞌwuk, e bahke song bung a ne, wahn, kana tiiri!”
\p 
\v 15 Abꞌbaabe elahm bao kehm rodo akpohko nyao, song lim ana bo tongo bo. Eka jia, Jus kpi ntubu ntubu, tong atem tete sik anv.
\s1 Ana Jisos ba kpiri abatꞌtoono ebe
\r (Mak 16:14-18; Luk 24:36-49; Jon 20:19-23; Elt 1:6-8)
\p 
\v 16 Abatꞌtoono Jisos, ewubu a nne awohng, bo kehm tahme go ewong ajehng ji li go Galili, edi ji Jisos tongo bo re bo je.
\v 17 Eji bo nyehn-e no, bo kehm gboko, jamm-e alahng, fere kak-e. Egom jindiki jo fꞌfaabe.
\p 
\v 18 Jisos kehm jeere kohlo bo, kehm tongo bo re, “Bo ma-m ka nsahm kpee nyi m bahke jo fili ejahbetul Esowo, fere jo fili njini.\f + \fr 28:18 \ft Mat 11:27; Ef 1:20-23\f*
\v 19 Songen fvfo go njini kpee, wahn song lim ane, bo jol abatꞌtoono ebame go ejahbe ajehng ajehng. Wohngen bo alahb go mbing nyi Nsoo, a Mmon, a Etingi Etohko,
\v 20 wahn fere tib bo, bo jo bum ejum ajehng ajehng ji m ma-n tong. Buumen re, m bahke jolo a nahne ngare anyehng anyehng tete eying jia mal.”
